\id ACT - Luyana Bible Translation Project 
\h Tikezo 
\toc1 Etikezo no Atumiwa 
\toc2 Tikezo 
\toc3 Tik 
\mt1 TIKEZO 
\mt2 no Atumiwa 
\imt1 Okulimukisa ku Tikezo 
\ip Ebuka no Tikezo ni buka no ngambolo no matatekelo no Keleke noomo inakuhasanyezwa okutunda mu Jelusalema okuta mu Judeya, mu Samaliya, mane ni mumaneku anjili ngeso, kanyi feela omo Jesu ana kwambelela aaiyetwa aye abo yo kasi kambamena kale ku wilu (1.8). Kama inakuñoliwa kwa Luka woyo kame yona kuñola Eliywi okwamana kwa Luka. Neli osikukwiyeta onene kona kuli kama anaku mamelanga onene mukuteula oulshanago wino. Nakulita etibuka tonje, ebuka yaye mane ni buka no Tikezo kwa Siofilasi woyo neli mu Gelike, kono eti buka tonyene kama tina kuñolelwa kumindi yao asikulapela bomweya ku ma Gelike mane ni ku ma Juda (1.1). 
\ip Ebuka no Tikezo kuti kama ina kun̄oliwa mukaci ka myaka 60-64 munyima no kuleiwa kwa Kilesite kakuli ebuka kama ibwa abo Paulusi yoka situndisiwa kale mutolongo. Luka kame nakwendabo ni mutumiwa Paulusi mi mane kame ana kuñola eyi ebuka yooli mu Antiyoki. Cwale abo Etikezo ni kutwalelela ku buka ya Luka mi kama itateka ni Jesu yo Kamba mena kuwilu. Elibaka no kuñola eyi ebuka kama lukufekile kanyi eliba ana kuñolela ebuka ya Luka. Kama ana kusaelanga Siofilasi nji mane nipalo no asikulapela ikule ngeso kanyi omo ana kwiyeteta mi nakuñola okwamana ni kuyoya kwa Jesu mane ni kuhasana kwaa sikulapela. 
\ip Ebuka no Tikezo kama ituba omwanda no Tikeleke no matatekelo noomo tina kumonahalelanga okuyoya mu tumelo mwa Jesu. Omwanda no atumiwa kama utumonisa omo tufanena okusepela amaata no Mebo no kukena muku hasanya eliñusa kwaa kwetu. 
\iot Emitwi no yambo 
\io2 Baweli e Mebo no kukena kama iiya kwaaiyetwa mane ni Tikeleke sebeli titateka okukula (1.1-8; 1). 
\io2 Aka no wili etikeleke kama tiyandisiwa mi sebeli titateka okukutaba mwiibaka ili kundee ya Jelusalema (8.2-12; 23). 
\io2 Munyima yeyo Paulusi sebeli ota mumusipili waye no matatekelo noulapeli (12.24-14; 28). 
\io2 Cwale abo ekuta sebeli ikuwana ba Jelusalema okulelisana eso sifanena kwa sikulumela aano ubya (15.1-35). 
\io2 Esisis tatamakao Paulusi sebeli ota mumusipili waye nowili noulumeli (15.36-18; 22). 
\io2 Munyima yeyo sebeli okutela mumusipili waye nowatu noulumeli (18.23-20; 38) 
\io2 Cwale abo Paulusi yo wanungiwa kale mu Jelusalema (21-26) 
\io2 Bama maneneno sebeli otundisiwa mu Jelusalema okutwaliwa ku Loma (27-28). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Mutompehi Teofilasi, mu buka no matatekelo, kame nina kun̄ola etingambolo no inu yonje ana ku tenda Jesu ni kwiyeta  
\v 2 okutwala ba liywaa ana ku shimbelwa ku wilu, aba ana kumana okuba etaelo mu maata no Mebo No Kukena kwaa tumiwa awo ana kuketa.  
\v 3 Munyima no mayando aye sebeli okumonahaza kwa onyene yo yoya mu ukumonahaza aka no kupula mu maywaa anakukwana makumi anee (40) mi yo lemine okwamba eyi no mubuso wa Nyambe.  
\v 4 Yo ikalile noo, sebeli waaba etaelo nji mulese okutunda mu Jelusalema, kono mu tatelele esepiso ya Sitange eyo ana kwamba, eyi muna yupu kwa mene.  
\v 5 Kakuli Jowani naku kolobeza ni meyi, kono kakwisa amaywaa no kupula okutunda abano anyi mba mukolobeziwa ni Mebo No Kukena. 
\s1 Jesu yo shimbelwa ku wilu 
\r (Maleka16.19-20; Luka24.50-53) 
\p  
\v 6 Cwale atumiwa aba ana kukuwana ni Jesu, sebeli amwibanguta nji, “Mbumu, ninji ba nako ino kame so usete omubuso kwa Isilaele?”  
\v 7 Jesu sebeli waatambula nji, “Ka musibiwa okulimuka enako simba emiaka eyo ana beeke sitange mu maata aye.  
\v 8 Kono mba mutambula amaata aba saiiye Emebo No Kukena baanyi, mi kame samutende etipaki tange mu Jelusalema, ni mu Judeya ni mu Samaliya moonje, ni kutwala ku mamaneneno no litunga.”  
\v 9 Aba ana kumana okwamba ngeso, sebeli oshimbelwa ku wilu amwalikete, mi elikumbi sebeli limutundisa mu miyo oo.  
\v 10 Yo katile ku wilu, mi onyene aaliketile ku wilu, ababo alume ayiili akufukile etinyambi no likena, sebeli aiya mukwimana ku nyonga yoo.  
\v 11 Sebeli aamba nji, “Aanyi alume no Galileya, ngasibine aba mwimanine me mwaliketile ku wilu? Uyu Jesu, ona shimbiwa okuta ku wilu, mbaiyi mundila imweya kanyi omo mumumonena yo katile mu wilu.” 
\s1 Matiyasi aba na Ketiwa nji ayole Judasi 
\r (Mateu27.3-10) 
\p  
\v 12 Cwale atumiwa aba ana kuukela ku Jelusalema okutunda ba lilundu no itondo ya Olibe, eli lili beebi ni Jelusalema mi omusipili wateni kame okukumanena ni liywaa no Sabata ba ku weenda.  
\v 13 Cwale aba ana kwingena mu mulenen̄i, sebeli ata ku musiyo oli kuwilu omo ana kwikalanga Pitolosi, ni Jowani, ni Jakobo, ni Andiliyasi, ni Filipi, ni Tomasi, ni Batolome, ni Mateu, ni Jakobo omwana Alufeya, ni Simoni Zeloti, ni Judasi omwana Jakobo.  
\v 14 Onje aa muumweya sebeli aongoteteta oku lapela, bamweya naakati, okubekabo ni Maliya inawaye Jesu, na inaaye. 
\p  
\v 15 Mu maywaa awo Pitolosi sebeli oimana mukaci no aasikupumena bamweya naaanu no kupula aa akwana omwaanda naanu makumi ayili (120), ni kwamba nji,  
\v 16 “Aalikani ange, elin̄olo kame lifanena okwiyatetetwa, elyo ku Mebo No Kukena eli lina kwambiwa kwa Dabida, eli lyaama oku kumanena eya Judasi woyo ona kutwaletela aa ana kununga Jesu.  
\v 17 Kakuli neli omunjili mwaaci mi kame ana kubiwa ekalulo mu musebezi wetu.” ( 
\v 18 Cwale wuyu mulume sebeli oula elitema ni mupuzo no mali no uyii waye, mi sebeli okwela banji ni kukauka bakaci mi einu na mu lipumo lyaye sebeli itundela bandee. 
\p  
\v 19 Cwale etaba eyi sebeli ilimukiwa kwaanu onje ana kwikala mu Jelusalema, mi elyo litema sebeli liisaniwa nji Hakeludama mu mushobo woo, okutalusa nji, “Elitema no unyinga.”) 
\p  
\v 20 “Kakuli kame ku n̄olilwe mu buka no Lisamu nji, 
\q1 ‘Cwale esibaka saye sifutuke amatota, 
\q2 cwale mi kuulwe omunu so yoya mo.’ 
\m Kame kun̄olilwe kame nji, 
\q1 ‘Mi esibaka saye no musebezi sishimbiwe ku munjili.’ 
\p  
\v 21 “Abakulingeso, omunjili kwa lume onakwendanga naaci mu nako yonje Mbumu Jesu yoenda naaci,  
\v 22 okutangisa ba kolobezo ya Jowani okulita ba liywaa ana ku shimbiwa kwaaci, omunjili kwa lume aa kame afanena okutenda opaki naaci ku kwinguka kwaye.”  
\v 23 Cwale sebeli alita aanu ayili, Josefa osi litina lya Basabasi, (nakwisaniwa kame nji, Jusitasi) ni Matiyasi.  
\v 24 Cwale sebeli a lapela ni kwamba nji, “Mbumu, weene olimukile emicima no aanu onje, otumonise kwaa ayili anyine ona kete  
\v 25 nji ashimbe esibaka mu situlo ni muutumiwa owo ana tundu Judasi, ni kuta ku sibaka saye.”  
\v 26 Cwale sebeli ashebuluka oonje, mi sebeli kulemiwa Matiyasi, woyo ona kwekiziwa kwao atumiwa likumi ni mumweya. (11) 
\c 2  
\s1 Okwiiya no Mebo No Kukena 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale eliywaa no Pentakota aba lina ku keela, onje kame ana kuungana mu sibaka simweya.  
\v 2 Ababo sebeli kuyupahala omulumo ona kutundelela ku wilu kanyi Emebo no lin̄ungwa, mi sebeli iiyala endoo yonje omo ana ikalanga.  
\v 3 Cwale sebeli ku monahala kwa onyene eso sikufekile kanyi etindimi no mulilo, awo aku tabile mi ni kwiiya mu kwikala beulu yoo ba munjili ni munjili.  
\v 4 Onje kame ana kwiyala ku Mebo No Kukena mi sebeli atangisa okwamba mu tipuwo tindina, omo Emebo No Kukena ina kwaa bela okwamba.  
\v 5 Cwale kame kuna kwikalanga aendisi no Majuda mu Jelusalema, awo ana kucilanga Nyambe aa atundelela mu tinaha tonje na mu litunga.  
\v 6 Cwale omulumo owo aba una kuyupahala aanu no kupula sebeli aunganako, mi kame ana kukomoka, kakuli onje kame ana kwayupa aamba mu tipuwo too.  
\v 7 Mi onje kame ana kukomoka onene, ni kwamba nji, “Kasa nji aa onje aamba ni Magalileya?  
\v 8 Cwale iikene aba twaa yupa aamba mutipuwo tetu toonje?  
\v 9 Aaci Amapanta ni Mamede ni Maelami naa ayakile mu Mesopotoniya, ni mu Judeya ni mu Kapadosiya, mu Ponto ni mu Esiya,  
\v 10 aa na ku Filikiya ni Panfiliya, Egepita naa ali mu ibaka no Lebiya ikubapile ni Silene naa atunda mu mindi no Loma, oonje Majuda ni mapulosebelite,  
\v 11 Amakilete ni Maalabe, kame twa yupa aamba mu malimi etu omusebezi no kuwaba wa Nyambe!” 
\p  
\v 12 Mi oonje kame ana kukomoka ni ku hakanyeha, akwambisa oonje nji, “Eyi taba kame italusa iikene?”  
\v 13 Kono anjili sebeli aasheka okwamba nji, “Kame akolilwe ni waine no ubya!” 
\s1 Elin̄usa lya Pitolosi 
\p  
\v 14 Kono Pitolosi sebeli oimana naa akwana likumi ni mumweya ni kwamba ni liywii no kuyupahala onene nji, “Anyi aanu na mu Judeya naanyi monje muyoya mu Jelusalema, mulimuke etaba eyi, mi muteetete wino ku maywi ange. 
\p  
\v 15 Aa aanu kasikoliwa, omo mu hupulela, kakuli ino isili ehola no (9 okoloko),  
\v 16 kono esi esi nakwambiwa kwa munuhi wa Nyambe Jowele nji, 
\q1  
\v 17 ‘Cwale enako no mamaneneno aba saiye, kame kwamba Nyambe, 
\q2 kame sani itele Emebo yange ba munu yonje. 
\q1 mi aanenu no ashimani naa no akatana kame sa nuhe, 
\q2 mi andumbana enu mba mono etipono, 
\q2 mi naa supali enu mbaa loto etitolo. 
\q1  
\v 18 Ee, mi mane naabika ange no alume naa no akati mu maywaa awo, 
\q2 mba na itele Emebo yange mi kame sa nuhe. 
\q1  
\v 19 Kame sani tende etimakazo mu wilu 
\q2 neyi saimonahale ba litunga bano banji. 
\q1 ounyinga, ni mulilo, ni wise 
\q2  
\v 20 eliywaa kame saali futuke okutenda ouwi 
\q2 okweti afutuke kanyi ounyinga, 
\q2 abo eliywaa lya Mbumu ekalya siiya kale, 
\q1 eliywaa linene eli lilimukiwa. 
\q1  
\v 21 Mi cwale ao onje aisana ba litina lya Mbumu kame sayoyisiwe.’ 
\p  
\v 22 “Anyi alume no Esilaele, muyupe amaywi aa! Jesu no Nazaleta omulume muna limukisiwa kwa Nyambe ni emisebezi no kongola, ni timakazo, ni tiponiso eyo ana kutenda Nyambe mwa yonyene mukaci kenu, kanyi omo mulimukele naanyi.  
\v 23 Wuyu Jesu ona kubetekiwa mu muhupulo ni mukulimuka kwa Nyambe, na muku mungongotela ni ku mwibaa ni maoko aawo asiku tenda ouyi.  
\v 24 Kono Nyambe na ku mwingula kwaafu, okumu lukulula kweeyi no kucilisa no aafu, kakuli ka kwa siku twesahala nji anungiwe ku lufu.  
\v 25 Kakuli Dabida abaamba okukumanena ni yonyene nji, 
\q1 “Kame ni monanga Ombumu balubala wange enako yonje, 
\q2 kakuli kame ali ku Lyoko lyange no silyo mi kanitamba okunyanganyisiwa. 
\q1  
\v 26 cwale abo omucima wange kame onaku wabelelwa, mi olulimi lwange kame lunaku nyakalala. 
\q2 mane ni lutu lwange mba luyoyo mu sepo, 
\q1  
\v 27 kakuli kautamba kuleselela Emebo yange mu sibaka no afu, 
\q2 simba nji oleselele woyo no kukena nji aole. 
\q1  
\v 28 Kame ona nimonisa endila ita ku moyo, 
\q2 mi okumonahala kowe kame sakuni iyate oku nyakalala.” 
\p  
\v 29 “Abaange, kame ni myambela epatalaza eyi no njekulyetu Dabida nji kame ana kufa ni kupumbekiwa, mi elibita lyaye kwa lisili kwaaci ni balelo lino.  
\v 30 Mu kutenda omunuhi wa Nyambe, ni mu kulimuka nji Nyambe kame ana musepisa mukweeta kwaye nji kame sakutunde omunjili ku lusika lwaye ni kwikala ba lubona lwaye.  
\v 31 kame ana kumona eyi nakuuso ni kwamba eyi no kwinguka kwa Kilesite nji, 
\q1 ‘Katamba okuleselelwa musibaka no ao no kufa, 
\q2 simba nji olutu lwaye luole.’ 
\m  
\v 32 Yokame Jesu ona ingulwa kwa Nyambe kwaafu, mi mutaba eyo aaci toonje kame tuli etipaki.  
\v 33 Munyima no kukambamisetwa ku Lyoko no silyo lya Nyambe, mi sebeli otambula Emebo No Kukena ana ku sepisiwa kwa Sitaye, cwale na iitelwe kwaaci yo mumona ni ku yupa.  
\v 34 Kakuli Dabida kasiku kambamena ku wilu, kono yo kame onamba nji, 
\q1 ‘OMBUMU naamba kwa Mbumu wange, 
\q2 Oikale ku Lyoko lyange no silyo 
\q1  
\v 35 konji aba sani tende eila yowe esipula no malyatelo no makondo owe.’ 
\p  
\v 36 “Cwale mulesele onje asi ndoo no Isilaele alimuke eniti nji Nyambe na mutende oumbumu ni Kilesite wuyu Jesu woyo munaku ngongotela!” 
\p  
\v 37 Mi cwale aba ana kuyupa eyi, kaa sikukuyupa wino ku micima mi sebeli aamba kwa Pitolosi ni kwa atumiwa onje nji, “Abeetu, ngasibine sa tu tende?” 
\p  
\v 38 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Mubake mi mu kolobeziwe moonje mu litina lya Jesu Kilesite nji mu lemenwe ku ibi yenu, mi mba mu tambula empo no Mebo No Kukena.  
\v 39 Kakuli esepiso kame ili kwaanyi ni kwaa nenu ni kwao ali oku no kuleba, awo onje sa isaniwe kwa Mbumu Nyambe wetu. 
\p  
\v 40 Pitolosi kame ana kwa kutaza ni maywii amanjili no kupula ana kwa kumbela, yo amba nji, “Mu ku babalele ku lusika olo no kwiiba!”  
\v 41 Cwale awo ana ku tambula amaywii aye sebeli akolobeziwa, mi kame sebeli kwekeziwa aanu no kukwana eikiti yaatu (3;000) ba liywaa elyo. 
\s1 Oupilo Mukaci no Alumeli 
\p  
\v 42 Mi cwale sebeli aongoteteta onyene mu tuto no atumiwa, ni muukuwana, muukutabela esinkwa ni mu titapelo. 
\p  
\v 43 Mi okucila sebeli kwikala mwaanu onje, mi etimakazo no kupula ni tiponiso na ikutendahala mwa atumiwa.  
\v 44 Mi asikupumena sebeli aikala bamweya nukutabela einu yoo yonnje.  
\v 45 Mi kame ana kuulisa amatema oo ni ufumu woo ni ku tabela aanu onje, omo ana kusaelela omunu yonje.  
\v 46 Mi mu liywaa ni liywaa kame ana kwikalanga bamweya mu ndoo ya Nyambe, nuukutabela esinkwa mu tindoo too, kame ana kulya eilya yoo mu tabo ni micima no kuwabelelwa.  
\v 47 Aalemine okulumbeka Nyambe ni ku wabelelwa kwaanu onje. Mi mu liywaa ni liywaa Nyambe kame na kuekeza ku palo no awo anakuyoyisiwa. 
\c 3  
\s1 Omulume no siyanga yo Balisiwa 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale Pitolosi ni Jowani kame ana ku kambemena ku ndoo ya Nyambe ba nako no milapelo, enako no munji eitenda eyi no waatu (15:00 okoloko).  
\v 2 Mi kame kuna kwikala omulume no siyanga okutunda ba kuleiwa kwaye kame ana kushimbiwangwa, woyo ona kubekiwangwa ba mwelo no limota lya Jeluslema mu liywaa, owo ona kwisaniwa nji wa kuwaba nji akumbele etuso kwaanu awo ana kwingenanga mu ndoo ya Nyambe.  
\v 3 Cwale aba na kumona Pitolosi ni Jowani aingena, sebeli waakumbela amali.  
\v 4 Mi Pitolosi sebeli omwaliketa, bamweya ni Jowani ni kwamba nji, “Otwa likete!”  
\v 5 Cwale yonyene sebeli waaliketa ni ku tatelela okutambula esinjili okutundelela kwa onyene.  
\v 6 Kono Pitolosi sebeli omwambela nji, “Mene sikwite esilibela ni gauda, kono kame ni kuba esi nikwite, mu litina lya Jesu Kilesite no Nazaleta, oimane wende!” 
\p  
\v 7 Pitolosi sebeli omushimba ni Lyoko no silyo ni ku mwimeka, mi ababo amakondo ni tingongo taye sebeli yongola.  
\v 8 Mi sebeli omatoka ni kwimana ni kweenda ni kwingena mu lilapa no ndoo ya Nyambe nonyene, yo enda ni ku matoka ni ku lumbeka Nyambe.  
\v 9 Mi aanu onje sebeli amumona yo enda ni ku lumbeka Nyambe,  
\v 10 sebeli amulimuka nji yokame osikukumbela etituso ba mweelo no kuwaba no ndoo ya Nyambe, mi kame ana kukomoka onene ni kumakala kweyo ina tendahala kwa yonyene woyo mulume. 
\s1 Pitolosi yo Aamba Kwaanu 
\p  
\v 11 Abo yo situndamene Pitolosi ni Jowani, aanu onje sebeli aitukela kwa onyene mu sibaka no mukunda wa Solomoni, akomokile onene.  
\v 12 Mi cwale Pitolosi aba na mono ngeso sebeli waambela aanu nji, “Alume no Isilaele, iikene aba mu komoka etaba eyi, simba iikene aba mu twaliketile ngeso, kanyi ni mu maata etu simba ni mu kukuna kwetu kwa Nyambe aba tuna twese wuyu mulume nji aende?  
\v 13 Nyambe wa Abulahama ni wa Isaka ni wa Jakobo, Onyambe wa anjekulyetu, kame ana kanyisa omubika waye Jesu, woyo muna kuba ni ku mu kana balubala wa Pilato, naba ana kusinga nji amu lukulule.  
\v 14 Kono kame mu na kukana uyu no kukena ni kuluka, mi kame muna kukumbela omwibai nji alukululwe.  
\v 15 Namukwibaa omunya moyo, woyo ana kwingula Nyambe kwaafu, mi aaci kame tuli etipaki no taba eyi.  
\v 16 Mi elitina lyaye, mulibaka no tumelo mu litina lyaye, na li ongota wuyu mulume woyo mu mona ni ku limuka mi ni tumelo mwa Jesu na ibalisa wino wuyu mulume balubala wenu moonje.”  
\v 17 “Cwale bano, abange, Kame ni limukile nji kame mutenda mukwalimuka, kanyi omo anaku tendala aendisi enu.  
\v 18 Kono eyo ana kwamba Nyambe ni tunwa no anuhi aye onje, nji Kilesite waye mba yanda, naiyatetetwe cwale.  
\v 19 Mubake cwale, mi musiuluke kame, nji eibi yenu ilemeniwe, enako eyo sakwiiye okuwetuluka sakutunde kwa Mbumu,  
\v 20 mi cwale kame sa tume Kilesite ona ketelwe aanyi, yonyene Jesu.  
\v 21 Woyo eliwilu kame lifanena okutambula okutwala enako eyo einu yonje abasa itendiwe eyino ubya eyo Nyambe ana kwamba ni tunwa no anuhi aye nokukena okutunda ku kale.  
\v 22 Mushe na kwamba nji, ‘Mbumu Nyambe mba tumu kwaanyi omunuhi okutunda kwaabenu kanyi omo anakuni tumena. Kame samu tetete kwa yonyene mu inu yonje eyo samiambele.  
\v 23 Mi kame sakutende nji omunu yonje woyo soulwa oku teteta kwa munuhi wa Nyambe mba sinyiwa okutunda kwaanu.’  
\v 24 Cwale anuhi a Nyambe onje aa anamba elin̄usa, okutunda kwa Samuele naa aneyi munyima, kame ana nuhu etinako eto.  
\v 25 Kame muli aana no anuhi a Nyambe ni ulikani owo Nyambe ana kuba kwanjekulyenu. Ana kwamba kwa Abulahama nji, ‘cwale mu lusika lowe aanu onje na ba litunga mba fuyauliwa.’  
\v 26 Nyambe nakutuma omubika waye kwaanyi oweli, okumi fuyola okufutula omunu yonje mwaanyi okutunda kuufokoli wenu.” 
\c 4  
\s1 Pitolosi ni Jowani aali booso no Kuta 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale alemine okwamba kwaanu, apulisita ni omukulu no atateleli no ndoo ya Nyambe na Saduki sebeli aiya kwa onyene.  
\v 2 Atinine kakuli kame ana kwiyetanga aanu ni kupaka mwa Jesu eyi no kwinguka kwaafu.  
\v 3 Cwale sebeli aanunga ni kwabeka mu tolongo okutwala ba liywaa linaku tatamako, kakuli neli amangolwaa.  
\v 4 Kono anokupula anakuyupa eliywi kame anaku pumena, mi epalo no aanu kame inaku kwana eikiti mutanu (5;000). 
\p  
\v 5 Eliywaa linaku tatamako abusisi oo na kulu, na iyeti no mulawo wa Mushe sebeli aungana mu Jelusalema.  
\v 6 Aali ni Anna omukulu no apulisita ni Kayafa, ni Jowani, ni Alekizanda, nanjili no lubasi no apulisita akulu.  
\v 7 Cwale aba ana kumana okwaimeka mukaci koo, sebeli aaibanguta nji, “Ka maata simba ka litina lya nyine mukutusisa okutendisa einu eyii?” 
\p  
\v 8 Cwale Pitolosi yo iyalile Emebo No Kukena, sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Abusi no aanu na kulu,  
\v 9 nji balelo kame twiibangutiwa okukumanena kweyi no kuwaba ina tendiwa ku mulume no sihole ni mumukwa ubine ana balisetwe,  
\v 10 ilimukiwe kwaanyi moonje naanu onje no Isilaele, nji mu litina lya Jesu Kilesite no Nazaleta, woyo munaku ngongotela ba sifapano, woyo Nyambe ana ingula kwaafu, mwa yonyene uyu mulume kame aimanine wino balubala wenu. 
\q1  
\v 11 ‘Eli eliwee muna kukana anyi ayaki 
\q2 kono kame lina futuka omutomo no muyako.’ 
\m  
\v 12 Cwale okuyoisisa kakusako ku munu yonje, kakuli kakwisa elitina linjili munji no liwilu eli libilwe kwaanu nji tuyoyiswe mwa lyonyene.” 
\p  
\v 13 Cwale aba ana mona oundume wa Pitolosi ni Jowani sebeli alemuha nji kaasiku kwiyeta, mi neli aanu feela alume no utokwa sebeli akomoka ni lemuha nji kame na kwikalanga ni Jesu.  
\v 14 Kono ba kumona omulume onaku balisiwa oimanine kunyonga yoo, sebeli aulwa nesi ana kwamba.  
\v 15 Kono cwale aba ana kumana okwaa laela nji atunde ba kuta, sebeli atangisa okwaambisa mu kaci koo nji,  
\v 16 “Iikene sa tutende kwaa alume?” Kakuli emakazo eyi ilimukiwa ina tendiwa kwa onyene kame inayupahala kwaanu onje aa ayakile mu Jelusalema, mi katu twese okwilatula.  
\v 17 Kono nji etaba eyi yulwe oku yupahala kwaanu, twaakanise onene okwamba kame ku munu yonje mu litina lya Jesu.” 
\p  
\v 18 Cwale sebeli aaisana ni kwaambela nji alese okwamba simba okwiyeta kame mu litina lya Jesu.  
\v 19 Kono Pitolosi ni Jowani sebeli aatambula nji, “Mu kwatule mwenyene nji kame kulukile mu miyo a Nyambe okumikuteka , aanyi mwatule.  
\v 20 Kakuli aaci katutwese okulesela okwamba eyi tuna mono neyi tuna yupu.”  
\v 21 Cwale aba ana kumana okwacilisa sebeli aalukulula nji akutele. Kasikuwana oufosi nji aabe ekoto, mulibakano aanu onje kame anaku lumbeka Nyambe kweyo inaku tendahala.  
\v 22 Kakuli omulume woyo inaku tendahalela emakazo no ku balisiwa kame ana kwikala ni myaka ibitelela makumi anee. 
\s1 Etapelo no Alumeli eyi no Undume 
\p  
\v 23 Cwale aba ana kumana oku lukululwa sebeli ata kwaa likani oo ni kwaambela eyo anaambele apulisita akulu na kulu.  
\v 24 Cwale aasikupumena aba ana kuyupa eyi, sebeli atumusa ku maywii oo onje oku lapela kwa Nyambe ni kwamba nji, Mbumu, wene ona uumbu eliwilu ni litunga ni liwate neyi ilimo!  
\v 25 Kame ona kwamba ni kanwa no mushemi wetu Dabida, omubika wowe, okwamba ni meyo no kukena nji, 
\q1 ‘Iikene amacaba aba atwebile, 
\q2 mi aanu ikene alelela eyi na mbulwa tuso? 
\q1  
\v 26 aambumu no litunga kame ana lumelelana, 
\q2 na endisi kame aku wanine bamweya 
\q2 okulwisa MBUMU ni ku lwisa Omuwabiwa waye.’ 
\m  
\v 27 Niti luli mu mumulenen̄i kame ana kukuwana bamweya okulwisa omubika no kukena woyo ona kuketa, onje Heloda ni Ponse Pilato na simacaba naanu no Isilaele.  
\v 28 Kame ana tende einu yonje eyi mu maata owe ni mulelo wowe eyo una kulela eyaka sitendahala kale, nji itendahale.  
\v 29 Cwale bano, Mbumu, omone emihupulo yoo, mi obe abika owe amaata no kwamba eliywi lyowe mu undume.  
\v 30 Cwale wolole elyoko lyowe oku balisa, mi etiponisa ni timakazo titendiwe mu litina lya Jesu omubika wowe no kukena.” 
\p  
\v 31 Cwale aba ana ku mana oku lapela, esibaka omo ana kukuwanena bamweya sebeli sizikinyeha. Mi oonje sebeli aiyala ni Mebo No kukena ni kwamba amaywi a Nyambe ni undume. 
\s1 Alumeli aba ana kukutabela Einu yoo 
\p  
\v 32 Cwale esikwata no aasikupumena sinakukuwana neli sa mucima ni mebo imweya. Kakwisa mukaci koo ona kwamba nji esinu ali naso nisaye yomboci, kono kame ana kuku tabelanga esinu akwite omukoo onje.  
\v 33 Cwale mu maata no kuneneba atumiwa ana kupaka onene okwinguka kwa Mbumu Jesu, mi esishemo sinene nasikwikala kwa onyene onje.  
\v 34 Kakwisa omunu ona kusinga esinjili mwa onyene. kakuli ano kupula awo anakwikala ni matema simba etindoo kame ana kuyulisanga, ni kulita amali nweso sina ulisiwa,  
\v 35 mi ni kusibeeka ku makondo no atumiwa, mi munu ni munu kame ana kutabelwanga omo asingela. 
\p  
\v 36 Cwale Josefa ona kwisaniwa kwa atumiwa nji Banabasi (okutalusa nji, “Omwana no susuwezo”), neli Mulibi, onaku leyelwa mu Saipulisi,  
\v 37 sebeli oulisa elitema lyaye, ni ku lita amali, ni kwabeeka ku makondo no atumiwa. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ananiasi ni Safila 
\p  
\v 1 Kono omulume wiisaniwa Ananiasi ni moywaye Safila sebeli aulisa esemba no litema lyoo.  
\v 2 Kono mu tingana no moyo waye sebeli oteulako amanjili amali awo anaku ulisako ni kulitako fela amanjili amali ni kwabeeka ku makondo no atumiwa.  
\v 3 Cwale Pitoosi sebeli wamba nji, “Ananiasi, ikene Satani aba ona mulumelele mu mucima wowe nji woonge Emebo No Kukena okuteulela ku mali ona ulisa elitema?  
\v 4 Abo owasiku ulisa kale elitema neli lyowe, mi naaba onamana okuli ulisa, amali asitendile owe. Kasa neli omuhupulo wowe? Iikene cwale ona tendele ngesi mu mucima wowe? Kausonga aanu, kono kame onaungo Nyambe!”  
\v 5 Cwale Ananiasi aba ana kuyupa amaywi aa, sebeli okwela banji ni kufa. Mi aanu onje ana kuyupa etaba eyi sebeli acila onene.  
\v 6 Andumbana sebeli aiya ni kufuka olutu lwaye ni kumutwala oka mu pumbeka. 
\p  
\v 7 Munyima no nako itenda etihola taatu moywaye sebeli okeela, yo kalimukile eyi ina tendahala.  
\v 8 Pitolosi sebeli omwibanguta nji, “Ona mbele nji kame muna ulisa elitema amali akuma aba?” 
\p Mi sebeli otamula nji, “Ee, banakumu.”  
\v 9 Kono Pitolosi sebeli wamba kwa yonyene nji, “Ngaibi muna lumelelana moonje okweteka Emebo no Mbumu? Omone, amakondo aawo anati muku pumbeka mbumowe aa okame ba mwelo, mi kame saku sakutwale ni wene!”  
\v 10 Ababo sebeli okwela banji ku makondo aye ni kufa, mi sebeli amushimba nukamu pumbeka ku nyonga ya mbumwaye.  
\v 11 Cwale okucila kunene sebeli kwingena kwaanu no ndoo ya Nyambe ni kwaanu onje anakuyupa etaba eyi. 
\s1 Etimakazo ni Tiponiso 
\p  
\v 12 Cwale etimakazo ni tiponiso no kupula kame tinaku tendahala kwaanu ni maoko no atumiwa. Mi kame ana kukuwanenga mu sibaka sinjili sa Salomoni siisaniwa nji Kozwana.  
\v 13 Kakwisa omunu onakutwesa oukuwana noo, kono aanu kame ana kwaalumba onene mulikute.  
\v 14 Cwale anokupula ana kupumena kwa Mbumu kame anakwekezeha, alume naakati.  
\v 15 Mane kame kuna litiwa asikutoma mu tindila ni kwalangeka ba mimbeta ni bamiseme nji Pitolosi abasabite anjili kwa onyene afukiwe ku mwinda waye.  
\v 16 Naanu kame sebeli akuwana okutunda mumindi mu Jelusalema, sebeli alita asikutoma nawo akwite Emebo nokwiiba, onje sebeli abalisiwa. 
\s1 Atumiwa abaana kuyandisiwa 
\p  
\v 17 Kono omupulisita omukulu bamweya nawo akuyupa naye onje na njili no Masaduki, sebeli ayupa omuna.  
\v 18 sebeli anunga atumiwa ni kwaabeka mu tolongo no sicaba.  
\v 19 Kono ousiku elin̄eloi lya Mbumu sebeli liiya mukuyatulula emwelo no tolongo nikwatundisamo ni kwamba nji,  
\v 20 “Mute mi mwimane mu ndoo ya Nyambe mi mwaambe kwaanu amaywi onje no moyo noubya.”  
\v 21 Mi cwale aba ana kuyupa eyi, sebeli aingena lilapa no ndoo ya Nyambe amasiku ni kwiyeta. Cwale omupulisita omukulu sebeli oiya naawo anakwikalanga naye ni kwisana bamweya ekuta naanu onje no Isilaele, ni kutumena ku tolongo mukwaalita.  
\v 22 Kono otupaso aba tunakukeela, kasitu kwaawana mu tolongo, mi sebeli tuuka kukuta okabiha,  
\v 23 “Natuwana etolongo iyatililwe wino natateleli aimanine ba mwelo, kono abatuna iyatulula katusiwanamo omunu mukaci!”  
\v 24 Cwale onduna no ndoo ya Nyambe napuliisita akulu aba ana kuyupa amaywi aa, sebeli aziyeleha ni kukomoka onene kweyo inatendahala kwa atumiwa, abilaela nji eyi taba ngasibine saitendahale.  
\v 25 Cwale sebeli kwiiya omunu ni kwaambela nji, “Alume munakubeka mu tolongo kame aimanine mu ndoo ya Nyambe mi kame aiyeta aanu!”  
\v 26 Cwale onduna ni tupaso sebeli ata okaashimba, kono kasa mukubambaba, kakuli kame ana kucila aanu okwakonda ni mawee. 
\p  
\v 27 Cwale aba anakumana okwaalita, sebeli aabeka balubala no Kuta, mi omukulu no mupulisita sebeli waibanguta nji,  
\v 28 “Natukumi laelela onene nji mulese okwiyeta mu litina lya Jesu, cwale bano namwiyata Jelusalema ni tuto yenu mi kame musinga okulita ounyinga no munu woyo beulu wetu!” 
\p  
\v 29 Kono Pitolosi naatumiwa sebeli atambula nji, “Kame tufanena okukuteka Nyambe, kasa omunu.  
\v 30 Onyambe no ashemi etu naingula Jesu kwaafu woyo muna kwibaa okumu ngongotela ba sitondo.  
\v 31 Nyambe nakumukulisa ni Lyoko lyaye no silyo nji atende omubusi ni muyoisi, woyo oba Isilaele okubaka ni kulemenwa eibi.  
\v 32 Kame tuli aapaki kwiinu eyi, mi kame tukwite Emebo nokukena eyo anabi Nyambe kwaao amukuteka.” 
\p  
\v 33 Cwale aba ana kuyupa eyi sebeli atina onene nikusinga okwaibaa.  
\v 34 Kono omufalisi munjili onakwisaniwa nji Gamaliele, omwiyeti no mulawo woyo olumbiwa ku sicaba sonje, sebeli oimana ni kulaelela nji aatumiwa atundisetwe bandee ba nako icana,  
\v 35 cwale sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Alume no Isilaele, mutokomele eyi musinga kutenda kwaa alume.  
\v 36 Kakuli munyima no maywaa aaTeudasi sebeli omonahala, nuukutoya nji nisinu sinene, mi aanu no kukwana emyanda inee sebeli akuwana naye, kono nakwibaiwa nawo onje anakumu kon̄anga sebeli ahasana ni kubwa.  
\v 37 Munyima ya woyo, Judasi omu Galileya sebeli omonahala mu nako no sipalo mi sebeli okoka aanu no kupula, kono ni yonyene sebeli ofa, mi naawo anakumu kon̄anga sebeli ahasana.  
\v 38 Cwalehe mu taba eyi, kame ni myambela nji, mutundeko kwalume aa mi mwasiye omboci, nji ni mulelo simba omusebezi otunda kwaanu, mbaukwangwa,  
\v 39 kono nji kame itunda kwa Nyambe, kamutamba okwatwesa. mba mumonahala nji naanyi kame mulwisa Nyambe.  
\v 40 Cwale sebeli asitokomela ekelezo yaye, mi cwale abana mana okwisana atumiwa, sebeli aashapa ni kwaalaela nji alese okuukela okwiyeta aanu mu Litina lya Jesu, sebeli aalukulula nji akutele.  
\v 41 Cwale sebeli asiya esibaka no Kuta awabelelwe, kakuli kame atendilwe aa alukela okwenisiwa mulibaka no Litina lya Jesu.  
\v 42 Mi amaywaa onje kasi kulesela okwiyeta mu Ndoo ya Nyambe ni mu tindoo nji Jesu yokame Kilesite. 
\c 6  
\s1 Atusi anaku kwana mutanu nayili 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale mu nako eyo epalo no aiyetwa abainakwekezeha, aendisi no Majuda ao aamba esigelike sebeli atongokela aendisi no Majuda ao aamba esihebelu kakuli neli ambelwa ao kame anakuketululwa abaku biwa eilya no liywaa ni liywaa. 
\p  
\v 2 Cwale atumiwa likumi nayili sebeli aisana aiyetwa onje ni kwaambela nji, “Kakulukele nji tulese okwiyeta eliywi lya Nyambe nji tube eiyi no kulya ba titafule.  
\v 3 Abetu, abakulingeso, mukete alume mutanu nayili mwaanyi aa asepahala aa aiyalile Emebo niku shangama, mi twabeke mu musebezi ou.  
\v 4 Kono aci mbatukongota muku lapela ni mu sebelezo no Liywi.” 
\p  
\v 5 Mi etaba eyo ana kwamba esikwata sonje sebeli siwabelelwa, mi sebeli aketa Setefani, omulume onaiyala etumelo ni Mebo No Kukena ni Filipi, ni Polokolasi, ni Nikolasi ni Timoni, ni Pamena, ni Nikolasi omupolosebelite na mu Antiyoke.  
\v 6 Esikwata esi sebeli asiimeka balubala no Atumiwa, sebeli alapela ni kwabeka amaoko oo beulu woo. 
\p  
\v 7 Cwale eliywi lya Nyambe sebeli lyekezeha okwambiwa, ni palo no aiyetwa sebeli yekezeha onene mu Jelusalema, mane ni palo no kupula no apulisita sebeli akubeeka ku tumelo. 
\s1 Okunungiwa kwa Setefani 
\p  
\v 8 Setefani ona kwiyala esishemo ni maata, sebeli otenda etimakazo ni tiponiso no kupula mu sicaba.  
\v 9 Cwale aanu anjili no ndoo no milapelo eyi isaniwa nji no alukuluhi, naa naku Sileni, naa naku Alekizandiya, naa naku tolopo no Silisia ni ku Asiya sebeli atangisa okukanana ni Setefani.  
\v 10 Kono sebeli akwangwa okukanana okushangama kwaye ni mebo eyo ana kwamba nayo.  
\v 11 Cwale sebeli ashonga alume anjili anakwamba nji, “Natumuyupu yo amba amaywi noku nyefula Mushe ni Nyambe!” 
\p  
\v 12 Sebeli asusuweza ngeso esicaba nakulu, naiyeti no mulawo wa Mushe, mi sebeli amupatisa okumulema niku mulita balubala no Kuta.  
\v 13 Sebeli alita apaki no mapwa ana kwamba nji, “Uyu mulume kalesele okwamba eyambo no ku nyefula endoo ya Nyambe ni mulawo wa Mushe.  
\v 14 Kakuli natumu yupu yo amba nji Jesu no Nazaleta wuyu mba sinyi esibaka eso, afutule ni mikwa no sizo eyi tunabiwi kwa Mushe!”  
\v 15 Aanu onje aa anakwikala ba Kuta aba ana kumulubukela, sebeli amona olubala lwaye nji kame lukufekile kanyi olubala no lin̄eloi. 
\c 7  
\s1 Omwambelo wa Setefani 
\p  
\v 1 Omupulisita omukulu sebeli wibanguta nji, “Etaba eyo kana moikalele?”  
\v 2 Setefani sebeli otambula nji, “Abaange, naanyi asitange, muyupetete kwa mene! Nyambe no kanya nakumonahaza kwa sitetu Abulahama abo yosiikala mu Mesopotamiya yokasita kale okaikala mu Halani,  
\v 3 mi sebeli wamba kwa yonyene nji, ‘Osiye esibaka sowe ni lusika lowe mi ote mu sibaka saniku monise.’  
\v 4 Cwale sebelli otunda mu naha no Makaladeya ni kuta okaikala mu Halani. Munyima ya sitaye Abulahama okufa, Nyambe sebeli omutundisamo niku mulita mu naha ino muyoya nibalelo lino.  
\v 5 Ka simuba esanda omo, simba esibaka no kulyata elikondo, kono sebeli omusepisa nji yonyene ni masika aye mbaabiwa esibaka simba nji kakwite omwana. 
\p  
\v 6 Cwale Nyambe sebeli omwambela nji, ‘Aikulyowe mba kayoyo mu naha no akoo omo sakaikale mu ukoba niku yandisiwa mu myaka nokukwana emyanda inee. (400)  
\v 7 Kono kame sani atule aanu saabeeke mu ubika Nyambe sebeli wamba, mi munyima nweyo kame satundemo ni kwiya mukuni lumbekela muno mu sibaka.’  
\v 8 Cwale Nyambe sebeli omuba oulikani no mupato. Mi cwale Abulahama sebeli oleya Isaka, ni kumubeeka ku mupato ba liywaa no mutanu ni twaatu, mi Isaka sebeli oleya Jakobo, Jakobo sebeli oleya anjekulyetu nokukwana likumi ni twiili. 
\p  
\v 9 Kakuli anjekulyetu kame ana kufela minoo Josefa omuna niku muulisa mu Engepita, kono Nyambe nakwikala naye,  
\v 10 mi sebeli omulamulela mu mayando aye onje niku muba okukateleha ni kushangama, balubala wa Falo Ombumu no Engepita woyo onaku muba oubusisi no Engepita ni beulu no asindoo yaye yonje. 
\p  
\v 11 Cwale sebeli kwiiya olukupwe munaha yonje no Engepita ni mu Kanana, ni mayando manene mane na shemi etu sebeli akwangwa oku wana eilya.  
\v 12 Kono cwale Jakobo aba ana kuyupa eyo nji kame kuli eilya mu Engepita, sebeli otumako anjekulyetu akano weli. 
\p  
\v 13 Ba musipili no wiili Josefa sebeli okulimukisa kwakulwaye, mi olusika lwa Josefa sebeli lulimukiwa kwa Falo  
\v 14 Cwale Josefa sebeli otuma aanu okashimba sitaye Jokobo ni lusika lwaye lonje, anakukwana makumi mutanu na yili naanu mutanu (75).  
\v 15 Cwale Jakobo sebeli ota ku Engepita, nukafelako yonyene na njekulyetu.  
\v 16 Eitupu yoo kame inaku twaliwa mu Shekemu nukateuliwa mu libita anaku ula Abulahama ni mali kwaana aa Homoli namu Shekemu. 
\p  
\v 17 “Kono enako no sepiso aba inaku sheteta, eyo Nyambe anaku sepisa Abulahama epalo no aanu mu Egepita sebeli yekezeha onene.  
\v 18 Mane sebeli kuyola Ombumu munjili mu Engepita woyo nokwa limuka Josefa.  
\v 19 Woyo sebeli otenda omushobo wetu mu kushangama no kwiiba, na kuyandisa anjekulyetu, sebeli wataukisa anoo nji alese okupula afee.  
\v 20 Munako eyi Mushe sebeli oleiwa, neli omwana no kuwaba onene balubala wa Nyambe. Mi kame anaku litiwa ba tikweti taatu mu ndoo ya sitaye,  
\v 21 mi ababo yosi limukiwa fela, mwanaye Falo no musizana sebeli okutolelaye, ni ukukuliseta ye nji atende mwanaye luli.  
\v 22 Cwale Mushe sebeli oiyetiwa okushangama konje no Aengepita mi sebeli oikala ni maata mu kwamba ni mu misebezi. 
\p  
\v 23 “Cwale aba ana kukwanisa emyaka makumi anee (40), sebeli oiyelwa etakazo mu mucima waye nokuta oka potela abaye aana no Isilaele.  
\v 24 Cwale sebeli omona omunjili no abaye yo tendiwa ouyi, sebeli omulwela, okumu lamulela mukwibaa Omuegepita.  
\v 25 Nakuyambuta nji abaye kame sa yupisise nji Nyambe kame saayoyise mulibaka no Lyoko lyaye, kono kaasikuyupisisa.  
\v 26 Cwale liywaa linaku tatamako sebeli omumonahaza kwaonyene aalwa mi sebeli waaeleza nji, ‘Alume, kame muli omwabaye munu, iikene aba mukulwisa?’  
\v 27 Kono omulume woyo onakutenda omukwaye ouyi sebeli okasha Mushe, ni kumwibanguta nji, ‘Anyine onaku beeke omubusisi ni mwatuli wetu?’  
\v 28 ‘Kame usinga okunibaa kanyi omo unakwibaela Omuegepita bingolwa?’  
\v 29 Mulibaka no liywi elyo, Mushe sebeli otunda mu Engepita okuta mu naha no Mindiyani, omo anokaleyelamo aana ayili. 
\p  
\v 30 Cwale aba kuna mana emyaka makumi anee (40), elin̄eloi sebeli likumonahaza kwa Mushe mu lihalaupa no lilundu no Sinai, mu lulimi no mulilo mu liputa.  
\v 31 Cwale Mushe aba anakumona ngeso sebeli okomoka, abana shetetako nji amonisise, sebeli oyupa eliywi lya Mbumu elyamba nji,  
\v 32 ‘Time Nyambe wa njekulyowe, Nyambe wa Abulahama Nyambe wa Isaka ni wa Jakobo.’ Cwale Mushe sebeli ocila ni kukwangwa okwaliketako.  
\v 33 Cwale MBUMU sebeli wamba kwa yonyene nji, ‘Otundise etinjangwa towe ku makondo, kakuli esibaka wimanine ni sakukena.  
\v 34 Kame ninalikete mi kame nimono amayando no aanu ange mu Egepita mi nuyupu okutonga koo, mi kame nineyi mukwaa lukulula. Cwale wiiye, niku tume ku Egepita.’ 
\p  
\v 35 “Mushe woyo ana kukana aamba nji, ‘Anyine ona kubeeke omubusisi ni mwatuli?’ Yokame ana beeke Nyambe omubusisi ni mulukululi woo mulibaka no lingeloi linaku monahala mu liputa. 
\p  
\v 36 Sebeli watundisa mu Egepita, yo tenda etimakazo neyi ikomokisa ni ba liwate no mucaa ni mu lihalaupa emyaka makumi anee (40).  
\v 37 Mushe yokame onakwambela aana no Isilaele nji, ‘Nyambe wenu mba mi litele omunuhi mukaci no abenu kanyi omo ana kuni beekela.’  
\v 38 Yokame woyo onakukuwana mu lihalaupa ni lingeloi linakwamba kwa yonyene ku lilundu lya Sinai, yoli na njekulyetu, ni ku tambula amaywi a yoyisa nji atube oo. 
\p  
\v 39 Kono anjekulyetu sebeli akana okumukuteka, kono sebeli amukuteka ku nyonga mu micima yoo ni kuukela ku Engepita.  
\v 40 Cwale sebeli aamba kwa Aluni nji,‘Otutendele emilimu eyi itwenda ku lubala, kanyi Mushe woyo onaku tutwaletela okutunda mu naha no Egepita, katu limukile esi sinamwiyele.’  
\v 41 Cwale mu maywaa awo sebeli aumba onamani, ni kutundiseta etinubu esiswaniso eso ni ku wabelelwa mu misebezi no maoko oo.  
\v 42 Kono Nyambe sebeli wafutukela ni kwaaba oku lapelela empi nakuwilu, kanyi omo kun̄olelwe mu buka no anuhi nji, 
\q1 ‘Anyi asi ndoo no Isilaele, 
\q2 ninji kame munaku nilitela eiyamana no kuyonda ni matabelo, 
\q2 emyaka inee mu lihalaupa. 
\q1  
\v 43 Cwale kame munakushimba Endoo ya Nyambe ya Muloke, 
\q2 ni lutungweti lwa Nyambe Lefani, 
\q2 neli amaswaniso munakukuketela okulapelela 
\q1 Cwale kame sanimitundise mu Babilona.’ 
\p  
\v 44 “Anjekulyetu nakwikala ni tabanakele no upaki mu lihalaupa, simba kanyi woyo ona kwamba kwa Mushe nakumu laelela yonyene ona kwitenda, kanyi esiswaniso eso anaku mona.  
\v 45 Munyima anjekulyetu sebeli aiya mu naha ni Joshuwa ku sicaba anakucita Nyambe balubala wa anjekulyetu. Sebeli iikalamo okutwala ba maywaa a Dabida.  
\v 46 Dabida naku wana esishemo kwa Nyambe mi sebeli okumbela nji awanene Nyambe wa Jakobo esibaka.  
\v 47 Kono neli Solomoni ona kumuyakela endoo.  
\v 48 Kono Nyambe Omwambakani ka ikala mu tindoo tina yakiwa ni maoko, kanyi omunuhi aba anakwamba nji, 
\q1  
\v 49 ‘Eliwilu lyokame olubona lwange, 
\q2 mi elitunga lyokame esipula nilyatile amakondo ange 
\q1 Mufuta ubine no ndoo muniyakela, kame kwamba MBUMU, 
\q2 kamba kasibaka eso ni fanena oku pumulela? 
\q1  
\v 50 Kasanji amaoko ange kasikuyaka einu yonje eyi?’ 
\p  
\v 51 “Anyi anu no tindingo tisatalalile, aa ulwile okwingenyeka emicima ni matwi yenu mu mupato, enako yonje kame mukanisa Emebo No Kukena! Kanyi omo ana kwikalela anjekulyenu, naanyi momwikalele.  
\v 52 Anyine omunuhi wasiku yandisiwa kwa njekulyenu? mane kame anakwibaa awo anakwamba baweli nji kame sakwiye woyo no kuluka. Cwale woyo muna kubeteka niku mwibaa.  
\v 53 Aanyi munaku tambula omulawo wa Nyambe onaku lukululwa ku mangeloi kono kamusi kuuteula. 
\s1 Okupwacauliwa kwa Setefani 
\p  
\v 54 Cwale aba ana kuyupa einu eyi sebeli atina, ni kukweca amaeo okumu lwisa.  
\v 55 Kono Setefani, yo iyalile Emebo No Kukena, sebeli omona ekanya ya Nyambe ni Jesu yoimanine ku Lyoko no silyo lya Nyambe.  
\v 56 Cwale sebeli wamba nji, “Komumone, kame nimona eliwilu eli liyatulukile ni Mwana no munu yoimanine kweli no silyo lya Nyambe!” 
\p  
\v 57 Cwale sebeli akuwa ni liywi linene ni kutika amatwi oo ni kwitukela kwa yonyene onje,  
\v 58 niku mukokela kundee no mulenen̄i niku mupwacula ni mawee. Etipaki sebeli abeeka eikumango yoo banji, ba makondo no ndumbana wisaniwa Saule.  
\v 59 Cwale alemine okupwacaula Setefani, sebeli olapela nji, “Mbumu Jesu otambule Emebo yange!”  
\v 60 Cwale sebeli okubama ni kukuwa ni liywi linene nji, “Mbumu, olese okwahupulela esibi sino!” Aba ana mana ngeso, sebeli okulanganena. 
\c 8  
\p  
\v 1 Saule naku pumena olufu lwa Setefani. 
\s1 Saule yo yandisa Ekeleke 
\p Cwale ba liywaa elyo sebeli kwinguka okuyandisiwa kunene mu Ndoo ya Nyambe mu Jelusalema, mi onje kame anakuhasanela mu naha no Judeya ni Samaliya sebeli kusiyala fela Atumiwa omboci.  
\v 2 Alume anjili no aasikupumena sebeli ata oka pumbeka Setefani, niku mulila onene. 
\p  
\v 3 Kono Saule sebeli otateka okusisinya Endoo ya Nyambe, ni kwingena mu tindoo okukokamo alume na kati ni kwaaingenyeka mu tolongo. 
\s1 Eliywi no Kuwaba sebeli likutaziwa mu Samaliya 
\p  
\v 4 Cwale awo anaku hasanyiwa sebeli ata alemine okukutaza eliywi.  
\v 5 Filipi sebeli ota mu mulenen̄i no Samaliya, nukaamba eyi ya Kilesite kwa onyene.  
\v 6 Aanu nokupula sebeli aikala ni mucima mumweya okutambula eyo anakwamba Filipi, Cwale sebeli amuyupa nikumona etimakazo ana kutende.  
\v 7 Kakuli Emebo no kwiiba sebeli inakutunda mwaanu nokupula awo anakwingeniwa yolemine okukuwa ni liywi linene, naanu asikukutela olun̄an̄ali ni iyanga no makondo sebeli abalisiwa.  
\v 8 Cwale okuwabelelwa noku neneba sebeli kwikalamo omo mu mulenen̄i. 
\s1 Simoni onganga 
\p  
\v 9 Kono oweli kame kunakwikala omulume onakwisaniwa Simoni onakutendanga amabibo mu tolopo no Samaliya onaku komokisanga esicaba, yonyene kame ana kukyemanga nji munu nokuneneba,  
\v 10 mi onje kame anaku mukutekanga, okutangisa ku mwanukana okutwala ku mukulu, sebeli aamba nji, “Uyu mulume ni maata a Nyambe awo aisanwa nji, ‘Amaata no kuneneba.’”  
\v 11 Kame anaku mukolwa kakuli naku tangisa kale okwakomokisa ni mabibo aye.  
\v 12 Kono aba anaku pumena Filipi aba anakwaambela eliywi no kuwaba no muboso wa Nyambe ni litina lya Jesu Kilesite onje alume nakati sebeli akolobeziwa.  
\v 13 Simba yonyene Simoni naku pumena, mi munyima no ku kolobeziwa sebeli okumalela Filipi, mi aba mona etimakazo neyi ikomokisa, sebeli okomoka. 
\p  
\v 14 Cwale atumiwa ku Jelusalema abaana kuyupa nji amasamaliya kame anatambula eliywi lya Nyambe, sebeli atuma Pitolosi ni Jowani.  
\v 15 Awo abaana kukeela sebeli aalapelela nji abiwe Emebo No Kukena.  
\v 16 Kakuli Emebo No Kukena kaya siku shulumukela simba ku mumweya kwa onyene, kono kame anaku kolobeziwa fela mu litina lya Mbumu Jesu.  
\v 17 Cewale sebeli abeka amaoko oo beulu yoo mi sbeli atambula Emebo No Kukena. 
\p  
\v 18 Cwale Simoni aba aaku mona nji Emebo kame inabiwi mukubeka amaoko no atumiwa, sebeli waasepisa okwaba amali,  
\v 19 ni kwamba nji, “Munibe ku maata awo, nji omunu yonje sanibeeke amaoko mba tambula Emebo No Kukenaa.” 
\p  
\v 20 Kono Pitolosi sebeli omwambela nji, “Amali owe ofe nawo, kakuli kame onahana nji kame ofanena okula empo ya Nyambe ni mali!  
\v 21 Kakwisa esi sobiwe simba esemba, mu taba eyo, kakuli omucima wowe kausiluka mu miyo a Nyambe.  
\v 22 Obake mu uyi wowe, mi olapele Nyambe, mwendi mbufanene okulemenwa omuhupulo oli mu mucima wowe.  
\v 23 Kakuli kame ni mona nji kame oli mu mioti no kulula onene ni mu tolongo no sibi.” 
\p  
\v 24 Simoni sebeli otambula nji, “Muni lapelele kwa Nyambe, nji kakwisa esinjili kweyo mu naamba sasini kwele.” 
\p  
\v 25 Cwale aba anakumana okupaka eliywi lya Nyambe, sebeli aukela ku Jelusalema, okakutaza eliywi no kuwaba kwaanu no kupula no masamaya. 
\s1 Filipi ni Nduna no Muisopiya 
\p  
\v 26 Kono elin̄eloi lya Mbumu sebeli lyambela Filipi nji, “Oimane mi ote ku Mbowela, ku ndila ishetumuka ku Jelusalema okuta ku Gaza, no lihalaupa, eyo nokwa endiwangwa.”  
\v 27 Cwale sebeli oimana ni kutako, sebeli omona omulume no muisopiya, neli muumba, esikombwa sinene sa Kandasi, Ombumu no mukati no isopiya, neli omubabaleli no ufumu waye onje, neyi mu Jelusalema muku lapela  
\v 28 mi muku ukela kwaawo yoikalile mu koloi yaye yo lemine okubala mu buka no munuhi Isaya  
\v 29 Emebo No Kukena sebeli yamba kwa Filipi nji, “Otwalelelele, oshetete ku koloi eyi.”  
\v 30 Cwale Filipi sebeli oitukela kwa yonyene, niku muyupa yobala mu buka no munuhi Isaya, ni kumwibanguta nji, “Kame uyupa eyo olemine okubala?” 
\p  
\v 31 Onduna sebeli otambula nji, “Ngasibine sani yupisise, okuulwile omunu onisimweta?” mi sebeli omema Filipi okutina nji aikale naye.  
\v 32 Cwale ekalulo no lin̄olo anaku bala neli eyi, 
\q1 “Kanyi omukoko utwaliwa mukwiibaiwa 
\q2 simba akana no mukoko nokwalila owoya wako aba upatuliwa, 
\q2 kasi yaamisa akanwa kaye. 
\q1  
\v 33 Mu kwenisiwa, mi ekatulo yaye sebeli iimekiwa. 
\q2 Anyine sotwesa okwa olusika lwaye, 
\q2 kakuli omoyo waye nautundisiwa mu litunga.” 
\p  
\v 34 Cwale onduna sebeli oibanguta Filipi nji, “Onambele, kame ni kulapela, omunuhi aba aamba eyi, kame akwamba yonyene nji kame aamba omunjili?”  
\v 35 Cwale Filipi sebeli oyamisa akanwa kaye ni kutangisa nelyo elin̄olo okumwambela amaywi no kuwaba a Jesu.  
\v 36 Cwale alemine okuta mu ndila sebeli awana abakuli ameyi, mi onduna sebeliwamba nji, “Omone, bano kame kuli ameyi. sikene esi sasini kanise oku kolobeziwa?”  
\v 37 Filipi sebeli wamba nji, “Nji kame opumena ni mucima wowe wonje, kame kukonahala. Nduna sebeli otambula nji, Kame ni pumena nji Jesu Kilesite ni Mwanaa Nyambe.” 
\p  
\v 38 Onduna sebeli olaelela ekoloi okwimana, onje Filipi ni Nduna sebeli aingena mu meyi, mi Filipi sebeli kolobeza onduna.  
\v 39 Cwale aba anakutunda mu meyi, Emebo ya Nyambe sebeli ishimba Filipi, mi onduna nakuulwa okumona Filipi kame, cwale sebeli otwalelela mu mwendo waye yo wabelelwe.  
\v 40 Kono Filipi nokakuwana mu Azoto, yo twalelela okukutaza eliywi no kuwaba mu titolopo tonje mane sebeli okakeela ku Sizeliya. 
\c 9  
\s1 Okufutuka kwa Saule 
\r (Tikezo22.6-16; 26.12-18) 
\p  
\v 1 Kono Saule yosi tukufalile okufumbela okwibaa aiyetwa no Mbumu, sebeli ota ku mupulisita omukulu  
\v 2 oka kumbela kwa yonyene aman̄olo no kuta nawo mu tindoo no milapelo naku Damaseka, nji abasa kawane anjili asi Ndila eyo, alume simba akati, aanunge ni kwalita mu Jelusalema. 
\p  
\v 3 Cwale Saule yo atumele okukeela ku Damaseka, ababo olumonyi lunaku tunda ku wilu sebeli lumubeeka mukaci.  
\v 4 Cwale sebeli okwela banji ni kuyupa eliywi elyaamba kwa yonyene nji, “Saule, Saule, iikene oniyandiseta?” 
\p  
\v 5 Sebeli oibaguta nji, “Tiwe anyine, Mbumu?” Mbumu sebeli wamba nji, 
\p “Time Jesu woyo oyandisa.”  
\v 6 “Cwale winguke oingene mu mulenen̄i, mi mbuka simwetiwamo eyo so fanene okutenda.” 
\p  
\v 7 Alume anakwenda naye kame anakwimana ni kukomoka, kakuli kame anaku yupa eliywi kono kaasiku mona omunu.  
\v 8 Saule sebeli oinguka banji mi cwale amiyo aye abaana kutona nakukwangwa okumona omunu, cwale sebeli amulema ku Lyoko niku mulita mu Damaseka.  
\v 9 Mu maywaa aatu yoka mono, ni kulya simba okunwa. 
\p  
\v 10 Cwale kame kuna kwikala omwiyetwa mu Damaseka no litina lya Ananiasi. Ombumu sebeli omwambela mu pono nji, “Ananiasi.” mi sebeli otambula nji, “Yamene yauno, Mbumu.” 
\p  
\v 11 Ombumu sebeli omwambela nji, “Oimane mi ote mu ndila isaniwa nji eyi noku luka, okasaele mu ndoo ya Judasi omulume naku Tasusi no litina lya Saule. Kakuli kame alapela,  
\v 12 mi ni yonyene namono omulume wisaniwa Ananiasi mu pono yoiya niku beeka amaoko aye beulu yaya nji cwale amone kame.” 
\p  
\v 13 Kono Ananiasi sebeli otambula nji, “Mbumu, kame nina yupu ya uyu omulume kwaanu nokupula eyi ana tende, omo ana yandisete ouyi aasikupumena owe mu Jelusalema.  
\v 14 Naaba aneyi kuno, kame ana biwi amaata okutunda kwa apulisita akulu ni kununga onje aa alapela elitina lyowe.” 
\p  
\v 15 Kono Ombumu sebeli omwambela nji, “Ote, kakuli kame ninamukete okutenda esibelekiso sange nji atwale Elitina lyange kwaa simacaba na Mbumu naana no Isilaele.  
\v 16 Cwale kame sanimu simwete okuneneba no kukola oko sayupe mulibaka no kuyandisa elitina lyange.” 
\p  
\v 17 Cwale Ananiyasi sebeli ota nuka ingena mu ndoo ni kubeeka amaoko aye beulu yaye ni kwamba nji, “Minange Saule, Ombumu onaku monahaza kwa wene mu ndila nani tumu, yonyene Jesu nji omone kame mi wiyale Emebo No Kukena.”  
\v 18 Cwale ababo esinu sikufekile kanyi amayayu sebeli situnda mu miyo aye ni kumona kame. Cwale sebeli oimana ni kukolobeziwa.  
\v 19 Cwale sebeli olya ni kuukeliwa amaata 
\s1 Saule yo Kutaza mu Damaseka 
\p Saule sebeli oikala naiyetwa mu Damaseka amaywaa acana.  
\v 20 Mu ndoo no milapelo ababo sebeli okutaza nji Jesu ni Mwanaa Nyambe. 
\p  
\v 21 Onje anaku muyupa sebeli akomoka ni kwibanguta nji, “Kasa yokame onaku yandisanga ouyi anaku isananga ba litina Jesu mu Jelusalema? mane mulibaka elyo bokame aba aneyi kuno, mukwaanunga ni kwatwala kwa apulisita akulu?” 
\p  
\v 22 Kono Saule sebeli oekeza onene mu kongola kwaye, ni kukoma aendisi no Majuda okwamonisa nji Jesu yokame Kilesite. 
\p  
\v 23 Cwale amaywaa nokupula abaanakubwa, amajuda sebeli asinganyeka okwibaa Saule,  
\v 24 kono Saule sebeli olimuka omulelo woo. kame anaku mundamenanga munji ni ousiku ku myelo nji amwibae.  
\v 25 Kono aiyetwa aye sebeli amushimba ousiku oku mumatukiseta ba limota, amubekile mu litanda. 
\s1 Saule yoli mu Jelusalema 
\p  
\v 26 Saule aba ana kukeela mu Jelusalema sebeli weteka nji akuwane naiyetwa, mi onje kame anaku mucila, kakuli kasiku pumena nji niyonyene neli omwiyetwa.  
\v 27 Kono Banabasi sebeli omushimba, ni kumu twala kwa atumiwa, ni kwataluseta omo anaku monena Ombumu mu ndila, woyo ona kwamba naye, nomo ana kutaleze ni maata mu Damaseka mu litina lya Jesu.  
\v 28 Cwale Saule sebeli oyoya noo mane nikukwendela oomo anakusingela mu Jelusalema,  
\v 29 yo kutaza mukuzwafisa mu litina lya Mbumu, ni kwamba muku kanana ni Majuda ao aamba esi Gelike onyene aafumba okumwibaa.  
\v 30 Cwale abaye aba anakuyupa eyo, sebeli alita Saule kwa Sesaaliya, ni kumu fundula okuta ku Tasusi. 
\p  
\v 31 Cwale etikeleke monje mu Judeya ni mu Galileya ni mu Samaliya sebeli tiikala mu kozo, ni kweenda mu kucila kwa Mbumu, mi kame tina kukula ni kususeziwa mu tuso no Mebo No Kukena. 
\s1 Pitolosi yoli mu Lida ni mu Joppa 
\p  
\v 32 Pitolosi yo lemine okupotela eibaka yonje no naha, sebeli oiya ni kwa asikupumena aa ayakile mu Lida.  
\v 33 Omo sebeli okawana omulume no Litina lya Aneya, woyo onaku langana ba mumbeta yokola oweti no lun̄an̄ali mu myaka mutanu ni twaatu (8).  
\v 34 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli wamba kwa yonyene nji, “Aneya, Jesu Kilesite kame akubalisa, oshimbe oulangano wowe.” Ababo Aneya sebeli oinguka.  
\v 35 Onje aa ayakile mu Lida ni Shaloni naku mumona, mi sebeli asiulukela kwa Mbumu. 
\p  
\v 36 Mu Jopa kame kuna kwikala omuiyetwa no mukati elitina lyaye neli Tabita, (okutalusa nji Dokasi) Kame ana kutendanga emisebezi no kuwaba ni tituso.  
\v 37 Mu maywaa ao sebeli okola ni kufa. Cwale aba anakumana okumu yowisa, sebeli akamu beeka mu musiyo na kuwilu.  
\v 38 Lida kakuli kame ina kwikala beebi ni Jopa, aiyetwa sebeli ayupa nji Pitolosi kwaali, sebeli atuma alume ayili okamu kumbela nji, “Shangwe, ulese ku liyeha wiye kwaaci.”  
\v 39 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli oinguka nikuta noo. Aba anaku keela, sebeli amutwala ku musiyo na kuwilu, etimbelwa tonje sebeli tiimana ku nyonga yaye alemine okulila, nikumu monisa eikumango ni misisi anaku tendanga Dokasi yo siyoya noo.  
\v 40 Kono Pitolosi sebeli watundiseta bandee onje, sebeli okubama ni manwi banji ni kulapela, cwale nikusiulukela ku situpu ni kwamba nji, “Tabita, oinguke!” sebeli otona, mi aba anaku mona Pitolosi sebeli oikala.  
\v 41 Pitolosi sebeli omulema ku Lyoko okumwimeka. Cwale sebeli oisana etimbelwa naa asikupumena ni kwaaba Tabita yo yoya.  
\v 42 Etaba eyo sebeli ilimukiwa kwaanu onje mu Jopa, mi anokupula sebeli apumena kwa Mbumu.  
\v 43 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli oikala mu Jopa amaywaa nokupula ku mulume oisaniwa Simoni, omusuhi no itumba. 
\c 10  
\s1 Pitolosi ni Koneliyasi 
\p  
\v 1 Mu Sesaaliya, kame kuna kwikala omulume no litina lya Koneliyasi, omukulu no masole, no mpi iisaniwa nji, “Italiya.”  
\v 2 Neli omunu ona kukubeeka ni kucila Nyambe nia sindoo yaye onje, kame ana kutusanga onene anokusheba mi kame ana kulapelanga enako yonje kwa Nyambe.  
\v 3 Ba nako no waatu omunji sebeli omona wino mu pono elin̄eloi lya Nyambe eliiya kwa yonyene ni kwamba nji, “Koneliyasi!” 
\p  
\v 4 Cwale Koneliyasi sebeli waliketa elin̄eloi mukucila ni kwamba nji, “Etaba ni ibine, Mbumu?” 
\p Elin̄eloi sebeli limu tambula nji, “Etitapelo ni tituso towe kwawo ashebile nati kambamene kwa Nyambe, mi natipulukiwa.  
\v 5 Cwale otume alume ku Jopa akashimbe Simoni woyo oisaniwa Pitolosi.  
\v 6 Kame ali ni Simoni omusuhi no itumba, endoo yaye kame ikubapile ni liwate.”  
\v 7 Cwale elin̄eloi lina kwamba naye aba linakuta, sebeli oisana abika aye ayili ni musole mumweya woyo ona kukubeeka kwa Nyambe kwawo ana ku mutatelelanga.  
\v 8 Munyima ya Koneliyasi okwaambela eyi inatendahala yonje sebeli waatuma ku Jopa. 
\s1 Epono ya Pitolosi 
\p  
\v 9 Eliywaa linaku tatamako, awo asili mu ndila, aali beebi ni Jopa, Pitolosi sebeli otina ba situwa no ndoo oka lapela, ba nako aba ina kukwana likumi ni twiili (12) omunji.  
\v 10 Pitolosi sebeli oyomba ni kusaela esino kulya, aasilemine okumu lukiseta eilya, sebeli omona epono.  
\v 11 Cwale sebeli omona eliwilu liyatuluka ni sinu siiya banji kanyi olwambi lunene lunungilwe ku mamaneneno yalo anee.  
\v 12 Mukaci yalo kame kuna kwikala emifuta yonje no iyamana neyi yenda ni mapumo ni tuyunyi na kuwilu.  
\v 13 Cwale eliywi sebeli liiya kwa yoyene lyaamba nji, “Imana, Pitolosi, wibae mi olye!” 
\p  
\v 14 Kono Pitolosi sebeli wamba nji, “Kokulwa, Mbumu, kakuli kanisilya kale esinu sonje no kwakena neyo no litilo.” 
\p  
\v 15 Eliywi sebeli liiya kwa yonyene kame akano wili nji, “Esi sikenisitwe kwa Nyambe, olese okwamba nji nisaalitilo.”  
\v 16 Nakuku tendahala ngeso twaatu, esinu eso sebeli susetwa ku wilu. 
\p  
\v 17 Pitolosi yosi nahana epono ana mono nji iikene, komumone, alume ana tumiwa kwa Koneliyasi munyima no kwibanguta ku ndoo ya Simoni sebeli akeela ni kwimana ba mwelo.  
\v 18 Cwale sebeli aisana ni kwibanguta nji, “Kana mokame muno ana tibelele Simoni wisaniwa Pitolosi?” 
\p  
\v 19 Pitolosi yo sinahana eyi no pono eyo, Emebo sebeli yamba kwa yonyene nji, “Omone, alume aatu kame akusaela.  
\v 20 Wimane mi oshetumuke, ote noo oulwile oku lindalinda, kakuli time ninaa tumu.”  
\v 21 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli oshetumukela kwaao alume ana tumeniwa kwa yonyene ni kwamba nji, “Yamene mu saela. Mulibaka libine aba muneeyi?” 
\p  
\v 22 Cwale sebeli atambula nji, “Koneliyasi, omukulu no masole, kuluka, woyo ocila Nyambe ni kukutekiwa ku sicaba sonje no Majuda. Kame ana laeliwa ku lingeloi no kukena okwisanena ku ndoo yaye, nji ayupe eyo so wambe.”  
\v 23 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli waatambula ni kwaingenyeka mu ndoo. 
\s1 Pitolosi ku ndoo ya Koneliyasi 
\p Eliywaa linaku tatamako Pitolosi sebeli ota noo, nanjili abaye namu Jopa sebeli ata naye.  
\v 24 Kweeli linaku tatamako eliywaa sebeli aingena mu Sesaaliya. Koneliyasi kame anakwa atatelela, mane kame anakwisana bamweya aa asinga onene naabaye.  
\v 25 Cwale Pitolosi aba anakwingena, Koneliyasi sebeli omuwaniketa niku kwela banji ni manwi ku makondo aye niku mukubamena.  
\v 26 Kono Pitolosi sebeli omwimeka ni kwamba nji, “Imana,” “Nimene, kame nili omunu fela.”  
\v 27 Pitolosi yo ambola ni Koneliyasi, sebeli aingena mu ndoo ni kuwanamo aanu nokupula aunganine.  
\v 28 Pitolosi sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Aanyi kame mulimukile nji ni kulwisa omulawo omunu kakuli o Mujuda kalukele okuwana nasimacaba andina simba okulekula omunjili kwa yonyene. Kono Nyambe nanikete nji nilese okwaliketa omunu yonje nji kame aiyalile elitilo kasikena.  
\v 29 Cwale aba nina kutumeniwa, kame nineyi nambulwa mukwakana. Cwale kame nimi ibanguta nji, iikene munani isanene?” 
\p  
\v 30 Koneliyasi sebeli otambula nji, “Kwabita kale amaywaa anee, Kame naikalanga mundoo yange me nilapela omunji ba nako no waatu (15:00) mi sebeli nimona omulume onaku manga eikumango no kubenya yo imanine balubala wange  
\v 31 ni kwamba nji, ‘Koneliyasi okulapela kowe naku yupahala mi ni tituso towe na tihupuliwa kwa Nyambe.  
\v 32 Cwale otumene ku Jopa mi okaisane Simoni no litina lya Pitolosi, kame ali mu ndoo ya Simoni osikusuha eitumba, eyi ili beebi ni liwate.’  
\v 33 Cwale bokame aba nina leluba ookutumena, mi nutende wino aba uneyi. Cwale tonje kame tuli bamweya balubala wa Nyambe, oku yupa eyo ona laelwe yonje kwa Mbumu okutwambela.” 
\s1 Engambolo Ya Pitolosi 
\p  
\v 34 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli oyatulula akanwa kaye ni kwamba nji, “Niti luli kame nilemuha nji Nyambe kakete omunu omo aikalele.  
\v 35 Kono mu sicaba ni sicaba munu yonje woyo omucila ni kutenda eyi ilukile, kame alumelelwa kwa yonyene.  
\v 36 Kame mulimukile elin̄usa anaku tuma kwaana a Isilaele, okwa kutaza eliywi no kuwaba no kozo ya Jesu Kilesite Ombumu no aanu onje.  
\v 37 Kame mulimukile eyo ineyi mu Judeya monje eyi inaku tangisa mu Galileya munyima ya Jowani oku kutaza ei no kolobezo.  
\v 38 Kame mulimukile Nyambe omo anaku wabela Jesu wa Nazaleta ni Mebo no Kukena ni maata, ao anaku tendisa einu no kuwaba niku balisa aanu onje awo anakwi kalanga munji no maata a Satani, kakuli Nyambe kame ana kwikala naye.  
\v 39 Cwale kame tuli apaki kwiinu yonje anaku tenda bamweya mu naha no Majuda ni mu Jelusalema. Kame ana mwibaa, okumu tuleka.  
\v 40 Kono Nyambe naku mwingula ba liywaa no waatu ni kumuba oku monahala,  
\v 41 kasa kwaanu onje kono kwaaci anaku yulekiwa kwa Nyambe okutenda apaki, awo anakulya ni kunwa naye munyima no kwinguka kwaafu.  
\v 42 Kame ana tulaelele okukutaza kwaanu ni kupaka nji yokame ona ketiwa kwa Nyambe oku tenda omwatuli no asikuyoya naa sikufa.  
\v 43 Kwayonyene anuhi a Nyambe onje kame apaka nji munu yonje so pumena kwa yonyene kame sa tambule okulemenwa eibi mu litina lyaye.” 
\s1 Asimacaba aba anaku tambula Emebo no Kukena 
\p  
\v 44 Abo Pitolosi yo saamba eyi, Emebo No Kukena sebeli ishetumuka beulu no aanu onje awo ana yupu eliywi.  
\v 45 Aasikupumena mwa onyene asimupato ana kwiiya ni Pitolosi sebeli akomoka, kakuli empo no Mebo No Kukena naitelwe simba kwaa siacaba.  
\v 46 Kakuli kame ana kwayupa aamba mu tipuo tindina oku lumbeka Nyambe. Cwale Pitolosi sebeli wamba nji,  
\v 47 “Kana kame kuli omunu so kanena aa aanu oku kolobeziwa ni meyi aa ana tambula Emebo No Kukena kanyi aaci?”  
\v 48 Cwale sebeli waalaela nji akolobeziwe mu litina lya Jesu Kilesite. Sebeli amukumbela okwikala noo amaywaa acana. 
\c 11  
\s1 Epiho ya Pitolosi ku Keleke ku Jelusalema 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale Atumiwa naaasikupumena awo ali mu Judeya sebeli ayupa nji asimacaba nonyene kame ana tambula eliywi lya Nyambe.  
\v 2 Cwale Pitolosi aba nata ku Jelusalema, onyene asimupato sebeli amuzekisa nji,  
\v 3 “Iikene aba onati kwaalume aa kasita ku mupato ni kulya noo!”  
\v 4 Kono Pitolosi sebei otangisa okwaataluseta mu utungi nji, 
\p  
\v 5 “Kame nina kwikala mu mulenen̄i wa Jopa meni lapela, mi muku hapiwa sebeli ni mona epono no sinu simonahala okwiiya banji kanyi olwambi no kuneneba olu lunungilwe ku mamaneneno anee, mane ni kwiiya kwa mene.  
\v 6 Aba nishetetako okwaliketa, sebeli ni mona eiyamana ni ibatana neyi yeenda ni mapumo ni iyunyi naku wilu.  
\v 7 Cwale sebeli ni yupa eliywi elyamba kwa mene nji, ‘Oimane, Pitolosi, oibae mi olye!’  
\v 8 Kono sebeli naamba nji, ‘Kokuulwa Mbumu! Kakuli asimbakwatanga kakwisa esi no matilo simba nokwakena esi sina ingene mu kanwa kange.’  
\v 9 Kono eliywi sebeli litambula aka no wiili okutunda ku wilu nji, ‘Eso ana kenisa Nyambe kaufanene okusi isana nji litilo.’  
\v 10 Esi kame sinaku tendahala kaatu, mi einu eyo yonje sebeli yukela ku wilu.  
\v 11 Ba nako eyo alume aatu sebeli akeela ku ndoo omo tuna kwikala, anaku tumenwa kwa mene okutunda kwa Sesaaliya.  
\v 12 Cwale Emebo sebeli inambela nji nite noo, okuulwile okuba elibaka. Abaange mutanu ni mumweya sebeli ata nange, mi nuukaingena mu ndoo no mulume woyo.  
\v 13 Cwale sebeli otwambela omo ana kumonena elin̄eloi eli imanine mu ndoo yaye ni kwamba nji, ‘Waatume ku Jopa mi akalonde Simoni woyo oisaniwa Pitolosi.  
\v 14 Kame saambe kwa wene elin̄usa elyo saaliku yoyise, wene naasindoo yowe onje.’  
\v 15 Nji ni tangise okwamba, Emebo No Kukena sebeli ishulumukela beulu yoo kanyi omo ina kwiyela kwaaci ku matatekelo.  
\v 16 Cwale sebeli ni puluka eliywi lya Mbumu, omo ana kwambela nji, ‘Jowani naku kolobeza ni meyi, kono anyi mbamu kolobeziwa ni Mebo No Kukena.’  
\v 17 Nji cwale Nyambe nakwaaba etimpo no kukufeka kanyi eto anakutuba aba tuna kupumena mwa Jesu Kilesite time anyine cwale nji nikanene Nyambe!” 
\p  
\v 18 Cwale aba anaku yupa eyi, sebeli akwa emicima ni ku kanyisa Nyambe aamba nji, “Cwale kwa simacaba Nyambe naabi ngeeso okubaka no moyo.” 
\s1 Ekeleke mu Antiyoki 
\p  
\v 19 Cwale awo anaku hasana mulibaka no mayando ana kwiiya ba nako ana kweenda Setefani okakeela ku Foenisiya ni ku Sipulasi ni ku Antiyoki, aulwile okwamba eliywi kumunu yonje konji ku Majuda omboci.  
\v 20 Kono kame kuna kwikala anjili kwa onyene, alume naku Sipulasi ni ku Sileni nakwiiyanga ku Antiyoki mu kwambola ni Mangelike, oku kutaza eliywi lya Mbumu Jesu kwa onyene.  
\v 21 Amaata a Mbumu na kwikala noo, mi ni palo no kupula awo ana kupumena sebeli asiulukela kwa Mbumu. 
\p  
\v 22 Elin̄usa no eyi sebeli liiya mukuyupahala mu Ndoo ya Nyambe na mu Jelusalema, mi sebeli atuma Banabasi ku Antiyoki.  
\v 23 Cwale aba ana kukeela ni kumona esishemo sa Nyambe, sebeli owabelelwa ni kwasusueza onje nji aongotete kwa Mbumu ni mucima no ku tundamena.  
\v 24 Kakuli neli mulume no kuwaba, nokwiyala Emebo no Kukena ni tumelo. Cwale aanu no kupula sebeli aekezeha kwa Mbumu. 
\p  
\v 25 Cwale Banabasi sebeli ota kwa Tesasi oka saela Saule.  
\v 26 Cwale aba anaku muwana, sebeli omulita ku Antiyoki. Kame ana kwikalamo omwaka aakuwana ni Ndoo ya Nyambe ni kwiyeta aanu no kupula onene. Mu Antiyoki aiyetwa neli ano weli okwisaniwa nji aasikupumena. 
\p  
\v 27 Cwale mu maywaa aa, anuhi a Nyambe sebeli aiya okutunda ku Jelusalema okuta ku Antiyoki.  
\v 28 Cwale omunjili mwa onyene ona kwisaniwa nji Angabusi sebeli wimana ni kwamba ni Mebo nji kame sakwikale elishebo linene mu litunga lyonje, mi eyi kame inaku tendahala mu nako ya Kilaundiyasi.  
\v 29 Aiyetwa sebeli alela oku twalela aasikupumena ayakile mu Judeya etituso omunu ni munu oku tundisa omwa tweseta monje.  
\v 30 Cwale sebeli atenda ngeso, mi niku tumena akulu no Ndoo ya Nyambe , mu maoko a Banabasi ni Saule. 
\c 12  
\s1 Amayando no Kupula 
\p  
\v 1 Mu nako eyo Ombumu Heloda sebeli otangisa oku yandisa anjili no Ndoo ya Nyambe.  
\v 2 Sebeli oibaa Jakobo minaye Jowani ni sabule.  
\v 3 Cwale aba ana kumona nji aendisi no Majuda na wabelelwa, sebeli wekeza okununga ni yonyene Pitolosi. Eyi neli mu maywaa no inkwa na mbulwa omumena.  
\v 4 Cwale aba ana kumana okumununga, sebeli omu beeka mu tolongo ni kumuba mu maoko no ikwata inee no masole, mi kame ana kulela oku mubeeka balubala noanu munyima no Paseka.  
\v 5 Cwale Pitolosi kame ana kuteulwa mu tolongo, kono Endoo ya Nyambe kaisiku lesele oku mulapelela mukusepahala kwa Nyambe. 
\s1 Pitolosi aba nalukululwa mu Tolongo 
\p  
\v 6 Ousiku owo luli abo Heloda yo hupula nji amulite bandee kwaanu, Pitolosi kame nalangananga mukaci no masole ayili yo nungilwe amawenge ayili, mi atateleli ayili aali ba mwelo no tolongo.  
\v 7 Cwale komumone, elin̄eloi lya Mbumu sebeli limonahala, mi eliseli sebeli limonahala mu tolongo, mi sebeli likuba Pitolosi ku timaci ni kumwingula okumwambela nji, “Oinguke mu wangu.” Amawenge sebeli akwa ku maoko aye.  
\v 8 Cwale elin̄eloi sebeli limwambela nji, “Okufuke mi okumange amakatulo owe.” mi sebeli otenda ngeso, elin̄eloi sebeli limwambela nji, “Okufuke omukanjo wowe mi onikon̄e.”  
\v 9 Cwale sebeli obana ni kukon̄a elin̄eloi, kasiku limuka nji elin̄eloi eyi litenda niya luli, kono yonyene kame anaku nahana nji kame amona epono.  
\v 10 Cwale aba anakusiya omutateleli no weli ni uyu no wili, sebeli akeela ba mweelo no sondo ou ota mu mulenen̄i. Omweelo sebeli oku yatulula wenyene kwa onyene, mi sebeli atundamo ni kwenda mu ndila, cwale ababo elin̄eloi sebeli limusiya. 
\p  
\v 11 Cwale Pitolosi sebeli olemuha yonyene ni kwamba nji, “Bano cwale kame ni yii nji ni niti! Mbumu na tumu elingeloi lyaye oku nilukulula mu maoko a Heloda ni kweyo yonje ana kutatelela aanu no Majuda.” 
\p  
\v 12 Cwale aba anaku lemuha sebeli ota ku ndoo ya Maliya, inawaye Jowani no litina linjili lya Maleka, omo ana kuungana ano kupula alemine okulapela.  
\v 13 Cwale abana kokota ba saandi no mweelo, omubika oisaniwa Loda sebeli oiya mukutambula.  
\v 14 Aba ana kulimuka eliywi lya Pitolosi, yo wabelelwe kasiku yatulula omweelo kono sebeli oituka okuta mukaci okaamba nji Pitolosi uno, kame aimanine ba mweelo.  
\v 15 Sebeli aamba kwa yonyene nji, “Kame otakana!” Kono yonyene sebeli ongoteta nji yokame. Sebeli aamba nji, “Ni lingeloi lyaye.” 
\p  
\v 16 Kono Pitolosi sebeli otwalelela okukokota, mi aba anaku yatulula sebeli amumona mi sebeli akomoka.  
\v 17 Kono sebeli waakobeta ni Lyoko nji aondoke, mi sebeli waatolokela omo ana mutundisete Mbumu mu tolongo. Mi sebeli wamba nji, “Mu simwete Jakobo naaasikupumena etaba eyi.” Cwale sebeli waasiya ni kuta ku sibaka sinjili. 
\p  
\v 18 Cwale aba kunakupa, sebeli kwikala omufilifili munene mukaci no masole kweeyo ina tendahala kwa Pitolosi.  
\v 19 Cwale Heloda aba ana kumusaela mi sebeli okwangwa okumuwana, sebeli ozekisa aatateleli ni kulaela nji kame afanena okufa. Cwale Heloda sebeli otunda mu Judeya okuta mu Sesaaliya oka ikalamo. 
\s1 Elifu lya Heloda 
\p  
\v 20 Cwale Heloda onaku tinena aanu namu Tile ni Sidoni, cwale sebeli aiya kwa yonyene aali muumweya onje mi aba anaku twesa okususueza Bulasitasi esikombwa sa Mbumu, sebeli akumbela ekozo. Kakuli eilya yoo kame inakutundanga mu naha ya Mbumu. 
\p  
\v 21 Ba liywaa linaku ketiwa Heloda sebeli okufuka eikumango no umbumu ni kwikala mu lubona lwaye, mi sebeli wamba kwaanu mu umbumu.  
\v 22 Aanu sebeli akuweleza nji, “Eliywi eli lya mulimu, kasa lya munu.”  
\v 23 Ababo elin̄eloi lya Nyambe sebeli limufula, kakuli kasiku kanyisa Nyambe, sebeli oliwa ku mibila ni kufa. 
\p  
\v 24 Kono eliywi lya Nyambe sebeli likula ni kwekezeha. 
\p  
\v 25 Cwale Banabasi ni Saule sebeli auka ku Jelusalema aba anakumana okwiyateteta omusebezi woo, sebeli aiya ni Jowani no litina linjiili lya Maleka. 
\c 13  
\s1 Banabasi ni Saule aba anaku Ketiwa ni ku Tumiwa 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale mu Ndoo ya Nyambe namu Antiyoki kame kuna kwikala aanuhi naaiyeti, Banabasi, Simyoni ona kwisaniwa Nija, Lusiusi namu Sileni ni Manaeni omunjili no manduna no kuta ya Heloda omubusisi ni Saule.  
\v 2 Abo alemine oku kubamena Ombumu ni kukuyumena eilya, Emebo No Kukena sebeli yaamba nji, “Muni ketele Banabasi ni Saule atende omusebezi owo ninaa isanene.”  
\v 3 Cwale aba ana kumana okuuyumena eilya ni kulapela sebeli abeeka amaoko woo beulu yoo ni kwaafundula 
\s1 Mu Sipulasi 
\p  
\v 4 Cwale, bakutumiwa ku Mebo No Kukena sebeli ata ku Selusia, mi okutunda abo sebeli alutela mu Sipulasi.  
\v 5 Cwale aba anoka keela mu Salamisi, sebeli aaka kutaza eliywi lya Nyambe mu tindoo no ilapelo no Majuda. Kame ana kweenda ni Jowani ona kwaatusanga. 
\p  
\v 6 Cwale aba anaende mu sooli mane okakeela ku Pafosi, sebeli akuwana ni mulume no mabibo, omunuhi no mapwa no Majuda no Litina lya Bal-Jesu.  
\v 7 Kame ana kwikalanga ku mubusisi Selgiusi Paulusi, omulume no kushangama. Woyo sebeli oisana Banabasi ni Saule na kulakaza okuyupa eliywi lya Nyambe.  
\v 8 Kono Elimasi no mabibo (kakuli neli yonyene etaluso no litina lyaye) sebeli wahanyeza, ni kweteka okukanisa omubusisi nji alese okupumena.  
\v 9 Kono Saule, woyo wisaniwa kame nji Paulusi, sebeli wiyala ni Mebo No Kukena mi sebeli omwaliketa  
\v 10 ni kwamba nji, “Weene omwana no kwiiba, wene esila no inu yonje nokuluka, wene wiyalile ouyi onje, kaulesele okusinya endila no kooloka ya Mbumu!  
\v 11 Cwale omone, elyoko lya Mbumu kame lili beulu yowe, kame sotende esibofu mi uulwe okumona eliywaa ba nako icana.” 
\p Ababo okwilola ni uwi sebeli ifuka amiyo aye, mi sebeli osaela omunu no kumwendisa ni Lyoko.  
\v 12 Cwale omubusisi sebeli opumena aba ana kumona esi sineeyi, kakuli kame ana kukomokisiwa ku tuto ya Mbumu. 
\s1 Mu Antiyoki namu Pisidiya 
\p  
\v 13 Cwale Paulusi naa ana kwenda noo sebeli atunda mu Pafosi ni kuta okakeela ni ku Pega namu Pamfiliya. Mi Jowani sebeli waasiya ni kuuka ku Jelusalema.  
\v 14 Kono onyene sebeli atunda mu Pega nuuka keela mu Antiyoki namu Pisidiya, mi ba liywaa no Pumulo sebeli aingena mu ndoo no milapelo nuu ka ikala banji.  
\v 15 Munyima no ku bala omulawo naanuhi a Nyambe, aendisi no ndoo no milapelo sebeli aatumena omunu ona kwamba nji, “Abaange, nji kame muli ni liywi no kususuweza aanu, mu lyaambe.”  
\v 16 Cwale Paulusi sebeli oimana, mi yo kobetite ni Lyoko, sebeli wamba nji, 
\p “Alume no Isilaele, naanyi mucila Nyambe, komuteetete!  
\v 17 Nyambe no aanu aa no Isilaele kame ana kukuketela asitetu ni kwaakulisa asiikalile mu naha no Engepita, ni Lyoko no kwimana sebeli waatundisamo,  
\v 18 cwale mu myaka no kukwana makumi anee (40) sebeli oyanda noo mu lihalaupa.  
\v 19 Cwale aba ana kumana okuyundisa amasika mutanu naayili mu naha no Kanana, mi sebeli waaba enaha yoo kanyi ayooli.  
\v 20 Cwale munyima nweeyo, 
\p Sebeli waaba aatuli okutwala ba nako no munuhi wa Nyambe Samwele, mi kame sina kushimba emyaka ina kukwana emwenda inee ni makumi atanu (450).  
\v 21 Cwale aba anaku kumbela nji abiwe ombumu, Nyambe sebeli waaba Saule omwana Kishi, omulume no lusika lwa Benjamine, ni kubusa emyaka inakukwana makumi anee (40).  
\v 22 Cwale aba ana kumana oku mutundisa, sebeli oimeka Dabida okutenda ombumu woo, yonaku pakiwa ni kwamba eyaye nji, ‘Kame nina wana Dabida omwana Jese, omulume woyo okolwisa omucima wange, woyo sotenda eyo nisinga yonje.’  
\v 23 Mu lusika no mulume uyu Nyambe na liti omuyoyisi no Isilaele, yonyene Jesu, kanyi omo ana kusepiseza.  
\v 24 Cwale Jesu yo kasiiya kale Jowani yo wakutaza kale ekolobezo no kubaka kwaanu onje no Isilaele.  
\v 25 Cwale Jowani yoli beebi niku mana omusebezi waye, sebeli nji, ‘Ngasibine muyambuta nji time anyine? Kasa mene yonyene. Kokuulwa, kono munyima yange omunjili okeile, simba etinjatangwa naku makodo aye sitwese okwa nungutula.’ 
\p  
\v 26 “Abaange, aanu no lusika lwa Abulahama naanyi monje aa acila Nyambe, kwaaci na kwiiyi elin̄usa no kuyoyisa.  
\v 27 Kakuli awo ayoya mu Jelusalema naa endisi oo, mulibaka nji kasi limuka Jesu simba okwayupa amaywii no anuhi a Nyambe aa abaliwa ba liywaa ni liywaa eli no Pumulo, naiyateetete eyi no kumwatula.  
\v 28 Simba nji kasikuwana omubonda owo ofanena elifu, sebeli akumbela Pilato kwalukulwela yonyene nji aibaiwe.  
\v 29 Cwale aba ana kumana okwiiyateteta eyo inakun̄oliwa eyaye, sebeli amutundisa ba sitondo ni kumu langeka mu libita.  
\v 30 Kono Nyambe naku mwiingula kwaafu,  
\v 31 ni kumoniwa mu maywaa no kupula kwaao ana kwiiya naye okutunda ku Galileya okuta ku Jelusalema, awo atendile cwale apaki aye kwaanu.  
\v 32 Cwale na tumilitele eliywi no kuwaba elyo Nyambe ana kusepisa kwaa njekulyetu nji,  
\v 33 esi ana iyatetete mwaaci anoo mu kwingula Jesu, kanyi kame omo kun̄olelwe mu Lismu no wiili nji, 
\q1 ‘Tiwe Mwanange, 
\q2 balelo kame nina kuleye.’  
\v 34 Cwale esisupo no niti aba ana mwingula kwaafu, nji katamba kuukela okoola, ya naamba Nyambe nji, 
\q1 ‘Kame sa nikube okukena 
\q2 ni timbuyoti no niti tina kusepisiwa kwa Dabida.’  
\v 35 Cwale ni mu lisamu linjili nakwambiwa nji, 
\q1 ‘Kutamba kupumenena woyo no kukena wowe nji amone okoola.’  
\v 36 Kakuli Dabida aba ana kumana okusebeza mu maywaa aye eso sina kusaelwa kwa Nyambe, sebeli ofa, ni kulangekwa kwa sitaye, ni kumona okoola.  
\v 37 Kono woyo anaingula Nyambe, katamba kumona okoola.  
\v 38 Cwalehe Abange, mu limuke nji, mwa yonyene woyo mulume na mwambeliwa oku lemenwa eibi yenu,  
\v 39 mwa yonyene omunu yonje woyo opumena kame alukululwa ku inu yonje eyo kamutwese oku lukululwa mu mulawo wa Mushe.  
\v 40 Mu tokomele nakubu, nji cwale mu lese okwiyelwa kweyo inambiwa kwaanuhi nji, 
\q1  
\v 41 ‘Komumone, anyi akamashungu, mu komoke, mi mufe! 
\q1 Kakuli kame ni tenda omusebezi mu maywaa enu, 
\q2 omusebezi samuulwe oku pumena, 
\q2 naba sami talusete woo omunu!’” 
\p  
\v 42 Aba ana kusinga okubanamo, aanu sebeli akumbela nji atalusete einu eyo afanena okutalusetwa eli no Pumulo linjili.  
\v 43 Cwale asi mukopano aba ana kufundulwa, aendisi no Majuda no kupula na pulosebelite awo asebeleza Nyambe sebeli akon̄a Paulusi ni Banabasi, awo sebeli aambola noo, ni kwakutaza okongoteta mu sishemo sa Nyambe. 
\p  
\v 44 Eli no Pumulo lina kutatamako omunu yonje namu mulenen̄i sebeli oiya mukuungana bamweya mukuyupa eliywi lya Nyambe.  
\v 45 Kono aendisi no Majuda aba ana kumona elikwanamunu, sebeli ayupa omuna, ni ku kanana eyo ina kwambiwa kwa Paulusi, ni ku mushendoola.  
\v 46 Cwale Paulusi ni Bananbasi sebeli aambela mukwacila nji, “Kame ku lukeele nji eliywi lya Nyambe lyambelwe anyi oweli. Kono aba mulikana kame mukwatula mwenyene nji kamu fanenwe omooyo no kwaabwa, komumone, kame tusiulukela kwa simacaba.  
\v 47 Kakuli cwale Ombumu natu laelele nji, 
\q1 ‘Kame nina kutumu nji otenda eliseli no asimacaba, 
\q2 nji olita oku yoyisa mu litunga lyonje okutwala ku mamaneneno.’” 
\p  
\v 48 Cwale asimacaba aba ana kuyupa ngeso, sebeli awabelelwa, ni kukanyisa eliywi lya Nyambe, mi ano kupula aa ana ketelwe omoyo no kwaabwa, sebeli apumena. 
\p  
\v 49 Cwale eliywi lya Mbumu sebeli lihasana mu silalanda sonje eso.  
\v 50 Kono aendisi no Majuda sebeli asusueza akati aa aketukiwa naalume abusai no mulenen̄i, ni kwingulela Paulusi ni Banabasi amayando, mi sebeli aacita mu naha yoo.  
\v 51 Kono onyene sebeli atutula eliluli ku makondo oo, ni kuta ku Ikoniyamu.  
\v 52 Cwale aiyetwa sebeli aiyala okuwabelelwa ni Mebo no Kukena. 
\c 14  
\s1 Mu Ikoniyamu 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale mu Ikoniyamu sebeli aingena bamweya mu ndoo no milapelo no Majuda, aba ana kwambamo eliywi, epalo no kupula sebeli ipumena bamweya ku Majuda niku Mangelike  
\v 2 Kono aendisi no Majuda anokwa pumena sebeli asusueza asimacaba, mi ni kwafilikanya emicima okulwisa aasikupumena.  
\v 3 Cwale sebeli aikalamo enako no kuleba, aamba eyi no Mbumu mukwacila, awo aaba oupaki ku liywi no sishemo saye, mukutenda eisupo neyi ikomokisa ni maoko oo.  
\v 4 Kono aanu namu mulenen̄i kame anokutaba, anjili ku lineku no Majuda anjili ku lineku no atumiwa. 
\p  
\v 5 Cwale omufilifili aba una kutendiwa ku Majuda bamweya na asimacaba, naa endisi oo, aba ana kusinga nji akatende asiku pumena ouyi ni kwaafula ni mawee.  
\v 6 Atumiwa aba anaku lemuha etaba eyo, sebeli acilela ku Lisitila ni ku Deba emulenen̄i namu Likaoniya, ni mu naha ikubapile nayo.  
\v 7 Omo sebeli akutazamo eliywi. 
\s1 Mu Lisitila 
\p  
\v 8 Cwale mu Lisitila kame kuna kwikalanga omulume onaku leiwa yoli esiyanga no makondo, neli esiyanga okutunda ba kuleiwa kwaye.  
\v 9 Yonyene kame ana kuteteta Paulusi yo aamba. Paulusi sebeli omwaliketa, mi sebeli omona nji kame ali ni tumelo nji abalisiwe  
\v 10 cwale sebeli omwambela ni liywi no kuneneba nji, “Oimane ni makondo owe!” mi sebeli omatuka ni kweenda.  
\v 11 Cwale enyangela aba ina kumona eyo ana kutenda Paulusi, sebeli atangisa okukuwa mu puo no Silikaniya nji, “emilimu kame ineyi kwaaci mu sumbiwa sikufeka kanyi aanu!”  
\v 12 Banabasi kame anaku mubeeka elitina lya Zeusi, Paulusi neli lya Hemasi, kakuli neli yonyene omukulu ku kwamba.  
\v 13 Omupulisita, no ndoo ya Zeusi onyambe woo eyo inakwikala balubala no mulenen̄i, sebeli olita amapulu akabisitwe ni tipalisa ba myelo kame anaku singa okutenda esitabelo bamweya naanu. 
\p  
\v 14 Kono atumiwa Banabasi ni Paulusi aba ana kuyupa eyo, sebeli akaola eikumango yoo, mi sebeli aitukela mukaci no aanu no kupula alemine okukuwa nji,  
\v 15 “Alume, ikene aba mutenda ngesi? naaci tuli alume kanyi aanyi, mi kame tuna militele amaywi no kuwaba, nji kame mufanena okusiuluka okutunda ku inu eyi no mbulwa tuso okuta kuwa Nyambe no kuyoya woyo ona kutenda eliwilu ni litunga, ni liwate, neyo yonje ilimo.  
\v 16 Mu tinako naku nyima kame ana ku lumelelanga aanu onje okwenda mu mikwa yoo.  
\v 17 Nabakulingeso, kasikulesela okuba oupaki kakuli kame anatende wino ni kumiba ombula na kuwilu ni tinako no kukutula, okumiba eilya ni kwiiiyata emicima yenu oku wabelelwa.”  
\v 18 Mu maywi aa kasikutwesa aanu okwakanisa okwatendela eitabelo. 
\p  
\v 19 Kono sebeli kwiiya aendisi no Majuda ana kutunda mu Antiyoki ni mu Ikoniyamu, ni kusususweza aanu, sebeli afula Paulusi ni mawee ni ku mukoka oku mutundisa mu mulenen̄i mu kuhupula nji nafu.  
\v 20 Kono aiyetwa sebeli amubeeka mukaci mi sebeli oinguka ni kwingena mu mulenen̄i. Ba liywaa linaku tatamako sebeli ota ni Banabasi ku Deba. 
\s1 Okuukela ku Antiyoki mu Siliya 
\p  
\v 21 Cwale aba ana kumana okukutaza eliywi mu mulenen̄i owo, ni kuwana aiyetwa no kupula sebeli aukela ku Lisitila ni ku Ikoniyamu ni ku Antiyoki.  
\v 22 Kame ana kongota emicima no aiyetwa ni kwaa susuweza nji atundamene mu tumelo, ni kwamba nji kame tufanena okwingena mu mayando no kupula nji twingene mu mubuso wa Nyambe.  
\v 23 Cwale aba ana kumana okuketa akulu mu keleke ni keleke, ni kulapela nuukuyumena eilya, sebeli aasiya mu sishemo no Mbumu woyo ana ku pumena mwa yonyene. 
\p  
\v 24 Cwale sebeli abita mu naha no Pisidiya ni kuta ku Pamfiliya.  
\v 25 Cwale aba ana kumana okwamba amaywi mu Pega, sebeli ata ku Ataliya,  
\v 26 cwale okutunda abo sebeli alutela ku Antiyoki, omo ana kubeekiwa mu sishemo sa Nyambe mu musebezi owo ana kwiyateteta. 
\p  
\v 27 Cwale aba ana kukeela, sebeli awaneka Ekeleke bamweya ni kwamba yonje eyo Nyambe ana tende noo, nomo ana yatulwele omweelo no tumelo no asimacaba.  
\v 28 Cwale sebeli aikala enako no kuleba naaiyetwa. 
\c 15  
\s1 Omukopano ku Jelusalema 
\p  
\v 1 Kono anjili alume ana kwiiya oku tunda mu Judeya sebeli aiyeta aasikupumena nji, “Aba kamwaingene mu mupato okuta mu mulawo wa Mushe, ka mu tamba okuyoisiwa.”  
\v 2 Cwale Paulusi ni Banabasi abaana kukanana noo onene, Paulusi ni Banabasi naanjili ngeso sebeli ayulekiwa nji ate ku Jelusalema kwaatumiwa naakulu akambole etaba eyo. 
\p  
\v 3 Cwale Endoo ya Nyambe sebeli yaafundula ngeso, sebeli ata endila no kubita mu Foenisiya bamweya ni mu Samaliya, alemine okwamba eyi no ku siuluka no asimacaba, mi sebeli aaba okuwabelelwa no kuneneba kwa asikupumena onje.  
\v 4 Cwale aba ana kwiiya ku Jelusalema, sebeli atambuliwa kwaatumiwa ni keleke, ni kwaakulu, mi sebeli atalusa yonje eyo ana kutenda Nyambe mwa onyene.  
\v 5 Kono aasikupumena anjili ao ali ku seemba no Afalisi sebeli aimana ni kwamba nji, “Esi sifanena ni kwatwala ku mupato, ni kwaa laela nji akuteke omulawo wa Mushe.” 
\p  
\v 6 Atumiwa naakulu sebeli akuwana bamweya okutatuba etaba eyi.  
\v 7 Cwale munyima no kwaambota onene, Pitolosi sebeli oimana nikwamba nji, “Abaange, kame mulimukile nji mu maywaa ana kubwa Nyambe na kuniketa mukaci kenu nji mulibaka no kanwa kange asimacaba kame afanena okuyupa eliywi lya Nyambe ni kupumena.  
\v 8 Cwale Nyambe woyo olimukile emicima yoo, kame aapaka mu kwaaba Emebo No Kukena kanyi omo ana tendele kwaaci.  
\v 9 Kasi tenda eshutano mukaci ketu nonyene, kono kame anaakenisa ni tumelo.  
\v 10 Cwalehe, iikene aba mweteka Nyambe mu kubeeka ecoko mu tindingo no aiyetwa eyo ana kwangwa anjekulyetu simba eyo natukutwesa okushimba?  
\v 11 Cwale kame tupumena nji kame satu yoyisiwe mu sishemo sa Mbumu Jesu, kanyi omo sayoyisetwe nonyene.” 
\p  
\v 12 Cwale esikwata sonje sebeli sondoka mi kame ana kuyupeteta kwa Banabasi ni Paulusi aba ana kutalusa etiponiso ni timakazo eto Nyambe ana kutenda mwa onyene mukaci no asimacaba.  
\v 13 Munyima aba ana kumana okwamba, Jakobo sebeli otambula nji, “Abaange muteetete kwa mene!  
\v 14 Simoni sebeli otalusa omo Nyambe ana ku tangiseta oweli okupotela asimacaba, nji mukaci koo akuketele aanu aa afanena elitina lyaye.  
\v 15 Eyambo eyi kame ilumelelana ni maywi no anuhi a Nyambe, kanyi omo kun̄olelwe nji, 
\q1  
\v 16 ‘Munyima no eyi, kame sa nuuke, 
\q2 mi kame sa ni yake esibaka ana kuyoya Dabida , eso sinakwi 
\q1 Kame sani yake ba matota no kale, 
\q2 mi kame sani wiimeke. 
\q1  
\v 17 Nji aanu ana siyalako asaele Mbumu, 
\q2 naa simacaba onje awo ana isaniwa mulibaka no litina lyange. 
\q1  
\v 18 Kame kwamba Mbumu, woyo ona kutenda einu eyi nji ilimukiwe okutunda ku matatekelo.’ 
\p  
\v 19 Abakulingeso, ekatulo yange ninji, “Katu fanene oku kataza asimacaba awo asiulukela kwa Nyambe.  
\v 20 Kono kame tufanena okwaan̄olela nji atunde kweyi no litilo no maswaniso, ni kuuhule, ni kweyi no kowiwa, ni ku unyinga.  
\v 21 Kakuli okutunda ku nako na kukale mu mulenen̄i ni mulenen̄i kame kuli ao akutaza eyi no milao ya Mushe eli no Pumulo neli no Pumulo mu tindoo no milapelo.” 
\s1 Elin̄olo kwaa Simacaba no Alumeli Okutunda ku Kuta 
\p  
\v 22 Cwale kame kuli wino atumiwa naakulu ni keleke yonje, okuketa alume okutunda mwaonyene ni kwaatuma ku Antiyoki bamweya ni Paulusi ni Banabasi. Sebeli atuma Juda woyo oisanwa nji Banabasi, ni Sailasi, alume abusa mukaci no aasikupumena,  
\v 23 ni kwatumena elin̄olo linjili eli lyamba nji, “Abaange, atumiwa bamweya naakulu, nikwaaasikupumena nwa simacaba mu Antiyoki ni mu Siliya ni mu silisiya, mulumele.  
\v 24 Kakuli na tuyupu nji aanu anjili ana tundu mwaaci kame ana mishupu ni maywi, oka mifilikanya emicima yenu, simba nji katwasikwa laela ngeso.  
\v 25 Naku monahala wino mwaaci, aba tuna lumelelana bamweya, okuketa alume okwatuma kwaanyi naa singiwa etu Banabasi ni Paulusi,  
\v 26 alume ana ku toboha omoyo woo mulibaka lya Mbumu wetu Jesu Kilesite.  
\v 27 Cwalehe natu mitumene Judasi ni Sailasi, awo onyene mbami talusete einu imweya mu liywi no kanwa.  
\v 28 Kakuli na kumonahala wino ku Mebo no kukena ni kwaaci okwamibeeka omushimbo no kuneneba okubita eyi einu no utokwa,  
\v 29 nji mukulya kweyo ina tendiwa esitabelo ku maswaniso neyi itunda ku unyinga ni kweyi no kowiwa neyi itunda mu uhule. Nji kame okuteula wenyene kweeyi, mbu tende wino. Musiyale wino.” 
\p  
\v 30 Cwale aba ana kufundulwa awo, sebeli ata ku Antiyoki, niku waneka bamweya emikopano ni kwaaba elin̄olo.  
\v 31 Cwale aba ana ku libala, sebeli awabelelwa onene ku maywi alyo no susuezo.  
\v 32 Cwale Judasi ni Sailasi, awo ana kutenda onyene aanuhi a Nyambe, sebeli asusueza aasikupumena ni maywi no kupula ni kwaaongota.  
\v 33 Cwale aba ana kwikalamo enako no kuleba, sebeli afundulwa mu kozo kwaaasikupumena awo ana kwafundula. 
\p  
\v 34 Kono Sailasi sebeli osinga oku siyala. 
\p  
\v 35 Kono Paulusi ni Banabasi sebeli asiyala mu Antiyoki, aiyeta ni kukutaza eliywi lya Mbumu, bamweya naanjili ano kupula. 
\s1 Paulusi ni Banabasi aba ano Kutaba 
\p  
\v 36 Cwale munyima no maywaa anjili, Paulusi sebeli wambela Banabasi nji, “Wiiye, tuuke tukapotele aasikupumena mu mulenen̄i ni mulenen̄i omo tuna kwambanga eliywi lya Mbumu, ni kumona omo ayoyela.”  
\v 37 Cwale Banabasi sebeli osinga okushimba Jowani woyo oisaniwa nji Maleka.  
\v 38 Kono Paulusi sebeli onahana nji alese okushimba omunu ona kwaasiya asili mu Pamfiliya, mi kasi kuta noo mu musebezi woo.  
\v 39 Cwale sebeli kwinguka efapano no kuneneba, mane sebeli akutaba, Banabasi sebeli oshimba Maleka ni ku lutela mu Sipulasi,  
\v 40 kono Paulusi sebeli oketa Sailasi ni ku funduka, yo beekilwe mu sishemo no Mbumu kwaaasikupumena.  
\v 41 Cwale sebeli ota mu Seliya ni mu Silisiya, yo ongota etikeleke namo. 
\c 16  
\s1 Timoteya yota ni Paulusi ni Sailasi 
\p  
\v 1 Paulusi sebeli wiiya mu Deba ni ku Lisitila. Omo kame ku na kwikalanga omwiyetwa, no litina lya Timoteya. Omwana no mukati no Mujuda omuasikupumena, kono sitaye neli omungelike  
\v 2 Kame ana kupakiwa wino kwaa asikupumena na mu Lisitila ni mu Ikoniyamu,  
\v 3 Paulusi kame ana ku saela Timoteya nji amu sindekete, mi sebeli omushimba ni ku mubeeka ku mupato mulibaka no Majuda ana kwiikalanga mu ibaka eyo, kakuli kame ana kulimuka nji sitaye neli mungelike  
\v 4 Aali mu musipili woo okuta ku milenen̄i, sebeli alaela aaasikupumena nji amamele omulawo ana kubeeka atumiwa naakulu awo ana kwikalnga mu Jelusalema.  
\v 5 Cwale etikeleke kame tina kongotiwa mu tumelo, ni kwekeza ku palo mu liywaa ni liywaa. 
\s1 Epono ya Paulusi no mulume naku Mesodoniya 
\p  
\v 6 Cwale sebeli ata mu naha no Filinjiya ni mu Galatiya, kakuli Emebo No Kukena kame ina kwaakanisa okwamba amaywi mu Asia.  
\v 7 Cwale aba ana kwiiya okusheeteta amabapa ni Misiya, sebeli a saela okuta mu Betiniya, kono Emebo ya Jesu kaisikwa alumelela.  
\v 8 Cwale aba ana kumana okweenda mu naha no Misiya, sebeli ashetumukela ku Tulowasi.  
\v 9 Paulusi sebeli omona epono mu usiku, omulume naku Mesodoniya yo imanine yo mu kumbela ni kwamba nji, “Wiiye mu Mesodoniya mukututusa.”  
\v 10 Cwale aba ana kumana okumona epono eyo, Ababo sebeli tuku tukiseta mu wangu okuta ku Mesodoniya, me tunahana nji Nyambe kame ana twisanene oka kutazamo eliywi kwa onyene. 
\s1 Mu Filipi, Okufutuka kwa Lidiya 
\p  
\v 11 Aba tuna kufuula okutunda mu Tulowasi, sebeli tuta ku Samotilasi, eliywaa lina kutatamako sebeli tukafuweka mu Ne-yapolisi.  
\v 12 Aba tuna kutundamo sebeli tukaingena mu Filipi, omulenen̄i no weli mu sikiliti no Mesodoniya, kame ni koloni no Maloma. Sebeli twiikalamo amaywaa no mupula.  
\v 13 Cwale ba liywaa no Pumulo sebeli tuta ku nyonga no musindi, oko tuna kuhupula nji kame kuli esibaka no milapelo, mi sebeli twiikala ni kwamba naakati ana ku unganako.  
\v 14 Omukati omunjili mwa onyene ona kutuyupa neli no litina lya Lidiya, ona kutunda mu mulenen̄i no Tiyatila, omuulisi no ibyana no undilu. Woyo olapela Nyambe, mi Ombumu sebeli oyatulula omucima waye nji atokomele eyo aamba Paulusi.  
\v 15 Cwale aba ana kumana okukolobeziwa, naasindoo yaye, sebeli otu kumbela nji, “Nji namwaatula nji mbili wa ku sepahala kwa Mbumu, mwiiye mu ndoo yange mwikalemo.” Sebeli otu hapeleza okuta. 
\s1 Mu Tolongo ku Filipi 
\p  
\v 16 Eliywaa linjili kame tuna tanga mu sibaka no milapelo, sebeli tukuwana ni musizana no mubika woyo oli ni mebo no unuhi, naku fumisa onene molyaye mu ku nuha.  
\v 17 Sebeli okon̄a Paulusi naaci yo kuweleza nji, “Alume aa nabika a Nyambe oli beulu! Kame amyambela endila no mooyo!”  
\v 18 Eyi kame ana kwitenda mu maywaa no kupula. Kono Paulusi sebeli otina, ni ku futuka ni kwamba ku mebo nji, “Kame ni ku laela mu litina lya Jesu Kilesite otunde mwa yonyene!” Cwale sebeli itunda mwa yonyene ababo ba nako eyeyo. 
\p  
\v 19 Kono aolyaye aba ana kumona nji naabwelwe esepo no ku fuma, sebeli alema Paulusi ni Sailasi ni kwatwala mu sibaka no musika balubala nwaa busisi.  
\v 20 Cwale aba ana kumana okwaalita bouso nwaatuli, sebeli aamba nji, “Alume aa, Majuda mi kame alyanganisa omulenen̄i wetu.  
\v 21 Kame aiyeta emikwa eyo no kwafanena nji twiikon̄e ni kwiitambula aaci Amaloma.”  
\v 22 Enyangela sebeli itateka okwaalwisa, 
\p mi aatuli sebeli akaola eikumango yoo ni kuba etaelo nji afuliwe ni pafa.  
\v 23 Cwale aba ana kumana okwafula emiupa no kupula, sebeli aaingenyeka mu tolongo, ni ku laela omutateleli nji aatatelele onene.  
\v 24 Woyo aba na laelelwe ngeeso, sebeli waabeeka mu tolongo na mukaci ni kwaabeeka amakondo oo mu itondo. 
\p  
\v 25 Kono ba kaci no usiku Paulusi ni Sailasi sebeli alapela ni kwiimba etindimo kwa Nyambe, mi amapantiti ateeteta.  
\v 26 Mu nako imweya fela sebeli kwiiya ezikinyeho no litunga, cwale emitomo no tolongo sebeli inyanganya mi ababo emyelo sebeli iyatuluka mi amawenge onje sebeli anungutuka ku munu yonje.  
\v 27 Cwale omutateleli aba ana kwinguka ni kumona nji emyelo naiyatuluka, sebeli oshomona omukwale waye nji akwibae, ba kuhupula nji mwendi amapantiti onje naatundumo.  
\v 28 Kono Paulusi sebeli okuwa ni liywi no kuneneba nji, “Olese okwibaa, kakuli tusilimo toonje.” 
\p  
\v 29 Omutateleli aba ana ku kumbela elibona, sebeli witukelamo, mu kucila sebeli okakwela ku makondo a Paulusi ni Sailasi.  
\v 30 Cwale sebeli waatundiseta ba ndee ni kwamba nji, “Alume, ngasibine sani tende nji ni yoyisiwe?” 
\p  
\v 31 Cwale sebeli aamba nji, “Olumele mwa Mbumu Jesu, mbuyoyisiwa, wene mane naasindoo yowe.”  
\v 32 Cwale sebeli aamba amaywi no Mbumu kwa yonyene ni kwao onje ana kwikala mu ndoo yaye.  
\v 33 Sebeli waashimba mu nako eyeyo no usiku, ni kwaayowisa ba miupa-upa yoo, mi sebeli okolobeziwa ababo naasindoo yaye onje.  
\v 34 Cwale sebeli waalita mu ndoo yaye, ni kwaaba eilya balubala woo, ni ku wabelelwa naa sindoo yaya onje kakuli na lumele mwa Nyambe. 
\p  
\v 35 Kono aba kuna kupa, aatuli sebeli alaela omupolisa, ni kwamba nji, “Waalukulule awo alume akutele.” 
\p  
\v 36 Cwale omupolisa sebeli osimweta Paulusi amaywi awo, ni kwamba nji, “Aatuli nani tumu nji mu lukululwe mu kutele. Cwalehe na mulukululwa, mi mweende mu kozo.” 
\p  
\v 37 Kono Paulusi sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Kame ana tufulu balubala nwaanu, kono kasikutwatula oweli, aci tutendile tuli amaloma, mi naatubeeke mu tolongo. Cwale kame asaela oku tu tundisamo ku mukunda? Kokuulwa! Mwaalesele onyene aiye muku tutundisamo.” 
\p  
\v 38 Amapolisa sebeli asimweta aatuli amaywi ao, mi sebeli acila aba ana kuyupa nji neli Maloma.  
\v 39 Cwale sebeli aiya nuuku kokobeza kwaonyene. Sebeli aatundisamo, ni kwakumbela nji asiye omulenen̄i.  
\v 40 Cwale aba ana kutunda mu tolongo, sebeli ata kwa Lidiya, mi cwale aba ana kumana okumona naaasikupumena, ni kwaaongota emicima, mi sebeli afunduka. 
\c 17  
\s1 Mu Tesalonika 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale aba ana kubita mu Amfipolisi ni mu Apoloniya, sebeli aiya mu Tesalonika omo kuna kwikala endoo no milapelo no Majuda.  
\v 2 Paulusi mu mukwa waye sebeli oingena kwa onyene, mi mu tisunda taatu, yo kanana noo okutunda mu man̄olo  
\v 3 ni kwataluseta ni kwamonisa nji kame kuna kufanena Kilesite oku yupisiwa okukola ni kwinguka kwaafu, ni kwamba nji, “Woyo Jesu nineeyi mu kwamba kwaanyi eyaye, yokame Kilesite.”  
\v 4 Cwale anjili mukaci koo sebeli asusuezwa, nuukuwana ni Paulusi ni Sailasi bamweya naa nokupula no Mangelike mane naakati no kupula ao akutekiwa. 
\p  
\v 5 Kono aendisi no Majuda kame ana kwafelanga omuna, mi sebeli ashimba aafokoli anjili anatoliwa, ni kwaawaneka okwaatenda esitopa, ni kubeeka omulenen̄i mukaci, okutinguluka endoo ya Njasoni, okwaasaela nji aalite kwaanu.  
\v 6 Cwale aba na kuulwa okwawana, sebeli akokela Njasoni naanjili aasikupumena balubala no abusisi no mulenen̄i alemine okukuwa nji, “Alume awo ana liti outata mu litunga, kame aneyi ni kuno,  
\v 7 mi Njasoni naatambula, mi onje kame alwisa emilao ya Sizale aamba nji kame kuli omunjili Ombumu yonyene Jesu.”  
\v 8 Cwale aanu naabusisi no mulenen̄i sebeli ahakanyeha aba ana kuyupa eyi.  
\v 9 Cwale aba ana kushimba amali kwa Josani ni kwaanjili, sebeli aalesela nuukutela. 
\s1 Mu Beliya 
\p  
\v 10 Ababo aasikupumena sebeli afundula Paulusi ni Sailasi ousiku okuta ku Beliya, mi aba ana kukeela sebeli aingena mu ndoo no milapelo no Majuda.  
\v 11 Cwale aendisi no Majuda aa kame ana kwikala ni micima no kuwaba okubita awo na mu Tesalonika, kakuli kame ana tambula eliywi mu kutukufalelwa, ni kusaisisa mu man̄olo mu liywaa ni liywaa okumona nji einu eyi moikalele.  
\v 12 Ano kupula mwaonyene sebeli apumena, naakati no kukutekeha no Mangelike naalume ngeeso.  
\v 13 Kono cwale aendisi no Majuda na mu Tesalonika aba ana kuyupa nji eliywi lya Nyambe kame lyambiwa kwa Paulusi mu Beliya, sebeli aiya mo mu kufilikanya esicaba.  
\v 14 Cwale aasikupumena ababo sebeli afundula Paulusi, okumutwala ku liwate, kono Sailasi ni Timoteya sebeli asiyalamo.  
\v 15 Awo ana sindeketa Paulusi sebeli akakeela ku Atenesisi, abaana kuuka sebeli aiya ni titaelo okutunda kwa Paulusi nji, Sailasi ni Timoteya ate kwa yonyene muwangu mi ababo sebeli afunduka. 
\s1 Mu Atenesisi 
\p  
\v 16 Ababo Paulusi yosaatatelele mu Atenesi, sebeli otina aba ana kumona nji omulenen̄i kame wiyalile eifekiso no milimu.  
\v 17 Cwale sebeli okanana ni Majuda mu ndoo no milapelo naanu awo acila Nyambe, sebeli otenda ngeso muliywaa ni liywaa ku munu yonje woyo ona kuwaninga mu musika.  
\v 18 Cwale a si Epikulini ni sitoiki filosofi sebeli aambola naye. Mi anjili sebeli aamba nji, “Osibuwabuwi uyu iikene aamba?” 
\p Anjili sebeli aamba nji, “Kame amonahala kanyi omukutazi no milimu indina.” kakuli kame ana kwaataluseta ya Jesu neyi no kwinguka kwaafu.  
\v 19 Cwale sebeli amushimba, okuta naye ku Aleopangasi ni kwamba nji, “Kame tusinga okulimuka eyi tuto no ubya eyi wamba iikene italusa?  
\v 20 Kakuli nuliti eyambo no kwatwaelwa mu matwi etu, cwale kame tusinga okulimuka eyi italusa.”  
\v 21 Cwale Amaatenesi onje naanu andina ao ayoyanga mo kaasikutenda esindina konji okwamba simba okuyupa eyi no ubya. 
\p  
\v 22 Cwale Paulusi sebeli oimana bakaci nwa Aleopangasi ni kwamba nji, “Anyi alume no Atenesi, kame ni lemuhile nji mu ndila yonje kame muli ni tumelo.  
\v 23 Kakuli aba ninabiti kame nina mono outokwa wetu noo ku lapela, sebeli ni wana ealetale aba ku n̄olilwe nji, ‘Kwa Nyambe no kwalimukiwa.’ Iikene cwale aba mu lapelela einu no kwalimukiwa, eyi yanamba kwaanyi.  
\v 24 Nyambe ona ku tenda elitunga niinu yonje ilimo, bakutenda Ombumu no liwilu ni litunga, ka yoyo mu tikeleke ti yakilwe ni maoko nwaanu.  
\v 25 Simba kame asebelezwa ni maoko nwaanu, kanyi nji kame asaela esinjili, kakuli yonyene kame aba aanu onje ouplo ni kooyela ni inu yonje.  
\v 26 Cwale kame ana kutenda mumweya mu matunga onje nwaanu oku yoya ba lubala no litunga longe, yokame ona lukisa etinako ni miseto no aanu omo ayayo.  
\v 27 Cwale nji kame afanena okusaela Nyambe, mu kuyambuta nji mba mubabatele ni ku muwana, mi yonyene kayoyo oku no kuleba naaci.  
\v 28 kakuli mwa yonyene kame, 
\q1 ‘Tuyoya, ni kweenda, ni kwikala kwetu.’ 
\m Sokame anaamba asikuloka anjili nji, 
\q1 ‘Naaci kame tuli anaaye luli.’ 
\m  
\v 29 Cwale aba tuli ana a Nyambe, ka tulukele oku yambuta nji Nyambe mba feke kanyi gauda, simba esilibela, simba eliwee, eili eyi imanena esifekiso no mihupulo no munu.  
\v 30 Mu nako na kunyima Nyambe kame ana kwaliketanga aanu feela, kono bano kame alaela aanu onje okwaali nji abake.  
\v 31 Kakuli na kubeeka eliywaa elyo saatule elitunga mu niti mu mulume woyo ana kuketa, mi mweesi nabi aanu onje mu kumwingula kwaafu!” 
\p  
\v 32 Cwale aba na kuyupa eyi no kwinguka kwaafu, anjili sebeli asheka kono anjili sebeli aamba nji, “Kame satu kuyupe kame wamba ba tuto eyi.”  
\v 33 Cwale Paulusi ababo sebeli waasiya.  
\v 34 Kono aanu anjili sebeli akon̄a ni ku pumena, mwaonyene Denisi no Aleopangasi ni mukati no litina lya Damalisi naanjili aanu. 
\c 18  
\s1 Mu Kolinte 
\p  
\v 1 Aba kuna bwi eyo, Paulusi sebeli otunda mu Atenesi okuta ku Kolinte.  
\v 2 Cwale sebeli okawana Omujuda no litina lya Akila, kakuli Kulaude kame ana ku laela aendisi no Majuda okutunda mu Loma. Cwale sebeli ota okaamona,  
\v 3 kakuli neli omunu no musebezi umweya nonyene, sebeli oikala noo, mi kame ana ku sebezanga, kakuli neli asiku tenda amatende.  
\v 4 Cwale kame anakukanananga mu ndoo no milapelo eli no Pumulo lyonje, mi sebeli osusuweza aendisi no Majuda ni Mangelike 
\p  
\v 5 Cwale Sailasi ni Timoteya aba ana kukeela okutunda ku Mesodenia, Paulusi yo patehile ni kukutaza, okuba oupaki ku Majuda nji Kilesite yokame Jesu.  
\v 6 Cwale aba ana ku mu sheununa, sebeli otutula eikumango yaye ni kwamba nji, “Ounyinga wenu wikale ba mitwi yenu! Mene sikwite omubonda ku onyene. Okutunda bano kame sanite kwaa simacaba.”  
\v 7 Cwale sebeli otundamo ni kuta ku ndoo ya mulume no litina lya Tite Justusi omulapeli wa Nyambe, endoo yaye kame ina kwikalanga abeebi ni ndoo no milapelo.  
\v 8 Kilisipo omubusisi no tindoo no milapelo, ona ku pumena mwa Mbumu, bamweya naa sindoo yaye, mi Amakolinte ano kupula ana kuyupa Paulusi sebeli apumena mane niku kolobeziwa. 
\p  
\v 9 Cwale Ombumu sebeli wamba kwa Paulusi mu usiku umweya mu pono nji, “Olese kucila, kono waambe mi olese okondoka,  
\v 10 kakuli kame nili ni wene, mi kakwisa omunu so kulwisa simba okulemeka, kakuli kame nili naanu no kupula muno mu mulenen̄i.”  
\v 11 Cwale sebeli oikala omwaka mu mweya ni tikweti mutanu ni kamweya, (6) yo iyeta eliywi lya Nyambe mwaonyene. 
\p  
\v 12 Kono cwale Galiyo yoli omubusisi no Akaya, aendisi no Majuda sebeli akuwana ni ku lwisa Paulusi ni ku mulita balubala no Kuta.  
\v 13 Sebeli aamba nji, “Wuyu mulume kame asusuweza aanu ku lapele Nyambe mu ndila eyo ilwisa omulawo!” 
\p  
\v 14 Kono Paulusi aba ana kusinga okwamba, Galiyo sebeli wambela aendisi no Majuda nji, “Kambe ni mulibaka no kufosa simba okutenda omubonda, kambe kame kuli elibaka elyo ni twesa oku miyupisisa anyi aendisi no Majuda.  
\v 15 Kono kakuli ni mulibaka no tipuzo no maywi ni matina ni mulawo wetu, mu kumonene mwenyene. Kame ni kana okwatula eyambo eyi.  
\v 16 Cwale sebeli waatundisa mu Kuta.  
\v 17 Cwale onje sebeli alema Sosiene, omwendisi no ndoo no milapelo ni ku mufula balubala no Kuta. Kono Galiyo kasi kutwalako omucima. 
\s1 Okuuka ku Antiyoki 
\p  
\v 18 Munyima no eyi, Paulusi sebeli oikala amaywaa no kupula, ni kusiya akwaye ni kulutela ku Siliya, yo enda ni Pulisila ni Akila. Ku Senkiliya, sebeli okukuliwa etin̄uki, kakuli kame ano kununga esinjili.  
\v 19 Cwale sebeli akeela mu Efese, mi sebeli waasiyamo, kono yonyene sebeli ota mu ndoo no milapelo mu ku kanana ni Majuda.  
\v 20 Cwale aba ana ku mukumbela nji aikale noo enako no kuleba, sebeli okana.  
\v 21 Kono aba kwaasiya, sebeli waambela nji, “Kame sani kauke kwaaci nji Nyambe mba singi.” Cwale sebeli oluta okusiya Efese. 
\p  
\v 22 Cwale aba ana kukeela mu Sesaaliya, sebeli ota okakeeta etikeleke mi cwale sebeli oshetumuka ku Antiyoki.  
\v 23 Munyima no kwikalamo enako, sebeli ota ku sibaka ni sibaka mu naha yonje no Galatiya ni Filigiya yo ongota aiyetwa. 
\s1 Apolosi mu Efese ni mu Kolinte 
\p  
\v 24 Cwale Omujuda onakwisaniwa nji Apolosi, woyo ona kuleyelwa mu Alekizandiliya, sebeli wiiya mu Efese. Neli omulume no kulimuka okwamba wino ona kwiyeta eliywi.  
\v 25 Kame ana kwiyeta mu ndila ya Mbumu, ni kutenda omubika mu mebo, kame aamba ni kwiyeta wino-wino einu eyi yaama Jesu, kono eyo ana kulimuka yonyene neli kolobezo ya Jowani fela.  
\v 26 Sebeli otateka okwamba mu undume mu ndoo no milapelo, kono cwale Pulisila ni Akila aba ana ku muyupa, sebeli amutwala ku ndoo ni ku mutaluseta omo aikalele Nyambe wino.  
\v 27 Cwale aba ana kusinga okuta okulutela ku Akaya, aasikupumena sebeli amususuweza ni kun̄olela aiyetwa nji amutambule. Aba ana kukeela, sebeli otusa onene mu sishemo awo ana ku pumena.  
\v 28 Kakuli kame ana kutwesa okwambela aendisi no Majuda mu maata no kuneneba mukwamonisa mu man̄olo nji, Kilesite yokame Jesu. 
\c 19  
\s1 Paulusi mu Efese 
\p  
\v 1 Apolosi yoli mu Kolinte Paulusi sebeli okaula enaha eyi ilumbile ni kwiiya mu Efese. Omo sebeli owana aiyetwa anjili.  
\v 2 Cwale sebeli waaibanguta nji, “Na mukutambula Emebo No Kukena aba muna ku pumena?” Mi sebeli atambula nji, “Kokuulwa, katwa siku yupa simba mbicana nji kame kuli Emebo No Kukena.”  
\v 3 Cwale sebeli waaibanguta nji, “Ka kolobezo mu na kukolobezwa nayo?” 
\p Sebeli atambula nji, “Mu kolobezo ya Jowani.”  
\v 4 Cwale Paulusi sebeli wamba nji, “Jowani kame ana ku kolobeza ni kolobezo no kubaka, okwambela aanu nji apumene kwa woyo soiya munyima yaye, yonyene Jesu.” 
\p  
\v 5 Aba ana kuyupa eyo, sebeli akolobezwa mu litina lya Mbumu Jesu.  
\v 6 Cwale Paulusi aba anakumana okwabeeka amaoko aye beulu, Emebo No Kukena sebeli yaashulumukela beulu yoo, mi sebeli aamba mu tindimi no kwalimukiwa mane ni kunuha.  
\v 7 Oonje kame ana kukwana epalo ikuma ba likumi naayili (12). 
\p  
\v 8 Cwale sebeli oingena mu ndoo no milapelo mi mu tikweti taatu yo aamba mu undume, yo kanana noo ni kwakolwisa eyi no mubuso wa Nyambe.  
\v 9 Kono anjili kame ana kwikala ni mahanyi okwapumena, aamba eyi no kwiiba eyi no Ndila balubala no mukopano, sebeli otunda kwa onyene, ni ku shimba aiyetwa, yo ambola noo mu liywaa ni liywaa mu muyako no ndoo ya Tilanasi.  
\v 10 Eyo sebeli yekeza mu myaka yiili, nji cwale aanu no Asiya ayupe eliywi lya Mbumu aendisi no Majuda bamweya ni Magelike 
\s1 Aana a Sikeba 
\p  
\v 11 Cwale Nyambe naku tenda etimakazo no ku komokisa mu maoko a Paulusi.  
\v 12 Etitaulo mane ni tinyambi naiku tundisiwa ba lutu lyaye sebeli ibeekiwa kwaa sikukola, ni meeti sebeli atunda, ni mebo no kwiiba sebeli itunda mwa onyene.  
\v 13 Cwale anjili no aendisi no Majuda ana kwendanga atundisa Emebo no kwiiba, kame ano kutusisanga okwamba elitina lya Jesu nji, “Kame ni ku laela mu litina lya Jesu, woyo ona kukutaziwa kwa Paulusi.”  
\v 14 Aana mutanu na yiili no mupulisita mukulu no Majuda no litina lya Sikeba ana kutenda ngeso. 
\p  
\v 15 Kono emebo no kwiiba sebeli yaatambula nji, “Jesu ni muyii, ni Paulusi ni muyii, kono wene tiwe anyine?” 
\p  
\v 16 Cwale omulume woyo ona kwingeniwa ku mebo kwiiba sebeli waamatukela beulu ni kwaakoma, mane sebeli atunda ku ndoo eyo aali njeshe ni ku lemekiwa.  
\v 17 Cwale eyi yonje sebeli ilimukiwa kwaanu onje na mu Efese, aendisi no Majuda bamweya ni Magelike, mi sebeli aingenenwa okucila onje, mi elitina lya Mbumu Jesu sebeli lilumbiwa onene.  
\v 18 Aasikupumena no kupula kwaao ana kupumena sebeli aiya, mu kuukunyaza ni shongotola eyo no kwiiba ana kutendanga.  
\v 19 Cwale epalo nwao ana kutendanga amabibo sebeli alita etibuka too ni kuticin̄a aanu onje amwine, mi sebeli abala eteko no tibuka kame ina kwana eikiti makumi mutanu (50; 000) no muwaya-waya no silibela.  
\v 20 Cwale eliywi lya Mbumu sebeli liyanduluka ngeso ni kukula. 
\s1 Emifilifili mu Efese 
\p  
\v 21 Cwale eyo aba ina kubwako, Paulusi sebeli olela mu muhupulo no mebo nji abite mu Mesodeniya ni Akaya ni kuta ku Jelusalema, yo aamba nji, “Munyima no kwikala kuya,” sebeli wamba nji, “Kame ni fanena okamona ku Loma.”  
\v 22 Cwale aba ana kumana otuma aiyetwa aye ayili mu Mesodoniya awo amutusa, Timoteya ni Elasito, yonyene yosili mu Asiya mbicani. 
\p  
\v 23 Kusili mu nako eyo omufilifili no kuneneba sebeli wiiya mulibaka no Ndila.  
\v 24 Kakuli omulume wisaniwa Demetiliusi, woyo ona kuumbanga endoo no silibela no milimu no Atemisi, kame ana kuluwisa onene abeleki no musebezi owo.  
\v 25 Cwale sebeli waawaneka bamweya, naawo anjili asebeza omusebezi kanyi woo, ni kwamba kwa onyene nji, “Alume, kame mulimukile nji aba mufuma ni mulibaka no musebezi ou.  
\v 26 Cwale kame mu mona ni kuyupa nji kasa mu Efese feela kono ni mu naha yonje no Asia Paulusi kame ana susuweze ni kukolwisa epalo no aanu, yo aamba nji, emilimu itendiwa ni maoko kasa emilimu.  
\v 27 Ekozi eyo iiya, kasa nji omusebezi wetu mbau shwauka, kono ngeso ni ndoo no mulimu mukati otompeha oisniwa nji Atemisi kame saya liketwe kanyi esinu na mbulwa tuso, nji mane niku tompeha kwaye kame saku sinyehe, yonyene woyo olapelelwa mu Asiya ni mu litunga lyonje!” 
\p  
\v 28 Cwale aba ana kuyupa eyo, sebeli atina onene ni kukuwa nji, “Woyo no kuneneba ni Aetemisi no Maifese!”  
\v 29 Cwale omulenen̄i sebeli wiyala ni ku hakanyeha, mi sebeli aitukela bamweya mu teatele nikulema Gayusi ni Alisitako aanu na mu Mesodoniya awo ana ku sindeketanga Paulusi mu misipili.  
\v 30 Paulusi kame ana kusinganga oku monahaza kwaanu no kupula, kono aasikupumena kasi ku mulumelelanga.  
\v 31 Cwale ni manduna anjili na mu Esiya awo anokusinga naye, sebeli amutumena ni ku mukumbela nji alese okumonahaza ba patelo.  
\v 32 Cwale anjili sebeli akuwa sinu simweya, anjili sinjili kame, kakuli kame ana kuungana mu kuhakanyeha, mi ano kupula kasiku limuka eso ana kuunganena.  
\v 33 Anjili aanu mu nyangela sebeli atundisa Alekizanda, woyo aendisi no Majuda ana kubeeka kuuso. Cwale Alekizanda sebeli okobeta ni Lyoko nji akutambwele kwaanu.  
\v 34 Kono aba ana ku lemuha nji neli Mujuda, mu tihola timbili sebeli akuwa onje mu liywi limweya nji, “Ounene ni wa Atemisi no Maifese!” 
\p  
\v 35 Cwale omun̄oli no Kuta no mulenen̄i sebeli ondota enyangela ni kwamba nji, “Aana no Efese!” anyine kwaanu no kwalimuka nji omulenen̄i no Efese omubabaleli no ndoo no mulimu no mukati no kutompeha Atemisi ni wa liwee no sitabelo no kukena sinakwi ku wilu?  
\v 36 Cwale mumone nji einu eyo kailatulwa, abakulingeso kame mulukela okondoka mi mulese okutenda esinjili mu wangu.  
\v 37 Kakuli kame munaliti aa alume bano nji kasi sinya endoo no mulimu wetu no mukati simba nji asikunyefula emilimu yetu.  
\v 38 Cwale nji Demetiliyasi naabeleki ali kwa yonyene nji kame ali ni muzeko ni munu, etikuta kame tiyatulukile, kame kuli nasi kwatula, akutwale ku kuzeka.  
\v 39 Kono nji kame kuli ni taba indina musaela, kame saiatulwe mu mukopano ofanena.  
\v 40 Kakuli kame tuli mu utata no ku atulwa mu mufilifili balelo, kakuli katu kwite elibaka satwimane nalyo mulibakano mukopano owo.  
\v 41 Cwale aba ana kumana okwamba eyo, sebeli olukulula omukopano. 
\c 20  
\s1 Ku Masedoniya ni mu Gelike 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale omufilifili aba una kubwa, Paulusi sebeli owaneka aiyetwa, okwaasusueza ni kwaalana, niku funduka okuta ku Mesodoniya.  
\v 2 Cwale aba ana kumana okumona enaha eyo, ni kwaasusuweza onene, sebeli ota mu naha no Magelike  
\v 3 Omo sebeli okaikalamo etikweti taatu, mi aendisi no Majuda sebeli amukundamena abo anokutukiseta okuta mu Siliya, sebeli onahana okuuka endila no Mesodoniya.  
\v 4 Sopatele naku Beliya omwana Pilasi sebeli oomu sindeketa, Alisitakasi ni Sekundasi Amatesalonika, ni Gayusi na ku Debe ni Timoteya, naa naku Asiya neli Tikikasi ni Tilofimasi.  
\v 5 Onyene kame anoku tangeta, sebeli aka twimanena mu Tulowasi.  
\v 6 Kono aci sebeli tu tunda mu Filipi munyima no mukiti no Inkwa no mbulwa omumena, munyima no amaywaa mutanu, sebeli tu keela mu Tulowasi, omo sebeli twiikalamo amaywaa mutanu naayiili (7). 
\s1 Paulusi aba ana Kupota aka no Mamaneneno ku Tulowasi 
\p  
\v 7 Ba liywaa no weli mu sunda, abo me tukuwanine bamweya okulya esilyela, Paulusi sebeli wamba noo, kakuli kame na kufanena okufunduka amasiku eliywaa linaku tatamako, mi kame ana kwambola noo enako no kuleba mane konji bakaci no usiku.  
\v 8 Kame kuna kwikala etilambi no kupula mu ndoo na kuwilu omo tu nakukuwanena.  
\v 9 Cwale ondumbana no litina lya Eutikasi kame ana kwikala mu lihaulo no ndoo, sebeli olangana otulo no kuneneba luli abo Paulusi yo twalelela okwambola ba nako no kuleba, yoli mu tulo, sebeli okwela banji okatunda ku ndoo na kuwilu no waatu. Sebeli ononiwa yo file.  
\v 10 Kono Paulusi sebeli oshetumukela banji ni kwinamena beulu yaye, ni ku mufumbatela yo aamba nji, “Olese kubilaela, kakuli omoyo waye osili mwa yonyene.”  
\v 11 Cwale Paulusi aba ana kukambama kame, sebeli okomauna esinkwa, aba ana kumana okulya, sebeli wambola noo enako no kuleba konji amasiku, sebeli ofunduka.  
\v 12 Ondumbana sebeli amutwala ku mundi yo yoya, mi sebeliaombaombiwa mu micima onene luli. 
\s1 Okutunda mu Tulowasi okuta mu Miletasi 
\p  
\v 13 Kono sebeli tuku tangeta ku sisepe, sebeli tukulongamo ni ku fuula okuta ku Asosi, omo kame tunaku singa okushimba Paulusi, yonyene kame ana kukutukiseta ngeso, kakuli yonyene kame ana kusaela okweenda ni makondo.  
\v 14 Cwale aba ana ku tuwana ku Asosi, sebeli tu mu longa, ni kuta naye ku Mitileni.  
\v 15 Aba tuna kufuulamo, eliywaa lina kutatamako sebeli tukeela ba mabapa ni Kiyosi, eli lina kutatamako kame sebeli tukakeela ku Samosi, elinjili kame eliywaa sebeli tukakeela ku Miletasi.  
\v 16 Kakuli Paulusi kame ana kulela nji alese okufuweka mu Efese, nji cwale alese oku liyehela mu Esiya kakuli kame ano ku tukiseta okaikala mu Jelusalema nji kame kutwesahala, ba liywaa no Pentakota. 
\s1 Okulana kwa Paulusi Kwaakulu no Efese 
\p  
\v 17 Paulusi yoli mu Miletasi, sebeli otumena ku Efese okaisana aakulu no keleke.  
\v 18 Cwale aba ana kukeela kwa yonyene, sebeli waambela nji, “Kame mulimukile omukwa nina yoyo mukaci kenu enako yonje okutunda ba liywaa no weli elyo nina kukeela mu Asiya.  
\v 19 Kame nina sebeleze Mbumu mu uku kokobeza konje ni mu myooti ni mu miliko ina kuniyela mu mifumbo no Majuda.  
\v 20 Omo ka nisi ukela munyima oku myambela esinu sonje eso sina ku fanena oku mitusa, ni ku miiyeta mu sicaba ni mu ndoo ni ndoo.  
\v 21 Menilemine okupakela aendisi no Majuda bamweya ni Mangelike kweeyi no kubaka kwa Nyambe neyi no tumelo mwa Mbumu wetu Jesu Kilesite.  
\v 22 Komumone cwale, kame nita ku Jelusalema, meni nungilwe mu mebo, mu kwalimuka eyo saika tendahaleko kwa mene.  
\v 23 Esi ni limukile ninji mu mulenen̄i ni mulenen̄i Emebo No Kukena kame ina kuni pakela nji okunungiwa ni ku yandisiwa kame initatelele.  
\v 24 Kono kani bilaele eyo, mi kanibalele omoyo wange nji niwautokwa kwa mene, esi nisinga feela ninji ni manenene omusipili ni musebezi wange ananibi Ombumu Jesu, no kupaka eliywaa no sishemo sa Nyambe. 
\p  
\v 25 Cwale komumone, kame ni limukile nji aanyi monje awo inendele emisipili okumikutaza eyi no mubuso wa Nyambe kamutamba okumona olubala lwange kame.  
\v 26 Cwalehe kame ni myambela eniti balelo nji, kani kwite omubonda no unyinga wenu moonje.  
\v 27 Kakuli kani siuka munyima mu kumitaluseta omulelo wonje wa Nyambe.  
\v 28 Cwale aanyi muku babalele, mi mu lise omutapi mu nabiwi oku ubabalela mu Mebo No Kukena oku babalela Endoo ya Nyambe ya Nyambe eyo ana kuulele ni unyinga wa Mwanaye.  
\v 29 Kakuli kame ni limukile nji aba sani misiye, kame sakwiiye aandiwi no kucilisa mukaci kenu, awo saulwe okuyupela omutapi amakeke.  
\v 30 Cwale mukaci kenu luli kame sakutunde alume asaambe einu no mapwa nji aiyetwa aakon̄e.  
\v 31 Cwalehe mutokomele, muhupule nji mu myaka yaatu kani lesele okweleza ni myooti ousiku ni munji ku munu ni munu. 
\p  
\v 32 Cwalehe bano kame ni mibeeka kwa Nyambe ni ku liywi no sishemo saye, elyo saali miyake ni kumiba esanda naa akenine onje.  
\v 33 Kanisi lakaza esilibela ni gauda ya munu simba esibyana.  
\v 34 Aanyi mwenyine kame muyii omo ina belekele ni maoko ange okuwana omu no kuyoyela mane nawo ana kwikalanga nange.  
\v 35 Mu inu yonje kame nina mi monisa nji mu sebeze ngeso, kame mu fanena okutusa asiku fokola, me muhupula amaywi ana kwamba Jesu nji, ‘Embuyoti kame ili onene mu kuba kasa muku tambula.’” 
\p  
\v 36 Cwale aba ana kumana okwamba ngeso, sebeli okubama ni manwi banji ni kulapela noo onje.  
\v 37 Cwale onje sebeli alila niku kwela mu mbando ya Paulusi ni kumutubeta.  
\v 38 Kame ana kutomoha onene emicima onje mulibaka no maywi aye ana kwamba nji kaatamba kumona kame olubala lwaye. Cwale sebeli amusindeketa okamukeeta ku sisepe. 
\c 21  
\s1 Paulusi Yoota ku Jelusalema 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale aba tuna mana oukutaba noo mu ku bambaba feela, sebeli tufuula, mi sebeli tulumba ku Kosi, mi liywaa linakutatamako sebeli tukeela mu Lodesi, okutunda omo sebeli tuta ku Patala.  
\v 2 Cwale aba tuna kuwana esisepe silumbile ku Foenisiya, sebeli tukulongamo ni kuta.  
\v 3 Cwale aba tuna keela mu sibaka no Sipulasi, sebeli tusi yupela ku simoo okuta mu Silia, sebeli tuka fuweka mu Tile, kakuli omo esisepe kame sina kulongola etutu.  
\v 4 Cwale sebeli tuwanamo aiyetwa, ni kwiikala noo amaywaa mutanu ni twiili (7). Mu mebo sebeli aambela Paulusi nji alese okuta ku Jelusalema.  
\v 5 Cwale amaywaa etu aba ana kubwa, sebeli tu funduka okwekeza omusipili wetu ni kutu sindeketa onje, naa moyo oo naanoo, ni ku tulita konji aba ana kutu siisa omulenen̄i, sebeli tu kubama ni manwi ba likamba okulapela ni ku kulana omnjili ni munjili okuwaba.  
\v 6 Cwale sebeli tukulonga mu sisepe, onyene sebeli aukela ku mundi. 
\p  
\v 7 Cwale aba tuna kumana omusipil wetu okutunda mu Tile, sebeli tuta ku Tolemaisi ni kukeeta aasikupumena ni kwiikala noo eliywaa limweya.  
\v 8 Eliywaa lina ku tatamako sebeli tu funduka nuukakeela mu Sesaaliya, mi sebeli twiingena mu ndoo ya Filipi omwaambi no mikopano, woyo ona kutenda omunjili noao mutanu ni twiili (7) ni kwikala kwa yonyene.  
\v 9 Kame ana kwikala naanaye anee nwa sizana no kwaakwaliwa, ana ku nuhanga.  
\v 10 Aba tuna kwikalamo amaywaa mbicana, sebeli kwiiya omunuhi no litina lya Agabusi ona ku tunda ku Judeya.  
\v 11 Cwale aba ana kukeela kwaaci, sebeli okununga olukanda lwa Paulusi ku maoko ni ku makondoo ni kwamba nji, “Eesi, so kame esinaambiwa ku Mebo No Kukena nji, aendisi no Majuda mu Jelusalema mwasanungele omunya lukanda olu, ni ku mubeeka mu maata ano macaba.” 
\p  
\v 12 Cwale aba tuna kuyupa ngeso, aaci naanu sebeli tu mukumbela nji alese okukambama okuta ku Jelusalema.  
\v 13 Cwale Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, “Iikene aba mulila ni kucola omucima wange? Kakuli mene kame ni kutukisite kasa okwingena mu tolongo feela, kono simba okufa ku Jelusalema mulibaka no litina lya Mbumu Jesu.” 
\p  
\v 14 Sebeli okana okukolwisiwa kwaaci, sebeli toondoka ni kwamba nji, “Ku tendahale eso sisingwa kwa Mbumu.” 
\p  
\v 15 Munyima no maywaa ao, sebeli tuku tukiseta okuta ku Jelusalema.  
\v 16 Cwale naiyetwa anjili ana ku tunda ku Sesaaliya sebeli ata naaci, oku tutwala ku ndoo ya Nasoni, omwiyetwa no kale na ku Sipulasi, oko tuna ku fanena okwikala. 
\s1 Paulusi yo Potela Jakobo 
\p  
\v 17 Cwale aba tuna ku keela mu Jelusalema, aasikupumena sebeli atu tambula wino mu ku wabelelwa.  
\v 18 Eliywaa lina ku tatamako Paulusi ota naaci kwa Jakobo, mi onje akulu sebeli aikalako.  
\v 19 Munyima no kwakeeta, sebeli otalusa wino einu eyo Nyambe ana tende kwaasimacaba mu musebezi waye.  
\v 20 Cwale aba ana kuyupa eyo, sebeli akanyisa Nyambe. Mi sebeli aamba kwa yonyene nji, “Omwabetu, esi omwine nji, aendisi no Majuda aa ana lumele sebeli eikiti no kupula, mi aanu onje kame atukufalelwe omulawo.  
\v 21 Kame anaambelwe eyowe nji wene kame wiyeta aendisi no Majuda onje awo ayoya mwano asimacaba nji afulalele Mushe, okwaambela nji alese okutwala anoo ku mupato simba okukuteka eizo yoo.  
\v 22 Cwale ngasibine saitendahale? Kame saayupe nji nwiyi.  
\v 23 Otenda eyo tukwambela. Kame tukwite alume anee awo ali munji no sepiso noutokwa.  
\v 24 Waashimbe aa alume okakukenise noo, mi waatenekele nji cwale aka beulise emitwi yoo. Cwale aanu onje kame saalimuke nji kakwisa esinjili eso ana yupu kweyo inambiwa mulibaka lyowe kono nji ni wene kame oyoya mu ku tokomela omulawo wa Mushe.  
\v 25 Kono kweeyo no asimacaba ana lumele, kame tunaatumene elin̄olo no mulelo wetu nji kame afanena okukana kweeyo ina tendelwe emilimi, ni ku unyinga, ni kweyo ina owiwa, ni uhule. 
\p  
\v 26 Cwale Paulusi sebeli oshimba aalume awo, mi ba liywaa linaku tatamako sebeli okukenisa noo ni kwingena mu ndoo ya Nyambe, okwamba amaywaa no kukenisa koo aba saiyatetetwe ni nubu nai kubiwa eyi no munu ni munu woo. 
\s1 Okunungiwa Kwa Paulusi mu Ndoo ya Nyambe 
\p  
\v 27 Cwale amaywaa mutanu naayili aba ana kwatumela okubwa, aendisi no Majuda na ku Esiya awo ana kumumona mu ndoo ya Nyambe, sebeli asusuweza enyangela ina kukuwana mu kupula, ni ku mulema.  
\v 28 Cwale sebeli akuwa nji, “Alume no Isilaele, komutuse! Uno yokame omutu ona kwiiyetanga aanu onje mu ibaka yonje okulwisa aanu ni mulawo ni sibaka sino, abakulingeso osilita kame Amagelike mu ndoo ya Nyambe, mi na silafaza esibaka sino no kukena.  
\v 29 Kakuli kame ana kumumona oweli yo enda ni Tolofimo Omwiifese mu mulenen̄i, mi sebeli anahana nji Paulusi mwendi namu liti mu ndoo ya Nyambe. 
\p  
\v 30 Cwale omulenen̄i onje sebeli oimana amaefe-efe, mi aanu sebeli aituka ba bamweya, okalema Paulusi ni ku mukoka okumutundisa mu ndoo ya Nyambe mi ababo emyelo sebeli iyatiliwa.  
\v 31 Cwale aba ana kweteka nji amwibaye, eliywi sebeli liiya ku mwendisi no masole no Maloma nji Jelusalema yonje naimana ni mufilifili.  
\v 32 Mu nako imweya sebeli oshimba amasole na shebuluki oo, ni kwiitukela kwa onyene, cwale aba anakumona omwendisi ni masole, sebeli alesela okumufula.  
\v 33 Cwale omwendisi sebeli osheteta ni kulema Paulusi, ni ku laela nji anungiwe ni mawenge ayili. okubinda aibangute eyaye, nji yokame anyine, neeyo ana tende.  
\v 34 Anjili mu nyangela sebeli akuweleza sinu simweya, anjili sindina, mi sebeli okwangwa okulimukabo eniti mulibaka no lilata, sebeli nji Paulusi atwaliwe mu ndoo no kongola.  
\v 35 Cwale aba ana kukeela ba matulameno, konji oku shimbiwa ku Masole mulibaka no kutweba no nyangela.  
\v 36 Kakuli okupula nwaanu kame ana ku mukon̄anga, akuweleza nji, “Aibaiwe!” 
\s1 Paulusi Yoku Sileleza Yonyene 
\p  
\v 37 Paulusi yoli beebi ni kwingenyekwa mu ndoo no kongola, sebeli wamba ku mwendisi no masole nji, “Kame ni kumbela okwamba nowe?” 
\p Woyo sebeli omwibanguta nji, “Kame olimukile okwamba Esigelike?”  
\v 38 Kana kasa wene Omwengepita, uya, ona liti omufilifili mu maywaa aya anabu ni kwetelela aibai alume ana ku kwana eikiti inee (4;000) okuta noo mu lihalaupa?”  
\v 39 Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, “Mene kame nili Omujuda, okutundelela ku Tasusi mu Silisia, omulenen̄i noutokwa, Kame ni kumbela kwa wene nji naambe kwaanu.” 
\p  
\v 40 Cwale aba ana ku mulumelela, sebeli oimana aba noku tinena, mi sebeli okobeta aanu ni Lyoko, cwale aba kuna kondoka onene tuu, sebeli wamba noo mu puo no Sihebelu nji, 
\c 22  
\p  
\v 1 “Abaange naa sitange, muyupe aba ni kutambwela balubala wenu!”  
\v 2 Cwale aba ana kuyupa nji kame aambela mu puo no Mahehelu sebeli aondoka onene luli, mi sebeli wamba nji,  
\v 3 “Kame nili Omujuda, ona leyeliwa ku Tasusi mu Silisiya, kono kame nina kulele omuno mu mulenen̄i ku makondo a Gamaliele, mi kame nina iyetiwa no kupetahala okuta mu mukwa nwaa njekulyetu, ni kutukufalelwa eyi no Nyambe, kanyi omo mwiikalele balelo naanyi.  
\v 4 Kame nina lwisi onene Endila eyo mane oku twala ku lifu, kame nina kununganga alume bamweya naakati okwaa ingenyeka mu tolongo.  
\v 5 Omupulisita mukulu ni kuta no akulu onje kame ani paka. kame nina ku shimba aman̄olo okutunda kwaa onyene okutwala kwaabange, mi sebeli ni funduka okuta ku Damaseka nuukashimbamo aawo ana kwikalangamo ni kwaalita mu tololongo mu Jelusalema nji abiwe ekoto. 
\s1 Paulusi Yoamba Einokufuktuka kwaye 
\p  
\v 6 “Cwale abo meni lemine okweenda nji nishetete kunyonga ni Damaseka, omunji ba 12 okolokoluli olumonyi no kuneneba luna kutuda ku wilu ababo sebeli lunifuka.  
\v 7 Cwale sebeli nikwela banji ni kuyupa eliywi lyaamba kwa mene nji, ‘Suaule, Saule! Iikene oni yandiseta?’  
\v 8 Sebeli ni tambula nji, ‘Tiwe anyine, Mbumu?’ Cwale sebeli oni tambula nji, ‘Time Jesu no Nazaleta, woyo o yandisa.’  
\v 9 Cwale awo nina kwikala noo kame ana kumona olumonyi kono kasi kuyupa eliywi lya woyo ona kwamba kwa mene.  
\v 10 Cwale sebeli naamba nji, ‘Iikene nifanena okutenda, Mbumu?’ Mi Ombumu sebeli onambela nji, ‘Oimane, mi ote mu Damaseka, cwale omo kame soka ambelwe yonje eyo ofanena okutenda.’  
\v 11 Kakuli cwale kanisiku mona mulibakano kanya no lumonyi olo, kame nina kulemiwa ku Lyoko kwaao nina kweenda nooo okwingena mu Damaseka. 
\p  
\v 12 “Ananiasi, omulume onaku kubeeka kwa Nyambe okuta mu mukwa no mulawo, woyo opakwa kwaanu onje awo ayoyamo.  
\v 13 Cwale sebeli oiya kwa mene, ni kwiimana kunyonga yange, ni kwamba nji, ‘Saule minange, obiwe okumona kame!’ Mi mu nako eyeyo, sebeli ni mona ni ku mwaliketa.  
\v 14 Cwale ni kwamba nji, Nyambe nwaa njekulyetu nakukete nji olimuke eso asaela, okumona woyo no kuluka ni kuyupa ku liywi litunda mu kanwa kaye.  
\v 15 Kakuli kame sotende opaki waye kwaanu onje kweeyo ona mono ni kuyupa.  
\v 16 Cwale bano siikene osi tatelele? Oimane mi okolobezwe, mi oyowisiwe ku ibi yowe, wisane ba litina lyaye.’ 
\s1 Okwiisanwa kwa Paulusi oka Kutaza Kwaasimacaba 
\p  
\v 17 “Aba nina kumana okuukela ku Jelusalema ababo meni lapela mu ndoo ya Nyambe, sebeli ni mona epono,  
\v 18 ni ku mona Ombumu yo aamba kwa mene nji, ‘Olelube mi muwangu otunde mu Jelusalema, kakuli katamba ku tambula oupaki so ni pake.’  
\v 19 Cwale sebeli ni tambula nji, ‘Kame alimukile nji time nina kwiingenyekanga mu tolongo mu ndoo ni ndoo no milapelo ni kufulanga awo ana kupumenanga kwa wene.  
\v 20 Cwale ababo ounyinga wa Setefani opaki wowe aba ona kwiiteka, kame nina kwikalako, ni kupumena okwiibaiwa kwaye, ni kubabalela eikumango ya awo ana ku mwiibaa.’  
\v 21 Cwale sebeli wamba kwa mene nji, ‘Ote, kakuli kame sani kutume oku no kuleba kwaasimacaba.’ ” 
\s1 Paulusi Omuloma 
\p  
\v 22 Sebeli amuteeteta okutwala abo ana kwambela eliywi elyo, ababo sebeli atangisa okukuwa ni liywi lili beulu nji, “Omunu nongeso mu mutundise mu litunga, kafanene okuyoya!”  
\v 23 Sebeli akuwa ni kututula eikumango yoo ni ku tunyisa eliluli mu wilu.  
\v 24 Omwendisi no masole sebeli olaela nji alitiwe mu ndoo no kongola, nji aka mwibangute yo fuliwa nji alimuke eso amukuwela.  
\v 25 Kono aba ana kumana okumununga ni mihala no itumba, Paulusi sebeli oibanguta omwendisi ona kwimananga ba nyonga nji, “Kana nitukelo okufula omunu no Muloma, yo kasi atuliwa kale?” 
\p  
\v 26 Cwale onduna aba ana kuyupa ngeso, sebeli ota ku mweendisi no masole ni kwamba kwa onyene nji, “Siikene eso osinga okutenda? Kakuli omunu uyu ni Muloma!”  
\v 27 Cwale omwendisi no masole sebeli wiiya kwa Paulusi ni kumwibanguta nji, “Onambele, niti luli kame oleilwe ku Maloma?” 
\p Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, “Ee.” 
\p  
\v 28 Omwendisi no masole sebeli otambula nji, “Kame nina teneke amali no kupula nji nu kuulele etukelo eyo.” 
\p Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, “Kono mene ni mu kuleiwa.” 
\p  
\v 29 Cwale awo ana ku singa oku mufula sebeli amusiya ababo, omwendisi no masole ni yonyene sebeli ocila aba ana kuyupa nji Muloma, kakuli kame ana ku mununga. 
\s1 Paulusi yooli booso no Kuta 
\p  
\v 30 Kono eliywaa aba lina kupa, mu kusinga oku limuka elibaka no niti eyo amuzekiseta aendisi no Majuda, omwendisi no masole sebeli onungutula Paulusi, ni ku laelela apulisita akulu naa sikuta onje nji akuwane, sebeli ota ni Paulusi ni ku mubeeka balubala woo. 
\c 23  
\p  
\v 1 Paulusi yo alikete onene asi Kuta no Majuda sebeli wamba nji, “Abaange, kame ninaende ni lizwalo no kuwaba koonje balubala wa Nyambe, okulita ba liywaa no balelo lino.”  
\v 2 Cwale Ananiyasi omupulisita mukulu sebeli olaela awo ana kwimananga kunyonga yaye nji amupobole ba kanwa,  
\v 3 Cwale Paulusi sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Nyambe mba ku pobola, wene elimota libasizwe elikena! Kandi aba oikalile bano ni ku naatula okuta mu mulawo, kandi aba olaela nji nipoboliwe, kame ocola omulawo!” 
\p  
\v 4 Awo ana kwimananga ku nyonga yaye, sebeli aamba nji, “Weene kame okuta omupulisita mukulu wa Nyambe?” 
\p  
\v 5 Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, “Abaange, kanisi limuka nji mupulisita mukulu kakuli kame ku n̄olilwe nji, ‘Olese okwamba eyi no kwiiba ku mwendisi no aanu owe.’ ” 
\p  
\v 6 Cwale Paulusi mu kulimuka nji anjili neli Asaduki mi anjili neli Afalisi, sebeli okuwa mu Kuta nji, “Abaange, mene kame nili omufalisi, o mwana no mufalisi, kame naatulwa mulibakano kwinguka nwaafu kame nili mu muliko!”  
\v 7 Cwale aba ana kumana okwamba eyo, omufilifili sebeli winguka mukaci no Afalisi naa Saduki, mi esikwata sebeli sikutaba bakaci.  
\v 8 Kakuli Asaduki kame aamba nji kakwisa okwinguka kwaafu, simba elin̄eloi, simba Emebo, kono Afalisi kame apumena eyo yonje.  
\v 9 Cwale sebeli kwinguka elilata no kuneneba luli, mi anjili aiyeti no mualao aa aimanena Afalisi, sebeli aimana ni kwamba nji, “Ka tusiwana esi sifosahalile kwa yonyene uyu mulume! Mwendi ni mebo simba elin̄eloi yaamba mwa yonyene!” 
\p  
\v 10 Cwale Omufilifii aba onaku ekezeha, omwendisi no masole sebeli ocila nji Paulusi mba kaolwa mu ibindi kwa onyene, ni ku laela amasole okushetumuka okashimba Paulusi mukaci koo ni ku mulita mu ndoo no kongola. 
\p  
\v 11 Ousiku ona kutatamako Ombumu sebeli oimana kunyonga yaye ni kwamba nji, “Olese kucila, kakuli kanyi aba ona paka eyange mu Jelusalema, cwale ni mu Loma kame ofanena okanipaka ngeso.” 
\s1 Omulelo no Kwibaa Paulusi 
\p  
\v 12 Cwale eliywaa aba lina kupa, Amjuda anjili sebeli akuwana okulela ni kweeta nji katamba kulya simba okunwa konji aba saibae Paulusi.  
\v 13 Awo ana ku tenda omulelo owo, neli aanu ana kubitelela makumi anee.  
\v 14 Cwale sebeli ata kwa mupulisita omukulu ni kwaakulu, ni kwamba nji, “Kame tuna kunungu oluci nji ka tutamba kulya esinjili konji aba satwiibae Paulusi oweli.  
\v 15 Abakulingeso, anyi naasi Kuta mu simwete omwendisi no masole amulite kwaanyi, mi munise kanyi kame musinga okusaisisa etitaba taye. “Cwale aci kame tukutukisite oku mwibaa yo kasikeela kale kwaanyi.” 
\p  
\v 16 Kono omwana mandaye Paulusi no mushimani aba ana kuyupa emifumbo yoo, sebeli ota mu ndoo no kongola okasimweta Paulusi.  
\v 17 Cwale Paulusi sebeli oisana omunjili no abaleki ni kwamba nji, “Otwale uyu ndumbana ku mwendisi no masole, kakuli kame ali nesi asaela okumwambela.”  
\v 18 Cwale sebeli omushimba ni kumutwala ku mwendisi no masole ni kwamba nji, “Paulusi omupantiti kame anani isana ni kuni kumbela nji nilite uyu ndumbana kwa wene, kakuli kame kuli eso asaela okwamba kwa wene.” 
\p  
\v 19 Omwendisi no masole sebeli omulema ku Lyoko, ni kuta naye ku nyonga ni ku mwibanguta nji, “Siikene eso osaela oku naambela?” 
\p  
\v 20 Cwale sebeli wamba nji, “aendisi no Majuda kame ana kuyupu nji aku kumbele nji byuunda waalitele Paulusi ku Kuta yoo, atende kanyi kame asaele okusaisisa etaba yaye.  
\v 21 Kono olese okwaa lumelela, kakuli alume no kubitelela amakumi anee awo ana mukundamene, kame akunungile oluci nji katamba okulya simba oku nwa esinjili koonji aba sa ibae Paulusi oweli. Cwale kame aku tukisite, ni kutatelela esepiso okutunda kwa wene.” 
\p  
\v 22 Cwale omwendisi no masole sebeli ousa ondumbana, ni ku mulaela nji, “Olese okwambela omunu nji nunambele etaba eyi.” 
\s1 Paulusi yo tumiwa kwa Mubusisi Felikisi 
\p  
\v 23 Cwale sebeli oisana aendisi ayiili no masole ni kwamba nji, “Ba nako no 9 okoloko (21) ousiku mu kutukisete mu shimbe amasole akwana emyanda yiili (200) ni timbii makumi mutanu naayili, (70) naalume akwana emyanda yiili (200) asikulwisa etimbi nji ate ku Sesaaliya.  
\v 24 Mulukise ni tipeleswa eto sa titiniwe kwa Paulusi, mi mumutwale wino kwa Felikisi omubusisi.”  
\v 25 Cwale sebeli on̄ola elin̄olo eli lyaamba nji, 
\p  
\v 26 “Mene Kilaudiyasi Lisiyasi kwa Felikisi, omubusisi okutekiwa onene, mulumele.  
\v 27 Omunu woyo kame ana kulemiwa ku Majuda, mi kame ana ku singa oku mwibaa, cwale mukuyupa nji ni muloma sebeli niiya ni masole oku muyoyisa.  
\v 28 Cwale mu kusinga nji ni limuke eyo amulwiseta, sebeli ni mutwala ku Kuta yoo.  
\v 29 Omo sebeli ni wana nji kame amu zekisa mu yambo no mulawo woo, kono kakwisa omubonda owo ofanena elifu simba okunungiwa.  
\v 30 Cwale aba nina kumana okuyupa nji munu woyo kame ana kundamenwa, ababo sebeli ni mutumena kwa wene, mi kame nina laelele awo amuzekisa nji eyo amuzekiseta ailite kwa wene .” 
\p  
\v 31 Cwale amasole, sebeli atenda omo ana laelelwe, okushimba Paulusi ni kumulita ousiku ku Antipatilisi.  
\v 32 Cwale eliywaa aba lina kupa sebeli aukela ku ndoo no kongola, okusiya asikutina etimbii aata ni Paulusi.  
\v 33 Cwale aba anaku keela mu Sesaaliya, sebeli aba omubusisi elin̄olo, mane niku lita Paulusi kwa yonyene.  
\v 34 Omubusisi aba ana kumana okubala elin̄olo, sebeli oibanguta Paulusi nji kame atunda ku tolopo ibine. Cwale aba ana kuyupa nji kame atunda mu Silisiya,  
\v 35 sebeli wamba nji, “Kame sani yupe eyowe aba sakeele awo akuzekisa.” Cwale sebeli olaela nji atatelelwe mu ndoo ya Heloda. 
\c 24  
\s1 Paulusi yo Zekisiwa 
\p  
\v 1 Munyima no maywaa mutanu omupulisita mukulu Ananiyasi sebeli oiya nakulu anjili nimutalusi wisanwa Tetulusi. Mi sebeli akumonahaza kwa mubusisi oku talusa eyi ya Paulusi.  
\v 2 Cwale aba ana ku mwiisana, Tetulusi sebeli otangisa oku muhapeleza okwamba nji, 
\p “Aba tu yoya mu kozo no kuneneba ni mwa wene, mu kubiwa kwetu kwa wene, wene Felekisi no kukutekeha, einu no kupula kame itandahala mwa wene muno mu litunga.  
\v 3 Mundila yonje ni kubine konje kame twiitambula mu witumelo no kuneneba.  
\v 4 Kono nji nilese oku sinyeza enako, kame niku kumbela mu sishemo sowe otutetete kweyo tu kwambela.  
\v 5 Kakuli kame tu nawana woyo mulume nji mususwezi omunya tiputeho no Majuda onje mu litunga lyonje, yokame omutwi no tuto no kukeluha no Anazaleta.  
\v 6 Kame ana eteke mane okusilafaza Endoo ya Nyambe, kono natu muleme.  
\v 7 Kono omwendisi no masole Lisiasi, sebeli okeela ni ku mushimba mu maata no kuneneba, okutu byangulaye.  
\v 8 Mu ku mwibanguta mwenyene mba mulimuka okutundelela mwa yonyene einu yonje eyo tu munyaza.”  
\v 9 aendisi no Majuda noyonyene sebeli apumena nji eyo amunyaza ni yaniti.  
\v 10 Cwale omubusisi aba ana kwamba kwa yonyene, Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, 
\p “Mu ku limuka nji mu myaka no kupula kame ona tende omwatuli no litunga eli, kame ni wabelelwe okuba oupaki wange.  
\v 11 Kanyi omo olimukele nji kakusibita amaywaa likumi naayiili aba nino katunda ku Jelusalema mu kulaapela.  
\v 12 Kono kasikuniwana meni kanana naanu simba okususweza esicaba, simba mu keleke, simba mu tindoo no milapelo, simba mu mulenen̄i.  
\v 13 Simba mane okulita kwa wene esisupo kweeyo aamba eyange.  
\v 14 Kono kweeyi kame ni pumena kwa wene, nji okukumanena ni Ndila eyo aisaniwa kunyefula, kame ni lapela Nyambe no asitetu ni kupumena einu onje eyo ina lyatisiwa mu mualao simba eyi ina n̄oliwa kwaanuhi a Nyambe.  
\v 15 Mulibaka nokwikala ni sepo kwa Nyambe neyo nonyene apumena, nji okwinguka kwao no kuluka nawo nakwaluka,  
\v 16 mi cwale kame netekanga onene nji ni ikale ni lizwalo kuneku la Nyambe ni aanu.  
\v 17 Aba kuna kubita emyaka sebli ni lita etituso ni timpo ku Jelusalema kwaanu no kusheba.  
\v 18 Meni lemine okutenda eyi, sebeli aniwana me kenine mu Ndoo ya Nyambe, okuulwile esicaba ni mifilifili. Kono aendisi no Majuda anjili ana kutunda ku Esiya  
\v 19 kame afanena okukeela kwaanyi nji kame anyaza nji kame kuli esinjili eso nina foso.  
\v 20 Abakulingeso mu lesele aa alume onyene aambe eso nina kufosa aba nina kwimana balubala no Kuta,  
\v 21 konji esinu simweya eso nina kwamba meni imanine mukaci koo, ‘Ni ku kuteka okwinguka nwaafu eyo ni zekisiwa mu liywaa no balelo lino.’ ” 
\p  
\v 22 Kono Felekisi woyo ona kulimuka wino Endila, sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Aba sa keele Lisiyasi omendisi, okubinda sani nahane etaba yenu.”  
\v 23 Cwale sebeli oba etaelo ku mwendisi no masole nji iakale mu kutateleliwa nji mu kulukuluha mi aalikani aye abiwe ekolo no kumulitela eyo asela. 
\p  
\v 24 Munyima no maywaa, Felekisi sebeli oiya ni moyo waye Dulusila ona kutenda Omujuda, mi sebeli otumena Paulusi ni kuyupa yo aamba mu tumelo mwa Jesu Kilesite.  
\v 25 Yo lemine okwambola eyi no niti neyi no kuluka ni nuukulema mane ni katulo na kuuso, Felekisi yonyene sebeli ocila ni kwamba nji, “Ba nakon ino ote oweli. Cwale aba sani wane esibaka mba ni kwiisana.”  
\v 26 Ba nako imweya sebeli ohupula nji kame sabiwe amali kwa Paulusi. Cwale sebeli omutumena aka no kupula nikamba kwayonyena.  
\v 27 Kono aba ina kubwa eilimo yiili, Felekisi kame ana kuyoliwa kwa Polosiusi Festusi, ni ku laekaza okutenda aendisi no Majuda ouwa, Felekisi sebeli osiya Paulusi mu tolongo. 
\c 25  
\s1 Paulusi yo Kumbela kwa Sizale 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale Fesitasi aba ana keela aye, munyima no aywaa aatu, sebeli okambamena ku Jelusalema okutunda mu Sesaliya.  
\v 2 Omupulisita mukulu naakulu no majuda sebeli akumonahaza kwa yonyene, mi sebeli abiha kwayonyene okukumanena neya Paulusi.  
\v 3 mi sebeli akumbela nji atende mukwaawabelisa nji aatumene Paulusi ku Jelusalema, okulela okumu kundamena nji amwibae ba ndila.  
\v 4 Fesitusi sebeli otambula nji, Paulusi kame ali mu Sesaaliya, ni kwamba nji ni yonyene okutwa atemo abano.  
\v 5 Cwale sebeli waamaba nji, “Mu lusele alume aali ni tukelo mukaci kenu ashetumuke ni mene, mi nji kame kuli eso sina fosahala mwa yonyene, aiye mukumuhapeleza.” 
\p  
\v 6 Cwale aba ana ku mana okwikala noo mu maywaa no kwaakwana mutanu ni twaatu simba likumi, sebeli oukela ku Sesaaliya. Ba liywaa lina kutatamako sebeli oikala ba situlo no katulo, mi sebeli olaelela nji Pulusi alitiwe.  
\v 7 Cwale aba ana kwiiya, aendisi no Majuda ana kutunda ku Jelusalema sebeli amubeeka mukaci, ni ku hapeleza emibonda no kupula eyo akwangwa okulita oupaki wayo.  
\v 8 Paulusi yonyene sebeli okutambwela nji, “Kanisifoseza omulawo no Majuda, simba Endoo ya Nyambe, simbsa Sesale kanisi mufoseza simba kanyonyo.”  
\v 9 Kono Fesitusi muku singa oku wabeliswa aendisi no Majuda, sebeli wamba kwa Paulusi nji, “Ninji kame osaela okuta ku Jelusalema, mi omo oka atulwemo eyambo eto balubala wange?”  
\v 10 Kono Paulusi sebeli wamba nji, “Kame niimanine balubala no Kuta ya Sesale, moni lukela okwatulwela, Ku Majuda kanisifoza simba simyeya, kanyi omo olimukele wino ni wene.  
\v 11 Nji cwale kame nina matuka omulawo, nikutenda esinjili eso sifanena elifu, sikana okufa, kono nji kakwisa eniti mu yambo eyo aninungelela, kakwisa woyo sonibeeka mu maata oo. Kame niku lilelela kwa Sesale.”  
\v 12 Cwale Festusi aba ana ku kwaambota nasikuta yaye, sebeli otambula nji, “Kame ona bilaelele kwa Sesale, kame soote kwa Sesale.” 
\s1 Paulusi booso wa Agipa ni Benisi 
\p  
\v 13 Cwale munyima no maywaa acana aba ana kubwa, Aglipa ombumu ni Belunice sebeli akeela mu Sesaaliya mu kutambula Felstusi.  
\v 14 Cwale aba ana kwikalamo amaywaa no kupula, Festusi sebeli wambela Ombumu eyambo ta Paulusi nji, “Kuno kame kuli omulume ona siiwa mu tolongo kwa Felekisi.  
\v 15 Aba nina kwikala ku Jelusalema, apulisita akulu naakulu no Majuda kame ana kwiiya kwa mene mukuni simweta eyambo ya Paulusi, ni kukumbela nji aatulelwe elifu.  
\v 16 Kono sebeli naatambula nji kasa tukelo no sizo no Maloma okulumelela okwatuliwa abo omuzeki ni muzekisi kaasikuwana kale olubala ni lubala mane ni kubiwa okolo noukutambwela mu yambo yaye eyo amuzekisa.  
\v 17 Cwalehe abo aneeyi bamweya kuno, kanasiku liyeha, kono eliywaa linakutatamako sebeli niikala ba situlo no katulo ni ku laela nji alitiwe balubala no Kuta.  
\v 18 Cwale azekisi aye aba ana kwiimana, kasaamba esinjili no mibonda yaye eyo ana ku mununga, kanyi eyo nina kutatelela nji niiyupe.  
\v 19 Kono kame ana kwikala ni ngambolo naye eyi no tumelo yoo neyi no munjili woyo wiisaniwa nji Jesu, woyo ona kufa, kono Paulusi kame aongota nji kame ayoya.  
\v 20 Mulibaka no kuziyeleha mu yambo no ngeso, sebeli ni mwibanguta nji kautwese okuta ku Jelusalema nji okaatulelweko etaba eyi.  
\v 21 Kono cwale Paulusi sebeli okumbela nji abekiwe mu sitokisi okutatela ekatulo no Mbumu omukulu, sebeli ni laela nji ababalelwe okubitela aba sanimu tumene kwa Sesale.” 
\p  
\v 22 Cwale Aglipa sebeli wamba kwa Festusi nji, “Kame ni singa okuyupa wkwa woyo mulume.” 
\p Festusi sebeli otambula nji, “Mbumumono byuunda,” 
\s1 Paulusi Booso wa Aglipa 
\p  
\v 23 Cwale eliywaa aba lina kupa Aglipa ni Belunice sebeli aiya mu umbumu no kuneneba ni kwiingena mu Kuta aali naendisi no masole, naanu akulu no mulenen̄i. Cwale mu taelo ya Fesitusi, Paulusi sebeli olitiwa.  
\v 24 Cwale Fesitasi sebeli wamba nji, “Mbumu Aglipa nawo onje aikalile naaci muno, mumumwine omulume woyo aneyele aendisi no Majuda no kupula kwa mene mu ku muzekisa, bamweya mu Jelusalema ni muno, sebeli akuweleza nji kalukeele okuyoya kame.  
\v 25 Kono kame nina wana nji kakwisa omubonda anatende owo ofanena elifu, yonyene kame ana kubilaeze okuta kwa Sesale, kame ni nawana oku mutumenako.  
\v 26 Kono sikwite eso ni lukela okun̄olela kwa Sisale eso no niti mu taba yaye. Cwalehe kame nina muliti balubala lwenu, onene balubala lowe wene luli Ombumu Aglipa, nji munyima no kwamba etaba yaye, ni limuke eso sani twese okun̄ola.  
\v 27 Kakuli kwa mene ni taba nokwa yupahala aba sa ku tumiwe omunu no kunungiwa, ka kumonisiwa eyambo ana zekisiwa.” 
\c 26  
\s1 Paulusi yoku Tambwela balubala lwa Aglipa 
\p  
\v 1 Aglipa sebeli wamba kwa Paulusi nji, “Kame opumenenwe nji waambe.” Cwale Paulusi sebeli olola elikaa lyaye ni kwamba nji, 
\p  
\v 2 “Kame ni kwite etitonolo okwikala balubala lowe wene ombumu Aglipa, mi kame sa nibe oupaki wange wonje ku yambo eto anitamilikeza a majuda.  
\v 3 Kakuli wene olimukile emilao ni yambo eyo kasingi a majuda, cwale kame ni kukumbela nji oni tetete wino. 
\p  
\v 4 “Omooyo wange okutunda ku wanuke, inaikala okutunda kumatatekelo mu sicaba no abaange mane ni ku Jelusalema, kame a ulimukile oonje a majuda.  
\v 5 Kakuli kame au limukile, nji kame saela okupaka eniti, nji okukumanena ni ulapeli kame inakuyoya kanyi mufalisi.  
\v 6 Mi bano kame ni imana kuti ni atulwe mu sepo eyo a na ku sepisa Nyambe kwa sitetu,  
\v 7 eyo emishobo yetu likumu ni yiili asepile okawana, abo sa lapele mu niti omunji ni usiku, mi musepiso eyi ya ni nyaza nayo aendisi no Majuda.  
\v 8 Aanyi nji nisinu sikwangwiwa oku pumena nji Nyambe kame atwesa okwingula asikufa? 
\p  
\v 9 “Mene menyene, niti luli kame nina yambuta nji kame nina kufanena okutenda einu no kupula mu kulwisa elitina lya Jesu no Nazaleta.  
\v 10 Kame nini ku tenda ngeso mu Jelusalema, oku yatilela aasikupumena mu tolongo, oku tunda mu maata nina kubiwa kwa apulisita akulu, kono cwale aba ana kwaatulela elifu, ni mene sebeli ni pumena okwaalwisa.  
\v 11 Aka no kupula mu tindoo no milapelo tonje kame nina kwakandimekanga nji anyefule, mi kakuli kame nina kwaatwebela ouyi, sebeli nikaayandisa mu milenen̄i indina. 
\s1 Pauluso yooba oupaki waye 
\r (Tikezo9.1-19; 22.6-16) 
\p  
\v 12 “Mane sebeli nita ku Damaseka mu maata ni mu taelo no apulisita akulu.  
\v 13 Omunji luli Molyange, sebeli ni mona olumonyi menili mu ndila luna kutunda ku wilu, no ku benya onene okubitelela eliseli no liywaa, sebeli linibeeka mukaci na nina kweenda noo.  
\v 14 Cwale aba tuna kukwela banji tonje, sebeli ni yupa eliywi elyaamba kwa mene mu mushobo no Sihebelu nji, ‘Saule,Saule, iikene oniyandiseta? Kame olemana aba olaha ku muwayo.’  
\v 15 Cwale sebeli ni ibanguta nji, ‘Tiwe anyine, Mbumu?’ Ombumu sebeli otambula nji, ‘Time Jesu woyo olemine okuyandisa.  
\v 16 Kono oinguke mi wimane ni makondo owe, kakuli kame nina kumonaha kwa wene mulibaka eli, oku kuketa nji osebeze nikuba oupaki mweyo ona mono ni kweyo saniku monahaze nayo mwa wene otenda opaki no inu ino.  
\v 17 Kame sani ku lamulele kwaanu aa ni kwasimacaba oko ni ku tumena kwa onyene.  
\v 18 Nji otonise amiyo oo, nji afutuke okutunda mu uwi okuta mu liseli ni mu maata no Satani ni kusiulukela kwa Nyambe, ni ku lemeniwa ku iibi yoo, mi ni sibaka saawo akenine ni ku pumena mwa mene.’ 
\s1 Paulusi yo ambaa eyi no musebezi waye 
\p  
\v 19 “Okutunda abo, Molyange Mbumu Aglipa, kani sikana oku yupa ku pono na kuwilu.  
\v 20 Kono sebeli olemusa oweli ali ku Daseka, cwale ni mu Jelusalema ni mu naha yonje no Judeya, mane ngeeso ni kwaa simacaba, nji kam e afanena oku baka ni ku futukela kwa Nyambe ni ku tenda emisebezi eyo ilukela awo ana baka.  
\v 21 Mulibaka elyo aendisi no Majuda lyokame anani nungele eyambo mu Ndoo ya Nyambe elyo asinga okuni ibaela.  
\v 22 Mu liywaa no balelelo kame nina wana etuso okutunda kwa Nyambe, mi cwale kame niimana bano okuba oupaki kwaakkulu bamweya naanyonyo, kakwisa eso naamba kono eyo anaamba anuhi a Nyambe ni Mushe mbaitendahala,  
\v 23 nji Jesu mbayanda, mi cwale yokame no weeli okwinguka kwaanu, mi kame saambe eliseli kwaanu ni kwaasimacaba.” 
\p  
\v 24 Cwale Paulusi yooba oupaki waye, Fesitusi sebeli wamba ni liywi linene nji, Paulusi, kame olyangana, oukwiiyeta kowe no kuneneba kame ku kupulumukisa!”  
\v 25 Kono Paulusi sebeli wamba nji, “Mene, sitakana, molyange Fesitasi, kono kame naamba eniti luli.  
\v 26 Kakuli Ombumu oilimukile eyi inu, mi kwayonyene kame naamba meni lukuluhile, kakuli kame ni pumena nji einu eyi kakwisa eso kalimukile. kakuli eyo kaisiku tendahalela ku mukunda.  
\v 27 Mbumu Aglipa, kana kame opumena kwaanuhi a Nyambe? Kame nilimukile nji kame opumena!”  
\v 28 Cwale Aglipa sebeli wamba kwa Paulusi nji, “Mu nako ino inyonyo kame osinga nji ni futuke omuasikupumena?”  
\v 29 Paulusi sebeli otambula nji, “Simba enako inyonyo simba no kupula, kame ni twesa kwa Nyambe nji kasa wene feela kono nawo onje aniyupa mu liywaa lino kame safeke kanyi mene, konji fela amawenge.”  
\v 30 Cwale Ombumu sebeli oimana, ni mubusisi ni Benisi, naao ana kwikala noo,  
\v 31 mi cwale aba ana kumana okunda ba Kuta, sebeli akwambisa mukaci koo nji, “Uyu mulume kakwisa eso ana tende nji aatulelwe elifu simba okunungiwa mu tolongo.”  
\v 32 Cwale Aglipa sebeli wamba kwa Festusi nji, “Uyu mulume kame afanena oku lukululwa kambe kasi ku litiwa balubala wa Sesale.” 
\c 27  
\s1 Paulusi Yota ku Loma 
\p  
\v 1 Cwale abo abaabna kulumelelana nji ate mu Italiya, sebeli atwala Paulusi ni mapantiti anjili ku mukulu no masole Juliusi no sikwata no Augusto.  
\v 2 Aba ana kumana okwingena mu sisepe no Adlamiti, eso sina kufunduka ku likamba lya Asia sebeli tu fuula aaci ni Alisitako na mu ku Tesalonika omundi na mu Mesadoniya.  
\v 3 Eliywaa lina ku tatamako sebeli tu kakeela mu Sidoni, mi Juliyasi sebeli obabalela wino Paulusi, ni ku mufundula nji ate kwaabaye aka mu babalele.  
\v 4 Cwale sebeli amubeeka mu sisepe sina kuta ku Sipulasi, kakuli Emebo kame ina ku tulwisa.  
\v 5 Cwale aba tunakumana okuluta eliwate eli lita ku Silisia ni Pamifilia, sebei tu keela mu Mila mu Lisiya.  
\v 6 Omwendisi no masole sebeli owanamo esisepe sa Alekizanda eso sina kuta ku Italia sebeli otubeekamo. 
\p  
\v 7 Kame tuna kweenda mu kwaleluba mu maywaa no kupula, mi sebeli tu kakeela ku Silisia mu ku bambaba, mikanyi Emebo aba ina kutukanena oku luta sebeli tu kulisa ku nyonga ya Kilete ku lineku lya Salumoni.  
\v 8 Me tu kulisa elikamba mu kubambaba, sebeli twiiya mu sibaka siisaniwa Feya Habenisi, abeebi ni mulenen̄i no Lasea. 
\p  
\v 9 Mu kusinya enako no kupula, mi omusipili sebeli ocilisa kakuli okweti kame ina kubwa, cwale Paulusi sebeli waaeleza nji,  
\v 10 “Aolyange, kame ni mwene nji omusipili kame so ikale ni tikolofalo ni kusinyehelwa onene, kasa eibyana fela ni sisepe, kono bamweya ni moyo wetu.”  
\v 11 Kono omwendisi no masole sebeli obeeka etingana ku mwendisi ni munya sisepe okubita eyo ana kwamba Paulusi.  
\v 12 Cwale mulibaka no likamba okwa lukela oku fuwekelamo ba nako no mubebo, aanu no kupula sebeli aaeleza nji afuwekela fela mu liwate, mu litohonolo nji mba twese okakeela ku Fenekasi mu likamba no Kilete, elyo lyalikete ku mutulo ni upa, ni mbowela ni upa, okapumulelamo omubebo. 
\s1 Elin̄ungwa ba Liwate 
\p  
\v 13 Cwale Emebo naku mbowela aba ifuka wino, sebeli ahupula nji, omulelo woo mbaukondo, niku mona Ankola, sebeli afuula okukulisa amakamba no Kilete ao ali beebi ni likamba.  
\v 14 Kono kuuso mbicana sebeli kwinguka Emebo no lin̄ungwa elyo lisaniwa Eulakilo.  
\v 15 Cwale esisepe ba si nakushimbiwa ku mebo, sebeli sikwangwa oku yaliketa, sebeli tusi lesela sita nayo.  
\v 16 Cwale sebeli tu kashetwa kunji no sooli no Kilauda, ni kusinga okukwangwa oku kokela esisepe sicana.  
\v 17 Aba ana kumana okanona, sebeli ongota esisepe mu kusinunga emihala eyo ikeela kunji, mi mulibaka nji kame ana kucila okukashetwa ba muuwa naku Silete, sebeli akwisa amaseili ni kukuka yongeso.  
\v 18 Kakuli kame tuna ku lwisiwa ku mebo no lin̄ungwa, mu liywaa lina kutatamako sebeli atateka okukondela etutu yoo mu liwate eyo ina longiwa mu sisepe,  
\v 19 mi ba liywaa no waatu sebeli tu kondela ni maoko etu, einu eyo yendisa esisepe nayo.  
\v 20 Cwale eliywaa simba etitungweti kaisiku moniwa mu mywaa no kupula, mi eliwate kame lina bifi ouyi ku mebo, mane sebeli tuulwa esepo nji mbatu yoisiwa. 
\p  
\v 21 Cwale aba ana kwikala amaywaa no kupula aulwile esi no kulya, Paulusi cwale sebeli oiya kwa onyene ni kwaamba nji, “Alume, kambe kame muna kuni pumena oweli me musi fuula kale ku Kilete, kambe kamusiilwa okulemana ni ku sinyehelwa.  
\v 22 Kono cwale kame ni mi kutaza, mu koongote, kakuli kakwisa woyo so sinyehelwa omoyo kono kame sa ku sinyeha fela esisepe.  
\v 23 Kakuli ouno usiku elin̄eloi lya Nyambe nali kumonahaza kwa mene nili waye woyo ni sebeleza  
\v 24 mi sebeli lyaamba nji, ‘Paulusi olese okucila, kame so kaimane balubala lwa Sesale, mi omone, Nyambe nakubi onje awo oluta noo mu sisepe.’  
\v 25 Cwale mongole emicima, alume! Kakuli kame nili ni tumelo mwa Nyambe nji kame sa ku tendahale kanyi omo nina ambelwe.  
\v 26 Kono kame sa tu twaliwe ku yooli injili.” 
\s1 Okulwela No Sisepe 
\p  
\v 27 Cwale eliywaa no likumi ni tunee aba lina kukeela, me tu twaliwa oku nooku ku mebo mu liwate no Andilia, mu kaci no usiku aapuwi no sisepe sebeli akakanya nji natu keela ku naha injili.  
\v 28 Cwale aba aana kweteka ouliba no meyi sebeli awana eibima makumi aatu ni twiili, kuuso mbicana sebeli aeteka kame sebeli awana eibima makumi ayiili ni mutanu ni twiili.  
\v 29 Kame ana kucila nji mwendi mba tu twaliwa ku mebo ba mawee, sebeli akwisa amanjanga anee na mu litusi na kunyima nji esisepe siimane, mi kame ana ku lakaza nji kupee.  
\v 30 Cwale aapuwi no sisepe sebeli asaela oku luta okutunda mu sisepe, okwingena mu sisepe sicana mu liwate kanyi kame akakwisa atiankola na ku litusi na ku uso.  
\v 31 Paulusi sebeli osimweta omwendisi no masole ni masole nji, “Konji aa alume aba saikale mu sisepe, okubinda samu yoye.”  
\v 32 Cwale amasole sebeli apatula omuhala no sisepe, ni kuulesela okutela. 
\p  
\v 33 Cwale eliywaa ekalya sipa kale, Paulusi sebeli waakumbela onje nji alye eilya, ni kwamba nji, “Balelo yakwana kale amywaa likumi ni anee me mutatelele nuuku yumena eilya, memu ulwile esi no kulya.  
\v 34 Cwalehe kame ni mikumbela nji mulye esilya, mbaimibi okongola, kakuli kakwisa oluuki na ba mutwi no munu ni munu kwaanyi olo salu sinyehe.”  
\v 35 Cwale aba ana kumana okwamba eyi, sebeli oshimba esinkwa, nuukutumela kwa Nyambe balubala woo onje ni ku sipatola ni ku tangisa okulya.  
\v 36 Cwale sebeli aongola emicima ni kulya eilya nonyene.  
\v 37 Kame tunaku kwana epalo ikuma ba myaanda yiili ni makumi mutanu naayili ni mutanu ni kamweya (276) aanu mu sisepe.  
\v 38 Cwale aba ana kumana okulya wino, sebeli afukuza kukulema no sisepe oku yumbela ouloto mu liwate. 
\p  
\v 39 Cwale aba lina kupa eliywaa, kasi kulimuka enaha eyo nji ibine, mi sebeli alemuha esiko sili ni likamba, cwale sebeli asinga nji aba kukonahala atwalemo esisepe.  
\v 40 Cwale sebeli apatula emihala ina nungu etinkola ni kwisiya mu liwate, mi mu nako imweya ni kusheputula emihala eyo inungile amabala no ku siululisa esisepe, mi ni ku imeka eseili no kuneneba ba libala no sisepe nji cwale Emebo aba ifulabo yaatwale ku likamba.  
\v 41 Kono sebeli tu fuwama bamwalala no mushekesheke eso sili ni meyi oku nooku. Elitusi nakunyima sebeli licoka, cwale eli nakuuso sebeli likakatela ba mushekesheke 
\p  
\v 42 Omuhupulo no masole neli nji aibae amapantiti, okwaa sileleza nji alese okuyowa ni ku sila.  
\v 43 Kono omwendisi no masole mu ku singa okuyoisa Paullusi, sebeli waakanisa, mi ni ku laele nji aa atwesa okuyowa, amatukele oweeli mu liwate ate ba likamba,  
\v 44 mi anjili aku tusise amabala, anjili baibindi ina coko no sisepe. Cwale mokame omo ana ku keelela ba likamba, aayoya. 
\c 28  
\s1 Mu Melita 
\p  
\v 1 Munyima no kuyoya ngeso, okubinda cwale tu limuke nji esooli eso kame siisaniwa nji Melita.  
\v 2 Ni man̄eke aa alimo sebeli atutenda mu sishemo no kuneneba, ni kutu tambula toonje omunu ni munu, mi sebeli atumbula omulilo no kuneneba, mulibaka no mbula ona kuloka ni mulibaka no seenge.  
\v 3 Cwale Paulusi sebeli ocaa en̄ata no wandilala no itondo no kuku kuta ni kwibeeka ba mulilo, omo sebeli kutunda esibili mulibaka no kweenya, sebeli siku tingeta ba Lyoko lyaye.  
\v 4 Cwale aman̄ete aba ana ku mona enyoka ilepelela ba Lyoko lyaye, sebeli akwambisa mukaci koo nji, “Luli omunu uyu ni mwiibai, kakuli naaba aba bandukamu liwate, ouku faniketa ku wilu kalukele okuyoya.  
\v 5 Kono Paulusi sebeli otutulele fela enyoka mu mulilo kaisimu tenda ouyi.  
\v 6 Aanu kame ana kutatelela okumona nji kame sa timbe simba okukwela banji ababo nji afe, kono kame ana kutatelela ba nako no kuleba onene, mi sebeli amona nji kakwisa esi sitendahala kwa yonyene, sebeli afutuka okwamba nji neli nyambe. 
\p  
\v 7 Abeebi ni sibaka eso tuna kwikala kame kuna kwikala onduna no sooli wisaniwa nji Pubuliyasi, ni yonyene sebeli otu tambula wino, niku tushimba ku ndoo yaye amaywaa aatu.  
\v 8 Sitaye Publiusi kame ana ku langana okukola efibele ni ku sulula ounyinga. Pauusi sebeli otako oka mulekula ni kulapela, sebeli omu beeka amaoko aye beeulu niku mubalisa.  
\v 9 Eyo aba ina kubwa, onje aanu asikutoma ba sooli sebei aiya, mi kame ana ku balisiwa.  
\v 10 Cwale sebeli atuba etimpo no kupula, mi aba tuna ku fuula, sebeli atubeekela mu sisepe eyo tuna ku saela. 
\s1 Oku tunda mu Malite okuta ku Loma 
\p  
\v 11 Munyima no tikweti taatu sebeli tu funduka ni sisepe sina ku fuwekelanga musoli, esisepe na ku Alekizandiliya, mi balitusi ababekilwe esiswaniso no aana no mambile  
\v 12 Aba tu na kukeela mu Silakuze sebeli twi ikalamo amaywaa aatu.  
\v 13 Mi aba tu na kufundaka sebeli twenda ku nyonga no liwate mi sebeli tu kakela ku Lihegiomu, mi munyima no liywaa limweya Emebo naku mboela sebeli ifuka, mi ba liywaa li no wiili sebeli tu kafuweka mu Petiyoli.  
\v 14 Omo sebeli tu ka wana aasikupumena, mi sbeli atumema njintwiikale noo mu maywaa ana kukwana mutanu naayiili.  
\v 15 Cwale aasikupumena omo aba ana ku tuyupa sebeli aiya okutunda oku no kuleba ku Folamu mu sibaka no Appiusi ni ku mahotela aatu mukutu waniketa. Mu kwaamona, Paulusi sebeli oku tumela kwa Nyambe nikuongola omucima. 
\s1 Paulusi yo kutaza mu Loma munji no atateleli 
\p  
\v 16 Cwale aba tuna kukeela mu Loma, Paulusi sebeli amu lumelela nji aikale yomboci ni masole awo ana ku mu sileleza. 
\p  
\v 17 Munyima no maywaa aatu, sebeli oisana aendisi no Majuda, mi cwale aba anokuwana sebeli wamba kwa onyene nji, “Abaange, naaba kanisi tenda esinjili okulwisa aanu simba esizo sa Sitetu, kono kame nina kubeekiwa mu tolongo mu Jelusalema mu maata no Maloma.  
\v 18 Cwale aba ana kumana okuni ibanguta, sebeli asinga nji ani lukulule, kakuli kame ku nakuulwa omubonda no lifu mu taba yange.  
\v 19 Kono aendisi no Majuda aba ana kukana, cwale sebeli ni ku bilaeza kwa Sesale, simba nji kani sikwikala ni mubonda no ku lwisa enaha yange.  
\v 20 Cwalehe mulibaka elyo kame nina kumbele nji ni kumone, kakuli ni mulibaka no sepo no Isilaele eyo inisaiseta oku nungiwa amawenge.” 
\p  
\v 21 Cwale sebeli aamba kwa onyene nji, “Katu sitambula aman̄olo okutunda ku Judeya aa aamba eyowe, mi kakwisa aasikupumena ana tundu oko aneeyi mu kubiha simba okwamba eyi no kwiiba ona ku tenda.  
\v 22 Kono kame tu singa okuyupa kwa wene eso onahana, kakuli okwamana ku tuto no Ndila kame tu limuka nji kame ilwisa koonje.” 
\p  
\v 23 Cwale aba ana kumana oku lukisa eliywaa nookuwana naye, sebeli aiya oko ana kwikalanga mu kupula. Cwale sebeli waatolokela eyaye yonje oku tunda amasiku konji ku mangolwaa, okupaka eyi no mubuso wa Nyambe, nikweteka nji alumele eyambo ya Jesu bamweya oku tunda ba mulawo wa Mushe naanuhi a Nyambe.  
\v 24 Cwale anjili sebeli apumena eyo ana kwamba, mi anjili sebeli akana.  
\v 25 Cwale mu kukana okuyupa mukaci koo, sebeli afunduka, munyima ya Paulusi okwamba eliywi limweya nji, “Emebo No Kukena kame ina kwamba eniti kwa sitenu okubitela mu munuhi wa Nyambe Isaya nji, 
\q1  
\v 26 ‘Mute kwaanu aa, mi mu kaambe nji, 
\q1 luli mba mu yupu kono kamutamba ku yupisisa 
\q2 mi luli mba mu mono kono kamutamba oku monisisa, 
\q1  
\v 27 kakuli emicima no aanu aa, kame yongolile, 
\q2 ni matwi oo kaayupu 
\q2 mi amiyo oo kame akutimine, 
\q1 kono amiyo oo kame ana fanene okumona, 
\q2 amatwi oo kame afanena okuyupa, 
\q2 mane ni kuyupisisa ni micima yoo, 
\q1 mi kame afutukela kwa mene, 
\q2 nji naabalise.’”  
\v 28 Cwale mulimuke nji, “Okuyoisa kwa Nyamba kame kuna ku tumenwa asimacaba mi kame sayupe!”  
\v 29 Aba ana kumana okwamba amaywi ao, aendisi no Majuda sebeli amusiya, mi sebeli kwikala etin̄ananyi no kuneneba mukaci koo. 
\p  
\v 30 Cwale Paulusi sebeli oikala eilimo yiili mu ndoo eyo ana kutenekanga amali, ni ku tambulanga aanu onje awo ana kwiyanga kwa yonyene.  
\v 31 Kame ana ku kutazanga eyi no mubuso wa Nyambe ni kwaiyeta eyi ya Mbumu Jesu Kilesite epatalaza no kwaulwa okushweka simba simweya.